\id ACT  
\h Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇč 
\toc3 Up 
\toc2 Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇč 
\toc1 Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kap 
\mt1 Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kap 
\imt1 Outna kam 
\ip Gan timbigta kapca, anna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta aiŇčna ninininan, na anna Luka tiratna kam wembaŇč laŇčna timbigta kapca eacrena kammo ma memetmbaca nininia mboprina. Na gan timbigta kap toco, Luka ndo tiratnan. Aintik gan timbigta kapca aia watnandet, ŇäeroŇč Ratta up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo taup wandaca mina Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo wiwitia mboprena, ‚ÄúAn Ierusalemna meikramta…®rmo an kam wembaŇč laŇč an wiwiti te, Iudiana pitrik waŇčna inikna auŇčembapa, Samariana auŇčembapa, mon tawan Ňčgoinna auŇčembca gan tiacarpaik ndeacrenanmo, gan kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kocnai metmbaci mbopi taŇčraŇč.‚ÄĚ Anmo sapta 1 wes 8na inikca wat. 
\ip Na Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kapca, ma Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunna Iudana r…®k naŇčgepca iŇčmbaia ma acnaiatna, ri, ma gan tiacarpaikna auŇčembmo tamtamma taŇčri. Na Luk toco, ma gainda wandacna moca, Karaisna aiŇčapa meikramta…®rta t…®pemb kirarir laiŇčga morena tip kirara manmo raŇčgairenan, anna ma atua RaraŇč Aetaniaca IsraelnaŇčgepmo babuatna reikca moa m…®nna t…®katna. 
\ip Na reac aniac ianna Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kapca mboprenan, anna ŇäeroŇč Ratna aiŇč, na anna RaraŇč Aetaniacna ŇäeroŇč. Na out Ňčgoinna ŇäeroŇč Ratta Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena ramta…®rmo Pentikosna ra mbuŇča k…®patna. Ri, iŇčmbaia ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo gargar neaŇčga, mina iroarmo tiŇčara mori, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna aiŇčira moa taŇčrina. 
\ip Na gan timbigta kap toca aia watnande, ma kam t…®p roctir w…®tta up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kabena meikramta…®rmo wiwitica minmo mboprina. Na aia watrinanna, meikramta…®r w…®tta an kam wembaŇč laŇčmo raŇčgairenan, na Iesusna r…®t…®pacna tumbunna Ňčgepca magagrat. 
\ip Na Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kapca ma up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r w…®tna nininiarap, na Pitaapa Pol mbaniŇčna morina reikta nininiar w…®tta an ndeacrena. Na Pita ma Iesusap raŇčgairina ramoot ian. Na Pol tikca ma Ňčgaua Iesusmo mba raŇčgaiatke, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Ma Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunmo, mo irikna aiŇč aniaca moatna. Na Iesusa Polmo aca mamo moca ma out Ňčgoinna laruca mana aiŇča moatna ramoot. 
\ip Na gan timbigta kapna k…®dr…®kar ndeida, Luka ma Pol ndaruatna reikta nininia moatnanna, ma gan kam t…®pap mboprena ‚ÄúAiap.‚ÄĚ Na landamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida mina gaind ndamŇčiatna, Luka ma ndo Ňčgoinna Polapmo k…®dr…®k ndeidap taŇčrina, aintik ma aindopatna, ‚ÄúAia‚ÄĚ na an kam t…®pca gan timbigta kapna k…®dr…®kar ndeida eacrena. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra Iesusna kammo Ierusalemma t…®kca mbopca laruatna 
\mr (1.1‚ÄĒ8.3) 
\s1 Iesusa baburinanna ma ŇäeroŇč Ratmo mbag…®rica k…®pnande 
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Mk 16.19, na Lk 1.1-4, na 24.49-51\x*Tiopilus, an timbigta kapca Ňčgaua aku tirca neaŇčga k…®patnanna, anna Iesusna mandeb Ňčgepca moatna reikta kambapa, ma meikramta…®rmo mimitpac neaŇčgatna kambca, ma an m…®nna t…®kca moa k…®pca RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo tamuŇčna auŇč mac nda aŇčg…®a taŇčgatna m…®n mbuŇčna reik. Na aku an tirca neaŇčga k…®patna. Na an m…®nna t…®kca k…®p, k…®pca RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo mac nda aŇčg…®ra gacatna ra mbuŇč. Ma taŇčga ndona up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r tambuŇč ndarurina, na an ramta…®ra ma ndo larapacrina. Na ŇäeroŇč Ratna gargar mbuŇča ma minmo reac, reacna aiŇčira momona kam ndopca maiatke. IŇčmbaia RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo tamuŇčna auŇč mac nda aŇčg…®rca magat.\f + \fr 1:1-2 \ft Luka gan Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kap tirrinan. Na an kabena timbigta kapca ma Ňčgaua tirca mboprenanna, anna ma ndo tirrina Kam WembaŇč LaŇč.\f* 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Mt 28.17, na Mk 16.12, na Lk 24.36-49, na Up 10.41, na 1 Ko 15.5-7\x*Na ma tamuŇčna auŇča taŇč Ňčgocor ndeacri, outmbaica, ma g…®rg…®r bagaraniac aŇčg…®ca menaca, mutoca eaca. IŇčmbaia ma wat mac nda aŇčg…®ca ma Ňčgepca ndona up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r tambuŇč ndaruca minapmo ainta reac, reac mamori, mimo ndo nagaraca gaind ndamŇčina moca, gidik, ma mac nda maŇčgepri. Aintik ma minapmo rai 40na m…®n ndeaca ma minmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Bubuocna kam mambopat.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Lk 24.49, na In 14.16-17, na Up 2.33\x*Na an m…®n, ma minap eacri, na ma minmo kam gargar mbuŇča gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Ierusalem auŇč aniacmo kai tawi t…®kcarica taŇč teac, aku nemo Ňčgaua ndopatna reacmo, Aetta nenmo neaŇč ndopca babuatna reaca ma neaŇčnande.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Mt 3.11, na Mk 1.8, na Lk 3.16, na In 1.33, na Up 11.16\x*Na Ion, ma meikramta…®rmo k…®tac pukca, puk mbuŇča morena, na rocotta mba t…®kitndai, raeniŇč mai te, ne ŇäeroŇč Rat mbuŇča k…®tac puk aŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ais 1.26, na Emo 9.11, na Mt 24.3, na Lk 24.21\x*Na an m…®n mbuŇča mana up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra k…®pca punica mamo gainda digiatna, ‚ÄúKacoot, u mandeaca Israelna tiacarpaikna bubuoca minmo mac nda neaŇčit ki, wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Atu Ňčgoinna Israelna ramta…®r koinda ndorita gagrirta ramta…®rmo, mo laruca eacrina. Na mina minmo bubuocrina. Na Iesusna m…®n mbuŇča IsraelnaŇčgepca Romna pitrikna kaŇčgauk ndeacrina. Ainda moca Iesusa laruatna k…®dr…®kca, meikramta…®r w…®tta gaind ndamŇčiatna, ma RomnaŇčgepmo mo kecarinandet. Na IsraelnaŇčgepta wiwitna gagrirta ramta…®rmo mac mo Ňčgepnande.\f* 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mt 24.36, na Mk 13.32, na 1 Te 5.1\x*Ri, ma mina kammo gainda nda rutiatna, ‚ÄúAnna nena reaca wanaiŇč. Ne an raiapa ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…® Aetnan ndamŇčina, anna mana reac, ma ndo kabe ndamŇčirena. Anna mana landamŇčina ŇčginaŇčna kaŇčgauk ndeacrenan.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Mt 28.19, na Mk 16.15, na Lk 24.47-48, na In 15.27, na Up 2.32, na 3.15, na 5.32\x*Na iŇčmbaia an m…®n ŇäeroŇč Ratta ndo k…®pca nenap eac te, ne gagrar aŇčg…®nande. Te, ne Ňčgepca aukna morina reikta kambmo, Ierusalemna meikramta…®rmo an kam wembaŇč laŇč an wiwiti te, Iudiana pitrik waŇčna inikna auŇčembapa Samarianandapa, mon tawan Ňčgoinna auŇčembca gan tiacarpaik ndeacrenanmo, gan kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kocnai metmbaci mbopi taŇčraŇč.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iesusa tamuŇčna auŇč magat 
\r (Mak 16.19 na Luk 24.50-53) 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Mk 16.19, na Lk 24.50-51, na In 6.62, na 20.17\x*Karica Iesusa an kam ndopacarica, mina watrinan mbuŇča, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo aŇčg…®ra magari, na magari waw…®rpaikca k…®pca manmo, aŇčg…®ra iŇčgorocatke, mina mamo mba mac watatke. \fig RaraŇč Aetaniaca Iesusmo aŇčg…®ra magareke|src="gw135 mod.tif" size="col" copy="Wade" ref="1.9" \fig* 
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Mt 28.3, na Mk 16.5, na Lk 24.4, na In 20.12, na Up 10.3, na 10.30\x*Ma taŇčgacariatke, mina w…®t…®kca riac tamuŇčmo an motemmo, mataua ŇčginaŇčikca eacri. Na tik Ňčgapaoc gogokapna ramooteniŇča tawi Ňčgoin motemma, mina k…®t…®m ndarua maw…®t…®kat.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Mt 24.30, na 26.64, na Lk 21.27, na In 14.3, na 1 Te 1.10, na 4.16, na KIEK 1.7\x*ManiŇča gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Galilina ramta…®r, tida moca ne w…®t…®kca riac tamuŇčmo ŇčginaŇčikca eacre? An ramoot Iesus, ma nen t…®kcarica mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca mamo tamuŇčna auŇč naaŇčg…®ra magari, na ma gade gacpeke, ne watapekna kirar, mana gan tiacarpaikca nda k…®k…®pa, ne manmo aind mbatnandet.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mina Iudasna taup aŇčg…®na ramoot ian larapacatna 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Lk 24.50\x*Karica up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, mina Olip Ňčgacrina takur t…®kcarica, mina Ňčgepca Ierusalemma nda mataŇčgat. Na an Olip Takur ŇčgetacndiŇča, Ierusalemma tataŇča tawan Ňčgoinna wanaiŇč.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Mt 10.2-4, na Mk 3.16-19, na Lk 6.14-16\x*Ri, mina taŇčga Ierusalem auŇč aniacna inikca mbukca taŇčga ndorita Ňčgau ndeacrina kacna tamuŇčmbaina diabca mbukna morina, an ramta…®rta irembca gade, ianna Pita, na ianna Ion, na ianna Iemis, na ianna Andru, na ianna Pilip, na ianna Tomas, na ianna Batolomiu, na ianna Matiu, na ianna Iemis, ma Alpiusna nuoc, na ianna Saimon ma Selotna barna ramoot ian, na ianna Iudas ma Iemisna nuoc.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mt 13.55, na Lk 23.49, na 23.55, na 24.10, na In 6.42, na 7.5\x*An ramta…®ra ndorimo aŇčg…®ra iro kabea t…®kca, memetmbaca ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica mbendeirena, na meik ndeidapa Iesusna aem Mariaapa mana laipitik, mitoco memetmbaca k…®pca minap t…®kca mbendeirena. 
\p  
\v 15 Na an m…®nna k…®pca puniatna, Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 120na m…®n. Ri, Pita mina r…®kca w…®t…®kca minmo gaindopatna,  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Ňäap 41.9\x*‚ÄúMin aukna laiplacar, ŇäeroŇč Ratta Dewitmo iro neaŇčga ma atu ndopatna kambca, RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapna inik ndeacrena kambca, ma Iudasna kam ndopatna. An ramoot Iudas, ma or ikca mina k…®pca Iesusmo utiŇčgatna. Dewitta aindopatna kamna gagamma ma amna reac aŇčg…®nandet, na mandeaca mana gagamma ande ma malaruri.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 10.4, na Lk 6.16, na Up 1.25\x*Na an ramoot Iudas, ma aiap aiŇč kabea morina tumbunna ramoot ian, Ňčgaua ma toco ma ai aŇčg…®rca morina aiŇčna aiŇča morina ramoot ian.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mt 26.15, na 2 Pi 2.15\x*\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Mt 27.3-8\x*Karica an ramoot Iudasa ndo moatna t…®p Ňčgoreacna aiŇčna opoikna kituknduk aŇčg…®ca, an mbuŇča pitrik waŇč emtem Ňčgoikca. IŇčmbaia ma an pitrik Ňčgirikca keca gadaup titaca mimuŇčapa larkamapa an pitrik mairikat.\f + \fr 1:18 \ft U Iudasmo kaina reaca larurinanna matau lamŇči garacna mo te, u Matiu sapta 27 wes 5na timbigta kapna inikca wat. \f* 
\v 19 Ainda moca iŇčmbaia Ierusalemna inik ndeacrina meikramta…®r, mina muruŇča an kam anna waraca malamŇčiat. Ainda moca mina ndorita auŇčna kam mbuŇča an pitrik umbummo gaind Ňčgacrina, \it Akeldama\it*. An i \it Akeldama\it* mana m…®n…®Ňča gaind, ‚ÄúRacaindta Pitrik Umbum.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Ňäap 69.25, na 109.8\x*Karica Pita gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúAn kambca mina Ňäaparta timbigta kapna inikca tirca eacrena kambca gaind, ‚ÄėMana eacatna kac mananna kabena ramoot ianna mana kaca kai aŇčg…® teac, an kaca watcarica ma wanaiŇč ndeac, na u an kacmo kai watcarica ramoot ianna kai aŇčg…® teac.‚Äô Na an timbigta kapna kam t…®p ian toco gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄėKabena ramoot ianmo watcarica ma mana taup rutica ma morina aiŇč aŇčg…®ca mo.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúAintik aia mandeaca Kacoot Iesusa aina inikca aiap eacri, memetmbac taŇč k…®p t…®krina, ramta…®rta ianna watca manmo larapaca, ma Iudasna taup aŇčg…®.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Mt 3.16, na Mk 1.9, na 16.19, na Lk 3.21, na 24.51, na In 15.27, na Up 4.33\x*Na an larapacna ramoot, ma Ionna mandeb Ňčgepca meikramta…®rmo k…®tac pukca moatna aiŇčapa, Iesusna aiŇča mandeba aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepca, moa k…®pca RaraŇč Aetaniacna ŇčganŇčg…®atna m…®n ndaruri, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo aŇčg…®ca ma ai t…®kcarica tamuŇčna auŇč naaŇčg…®ca magat, na an reikca watatna ramoot ianna, aia ainta ramoot larapaca, ma ai Ňčgotaca Iesusna menaca mac nda Ňčgepatna kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwitina.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 Pita aindopatke, mina Ňčgepca ramoot mbuniŇčmo lamarapacat ianna Iosep, mana i ianna Barsabas, na mana i ian toco Iastus. Na ramoot ianna ia Matias.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt 1 Sml 16.7, na Ier 11.20, na In 2.25, na KIEK 2.23\x*Karica mina gaind mambendeiat, ‚ÄúKacoot, u gan ramta…®rta iroar inkar teacrena landamŇčiara, u malamŇčireke, gan ramootniŇčmo u ndo maniŇčmo, aimo ian wandaca mbop.  
\v 25 Te, ma up aŇčg…®rena ramoot ian ndaruca, Iudasna taup aŇčg…®na. Iudasa an aiŇč an t…®kcarica. Na ma taŇčga ndona eacrina auŇč, an mac nda mataŇčri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Ri, mina Ňčgepca mat…®p rocot, na gegerei ian tocna gegerei nagereica wattatnanna, Matiasa ndo aŇčg…®atna mbatca, mina manmo aŇčg…®ra parniŇčapa mbut kabe ndeacrena up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta inik mat…®kat. 
\c 2  
\s1 ŇäeroŇč Ratta irikatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt TW 16.9-11, na Up 1.14\x*Pentikosna ra aniac laruatke, Iesusna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇča k…®pca taup kabea punica eacri.\f + \fr 2:1 \fk Pentikosna ra aniac: \ft Anna Israelnanda is kocorta tapac ambrena rana iŇčmbai, an 50na m…®nna raipaik mai te. Pentikosna ra larurena. An i, Pentikosna ra aniac, mana i ianna, mina War…®Ňčna Amta Reik AŇčg…®na ToŇčtoŇč Na Ra Aniac. Na Taup Ndamta…®rna timbigta kapca an kam toco eacrenan sapta 23 wes 15 taŇčca wes 22na m…®n.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Up 4.31\x*Na tamuŇčna auŇča m…®tm…®t ianna anduna ndaruatke, mina waracatnanna, anna ma aigogomna m…®tm…®tna kirar toc nak…®patnanna, mina mbiraca eacrina an kacna inikmo kocnaia neaŇčga gararamacariat.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Mt 3.11\x*Ri, mina wattatnanna, reac ianna tacna kirar toc, ndaruatke, anna inikca tacna mim tocna reikca titaca an inik ndaruca mina watri, an tac tocna mimma mina kabe, kabemo muruŇč mairikat.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Mk 16.17, na Up 1.5, na 4.31, na 10.44-46, na 1 Ko 12.10, na 13.1\x*Ainda moca minmo muruŇča ŇäeroŇč Ratta mbukca m…®nna t…®kca, na mina Ňčgepca auŇčembta kambca muruŇč mambopri, anna ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo gargar neaŇčga, minmo kabena auŇčembta kamb puŇč topna moca. 
\p  
\v 5 Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®pacrina Iudana meikramta…®r ndeida, gan tiacarpaikna pitrik waŇčgorta auŇčemb ŇčgetacndiŇč nak…®pca mina muruŇča Ierusalem ndeacrina.  
\v 6 Na an m…®tm…®t aniaca laruatna m…®nna, meikramta…®ra mina muruŇča anna waraca, anna wat ndopca k…®pca mapuniat. Na mina kour ikca waracri, Iesusna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r mbopatna kambca, an k…®pca puniatna auŇčembta auŇč kabe, kabena kamb puŇč toprina, ri, mina waracatnanna mina kam Ňčgoin. Ainda moca mina Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca tamtam ndamŇčirina.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Up 1.11\x*Karica an Iudana meikramta…®ra anna watca Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca, aindopatna, ‚ÄúAn ramta…®ra muruŇča Galili niŇčgiknan ki?  
\v 8 Kaica aia waracapeke, mina aina auŇčemb kabe, kabena kamb koind puŇč ndopapekna.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Wat, aia pitrik kabe ŇčgetacndiŇča mba k…®pri. Aina gan inikna meacramoot kabe, kabea, aia gan pitrikartiŇč nda k…®patna, aina ndeida pitrik Partiapa, Midiapa, Elamnan. Na aina ndeida aia gan pitrikartiŇč toco k…®prina, Mesopotemiapa, Iudiaapa, Kapadosiaapa, na Pontusapa, Esiana pitrikap an ŇčgetacndiŇč nak…®prina.  
\v 10 Na pitrik Pirigiapa, Pampilia, na pitrik Isipap, na pitrik Libia ma mon Sairini auŇč aniaca rambuŇčaia eacrena, na aia Romna meikramta…®r toco, aia muruŇč nak…®pca gan ndeacrina.  
\v 11 Aia Iudanandapa Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇča muruŇča ndorita iroar Ňčgetrikica, Iudana r…®pacrina r…®t…®paca raŇčgairi. Aina ndeida mon mut Kiritapa pitrik Arebianan, aia muruŇča waracri, mina aina auŇčembta kamb puŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniacna morina reik anikta kamb topri, aia waracatna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Ainda moca mina Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca, iroara tamtam ndamŇčica ndori puŇčga aindopatna, ‚ÄúAn laruapekna reaca, anna kaina reacna m…®n…®Ňč?‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Ri, mina ndeida minmo piria mbopca gaindopca, ‚ÄúAnna mina wain puik amba, amba paŇčaind roreca mboprena kamb.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pita an laruapekna reikta kamna m…®n…®Ňč ndopca laruatna 
\p  
\v 14 Karica Pita up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r 11na m…®npaikap w…®t…®kca, ma kam aniac Ňčgoin mbuŇča meikramta…®rmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Iudanandapa, an k…®pamaica gan Ierusalem ndeacrena meikramta…®r, ne gan laruapekke, ne watapekna reikta m…®niŇčga, aku mbop te, ne kour ikca matau warac.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Te 5.7\x*Ne an ramta…®rmo anmo ŇčaŇčaoraŇč ndopat ki? WanaiŇč Ňčgoin, mina wain pukca mba amba ŇčaŇčaoreke, na mandeac ŇčaŇčarmuŇča, rana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 9na m…®n niŇčgik.\f + \fr 2:15 \ft Na an kamma Pita mbopatnanna, Iudananda mina puk wainmo ŇčaŇčarmuŇč Ňčgoinna mba ambrena.\f* 
\v 16 Gan reaca mandeban ndaruapeknan atua an reacmo ramma morina ramoot Ioela, mana kammo, ma gaindopatna,  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Iol 2.28-32, na Sek 12.10, na In 7.38, na Up 10.45, na 21.9\x*‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniaca aindoprina, ‚ÄúMaica gan tiacarpaikna mamamaia k…®pi rambuŇčai te, aku ndona ŇäeroŇč Ratmo, meikramta…®r tambatmo muruŇčcamiŇča kactacnandet. Te, nena nuikapa momboura, rambca moa mboprina ramta…®rta kirarir toc ndaruca aukna kam ndopnande. Te, ramta…®r Ňčgaibi manmb…®anmemraŇč, tocna tamram mbuŇč mbatnande, te, ramta…®r bagrara, tamram mbuŇč mbatnande.  
\v 18 Na an m…®n toco, aku ndona mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ramta…®rapa meikmo ndona ŇäeroŇč Ratmo min nambatta kactac te, mina aukna kammo atuna rambca moca mboprina ramta…®rta kirarir toc ndopnandet.  
\v 19 Te, aku ainta Ňčgagatracarmo riac tamuŇča t…®ki laru te, aku gan Ňčgagatracarmo tiacarpaik w…®k…®nna t…®ki larunandet. An reikta Ňčgagatracara, racaindpaikapa tacapa tactuor aniaca gan tiacarpaik ndarunandet.  
\v 20 Te, ra kocnai nenepucari te, karwaia kocnai laupcarica racaindpaik toc ndacarinandet. Na iŇčmbai Ňčgoinna Kacootna ra aniac Ňčgoinna larunandet.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Ro 10.13\x*An m…®nna, meikramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇča Kacootna i Ňčgac te, ndori kotacna digi te, ma minmo mac nda aŇčg…®ca mina mba Ňčgocraiitndai.‚ÄĚ‚Äô Na an kambca ramma morina ramoot Ioel, ma an ndopatna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt In 3.2, na 14.10-11, na Ib 2.4\x*Na Pita ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe IsraelnaŇčgepta meikramta…®r, ne aukna gan kammo, kour ikca matau warac. Aku nemo gan Nasaretna ramoot Iesusna kam ndop te, ne warac. Ne ndori waracatke watatna, RaraŇč Aetaniacna moatna reik anikta aiŇčir anikapa, mana moatna ainta Ňčgagatracara, ma Iesusna para t…®kca ma nena r…®kmo ndoa watrapaca aindopna moca, ‚ÄėAn ramootta RaraŇč Aetaniac mbag…®rica k…®patna ramoot.‚Äô  
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Mt 27.35, na Mk 15.24, na Lk 23.33, na In 19.18, na Up 4.28, na 1 Pi 1.20\x*Na an ramootmo, nena para t…®katnan. Na an ramootmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca atu Ňčgoinna ma lamŇčiatna, ma manmo ainda mo ndopca, ma kam leaca maica nena para t…®katna. Te, ne mamo aŇčg…®ra ramta…®r Ňčgorikta par mat…®kat, na mina manmo ik naaŇčg…®ra keraca ma mamenacat.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Mt 28.5-6, na Mk 16.6, na Lk 24.5, na Up 3.15, na 4.10, na 10.40, na 13.30-31, na 17.31, na 1 Ko 15.15\x*Te, RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma manmo mba an memenacna taup Ňčgoreaca mba wattacarica ma mba anna mba mac eacatke. Na memenaca ma gargar kocor ma an ramootmo mo menacna towanaiŇč.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Ňäap 16.8-11\x*Aintik Dewit toco atua ndomo aindopatna, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄėAku Kacootmo watreke, 
\q2 ma aukna k…®t…®mmo 
\q3 memetmbaca aukap eacreke, 
\q3 na ma aukmo moa gagrarenan, 
\q2 aintik reac ianna aukmo moi nanambi te, 
\q3 na moi rugut mona m…®nna wanaiŇč. 
\q1  
\v 26 Ainda moca aukna iro inikca toŇčtoŇč aniac laruca, 
\q2 aku kam toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoinna, aindopnandet. 
\q1 Aku RaraŇč Aetaniacna ndabirena, 
\q2 ma aukmo reik laiŇčga monande. 
\q1  
\v 27 \x - \xo 2:27 \xt Up 13.35\x*Ainda moca u aukmo mba watcarica, 
\q2 aukna ŇčeroŇča an meikramta…®rta menaca eacrena 
\q3 taupca mba eacitndai. Na ramootmo u babuca, 
\q2 ma una ramoot rat ndarurina ramootta, 
\q3 u mamo mba watcarica 
\q3 ma an menaca kotrena taupca mba eacitndai, 
\q3 wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.\f + \fr 2:27 \ft Menacrena warirta ŇčerŇčgaur eacrena taup. Na IudanaŇčgepca manmo Girikna kam mbuŇča \ft \+it Ades\+it* Ňčgacrena. \f* 
\v 28 U aukmo iarwar ndeacna auŇč laŇčna taupca 
\q2 u aukmo wandaca mamairi. 
\q1 Ainda moca u aukmo watcarica 
\q2 aku unap eac te, 
\q2 u aukmo moca aku iarwar ndeteacna toŇčtoŇč bagaraniaca, 
\q2 memetmbaca aukap eacraŇčnandet.‚Äô 
\b  
\m Na gan kambca Dewit mbopatna kam.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 29 \x - \xo 2:29 \xt 1 GRP 2.10, na Lk 1.32, na 1.69, na Up 13.36, na 2 Ti 2.8\x*Karica Pita gaindopatna, ‚ÄúMin laiplacar, aku nemo wandoŇč Ňčgoinna aindopnande, aina nicau Dewit. Ma menaca mina manmo mamutocri. Mana mukca aiap maeacreke.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 2:30 \xt 2 Sml 7.12-13, na Ňäap 89.3-4, na 132.11\x*Na Dewit tikca, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna ramma morina ramoot ian. Aintik Dewit, ma lamŇčirina RaraŇč Aetaniacna babuca mbopatna gan kamma, ma gidik Ňčgoin ndopatna, ‚ÄėIŇčmbaia aku una mombonikta ianmo aŇčg…®ri gagrirta ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ri w…®t…®kca, ma una kirar toc ndarunande.‚Äô  
\v 31 \x - \xo 2:31 \xt Ňäap 16.10, na Up 13.35\x*Aintik Dewitta an RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbopatna reikta kammo, ma atuna ndamŇčiatna, mamo RaraŇč Aetaniaca mba watcarica ma memenacna taup inikca mba eacitndai, na mana wa…®ra mba kotitndai. Na Dewit, ma an kam ndopatnanna, ma mba ndonake, mba mbopatke, wanaiŇč. RaraŇč Aetaniaca mo ndopatna reikmo, ma atuna ndamŇčiatna. Ainda moca ma an ramootna kamma ma an ndopatna, an ramootta RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot, ma muk ndiŇč mac nda Ňčgepnandet.\f + \fr 2:31 \ft An ramootta RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot, na Girikna kam mbuŇča mina gaind Ňčgacrena, \ft \+it ‚ÄúKarais.‚ÄĚ\+it*\f* 
\v 32 \x - \xo 2:32 \xt Up 1.8, na 2.24\x*An ramoot, ande Iesus. RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo mukca t…®kca moa maŇčgepat. Na aia muruŇča manmo muk ŇčgetacndiŇč naŇčgepatna iŇčmbai mbuŇča aia manmo watatke, aia mana nda Ňčgepatnanna aia ndorita lamnik puŇčga watca, aia nemo anna wiwitia mboprena.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 2:33 \xt In 14.26, na Up 1.4, na 5.31, na 7.55-56, na 10.45, na Epe 4.8, na Ib 10.12\x*Na Iesus tikca mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca mamo aŇčg…®a gaca ndona tamuŇčna auŇča, ma mana par umbai maeacreke. Aintik atua RaraŇč Aetaniaca mamo neaŇč ndopca babuatna ŇäeroŇč Ratta, ma mamo neaŇčga ma muruŇčcamiŇča kactaca, ne waracatke, na mawatat.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 2:34 \xt Ňäap 110.1\x* Na Dewit, ma tamuŇčna auŇča Iesus gacatna kirar toca mba gacatke. Na ma aindopatna, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniac Kacootta ma aukna Kacootmo gaindopatna, 
\q2 ‚ÄúU aukna par umbaia mbirac te. 
\q2  
\v 35 Aku una puŇčnaŇčgepmo, 
\q3 una kaŇčgaukca t…®knande.‚ÄĚ‚Äô 
\b  
\p  
\v 36 \x - \xo 2:36 \xt Up 5.30-31\x*‚ÄúAintik ne IsraelnaŇčgepca ne gaind Ňčgoinna matau lamŇči, an ramoot Iesusmo, ne manmo aŇčg…®ra ik naaŇčg…®a keracatnanna, mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo aŇčg…®rca Kacoot Ňčgacrina, na an ramoot, ma RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca iro inkar Ňčgetrikica puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat 
\p  
\v 37 \x - \xo 2:37 \xt Sek 12.10, na Lk 3.10-12, na Up 9.6, na 16.30\x*Ainda moca meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca Pita mbopatna kam mbaraca, an kamma mina iroar inkarca r…®Ňčri. Mina Ňčgepca Pitaapa up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo gaind madigiat, ‚ÄúMin laiplacar, ainda mo te, aia tida moit?‚ÄĚ  
\v 38 \x - \xo 2:38 \xt Lk 24.47, na Up 3.19\x*Ri, Pita minmo gainda nda rutica mambopat, ‚ÄúNe muruŇčcamiŇča ramoot kabe, kabea, ne ndorita iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica, Iesus Karaisna i mbuŇča k…®tac puk aŇčg…® te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nena t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukara, ma mo kecarinandet. Ne ainda mo te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nenmo ŇäeroŇč Rat neaŇčnande.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 2:39 \xt Ais 57.19, na Iol 2.28, na Up 10.45, na 14.27, na Epe 2.13, na 2.17\x*Ňägaua RaraŇč Aetaniac baburina ŇäeroŇč Ratta ma nenapa nena mombonikapa mon tawanna auŇčembta meikramta…®rap, ma ndo aca k…®pekna meikramta…®rmo ma ŇäeroŇč Ratta neaŇčnande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 40 \x - \xo 2:40 \xt TW 32.5, na Pil 2.15\x*Ri, Pita minmo kabena kamb ndeidap mbopca maica, ma minmo kam gargar Ňčgoinna gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNdorita ŇčginaŇča matau mo, te, ndoritake wat, moca ne toco, an t…®p Ňčgorikca morena meikramta…®rap Ňčgocrai nari.‚ÄĚ  
\v 41 \x - \xo 2:41 \xt Up 2.47, na 4.4, na 5.14\x*Ri, Pitana mbopatna kambca meikramta…®r w…®t anikta iroar inkara r…®Ňčga, mina puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat. Na an ra ndaruca Iesusa r…®paca eacrena wiwitta mbukatna meikramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a, 3,000na m…®n toc malaruat. 
\s1 Meacramoota iro kabe Ňčgoin aŇčg…®ca maeacri 
\p  
\v 42 \x - \xo 2:42 \xt Up 20.7\x*An k…®dr…®kca meikramta…®ra up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta riptia mataua waracri, na mina ndorita reikmo ndorimo otacrina, ri, mina ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica tapac r…®mb…®tca ndorimo biŇčaica ambrina, ri, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mambendeiri.\f + \fr 2:42 \ft LandamŇčina ramta…®r w…®tta gaind ndamŇčirena, an outna Karaisna r…®t…®pacna tumbunna meikramta…®ra, mina ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica ambrena, na mina am mai te, mina Iesusna tikapa racaindpaikna ndamŇčica mina tapacapa wain puk amnande.\f* 
\v 43 \x - \xo 2:43 \xt Mk 16.17, na Up 4.33, na 5.11-12\x*Na Iesusna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta para t…®kca ainta Ňčgagatracara mori, meikramta…®ra muruŇča an Ňčgagatracara watta maica, mina rugdar mamori.  
\v 44 \x - \xo 2:44 \xt Up 4.32-35, na 5.12, na 6.8\x* Ainda moca meikramta…®ra Iesusa r…®paca eacrenanna, memetmbaca mina muruŇča ndorimo aŇčg…®ra, punica eacrina, ri, mina ndorita reikmo ndorica biŇčaia maaŇčg…®ri.  
\v 45 Karica, mina ndorita pitrikar waŇčgorpaikembapa, ndorita t…®kca eacrina reikmo mbik t…®kca oikrina taupca t…®kca meikramta…®ra oikri, mina an kitukndukar aŇčg…®ca, an koteterina meikramta…®rmo, an kitukndukar biŇčaica mina an puŇčga reik maoikri.  
\v 46 \x - \xo 2:46 \xt Lk 24.53, na Up 1.14, na 20.7\x*Na an r…®pacrina meikramta…®r, memetmbaca mina ndorimo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca aŇčg…®ra punireke, ndorita kaikmo ian ianna t…®kreke, amba taŇčreke, toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin, ainda moca mina ndorimo aind naaŇčg…®ra punica aind Ňčgambca taŇčrena.  
\v 47 \x - \xo 2:47 \xt Up 2.41, na 4.33, na 5.14, na 6.7, na 11.21, na 11.24, na Ro 14.18\x*Na memetmbaca mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna i aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepreke, meikramta…®ra minmo ainda morenanna moca, mina toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Na Kacootta ra kabe, kabena inikca ma meikramta…®rmo mac nda aŇčg…®rena, ma ainda moreke, mina Iesusa r…®paca eacrena tumbunna mbukreke, Iesusa r…®pacrena tumbunna ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a kunda tamuŇč Ňčgoin magareke. 
\c 3  
\s1 Pita, ma orniŇča menaca eacrina ramootmo moa laŇča moatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Ňäap 55.17, na Up 2.46, na 10.3, na 10.9, na 10.30\x*Oit ianna, wigwac mbuŇča, rana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a mbonkacna m…®nna t…®katke, Pitaapa Ionna RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbendeina moca mataŇčgat.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt In 9.1, na Up 14.8\x*ManiŇča taŇčga laruca wattatnanna, meikramta…®r ndeida ramoot ianna orniŇča menaca eacrina ramootap aŇčg…®ca mak…®pat, na memetmbaca mina an ramootmo ra, ra katuca aŇčg…®a k…®pca ma an RaraŇč Aetaniacna raekmbaina Kacna wuoc aniacna t…®Ňča t…®kca ma an ndeacraŇč te, watraŇčnande. Na an t…®Ňčna ia T…®Ňč Taror. Meikramta…®ra RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukna k…®p te, ma minmo kitukndukarta runande. Na an ramoot, mana orniŇča aemna nikinikca t…®kca Ňčgocraica, mana aemma mamo ainda m…®ratna.  
\v 3 Na an ramoot, ma Pitaapa Ionna watca, maniŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukna taŇčgatke, ma maniŇčmo kitukndukna maruat.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Up 14.9\x*Na Pitaapa Ionna manmo mataua watikca, Pita aind mambopat, ‚ÄúU aŇčga wat.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Ri, an ramootta anmo maniŇčmo ndomo reac ian neneaŇč ndopca watatke.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Up 3.16, na 4.10, na 16.18\x*Ri, Pita aindopatna, ‚ÄúAku k…®tca…®rtukar kocor, na auk ndambuŇča reac ianna ndo maeacreke, aku unmo neaŇčnande. An reaca aku umo Nasaretna ramoot Iesus Karaisna i mbuŇča aindopnande, u Ňčgepca taŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Aindopacarica Pita mamo otaca mana gagar umbai ŇčgutiŇčga manmo aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepca w…®t…®katke, tawi Ňčgoin motemma mana ort…®mb…®kniŇčapa Ňčgorac mburmburniŇča laŇč mamoat.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Ais 35.6, na In 5.14, na Up 14.10\x*Ri, ma putrikica Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca maniŇčap taŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca tamtam naaŇčg…®ra putriri, an inikca taŇč k…®p t…®kri, RaraŇč Aetaniacna imo aŇčg…®ra maŇčgepri.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Up 4.16, na 4.21\x*Ainda mori, meikramta…®ra muruŇča watri ma Ňčgepca RaraŇč Aetaniacna imo aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepri, tamtamma putririnanna watca.  
\v 10 Mina malamŇčiat, anna ande orniŇča menaca eacrena ramoot. Memetmbaca ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca ma taŇčga raekmbaina wuocna T…®Ňč Tarormo an ndeacrena. Na meikramta…®rmo kitukndukarapa reikta rurena ramoot. Na mina watri ma laŇč mamori, ainda moca mina anna watca mina iroara tamtam malamŇčiat. 
\s1 Pita RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca meikramta…®rmo an kamb ndopatna 
\p  
\v 11 Ainda moca meikramta…®ra Ňčgepca an ramootta watna moca, muruŇča ootta k…®pca laruca wattatnanna, ma Pitaapa Ion mbaniŇčmo muocameraca mina wacraet ndeacri, mina k…®pca laruca anna t…®kca mawatri. Na an wacraetna imo, mina gaind Ňčgacrena, Solomonna wacraet.  
\v 12 Ri, Pita ainda watatke, ma meikramta…®rmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNe IsraelnaŇčgepta meikramta…®r, kaina moca ne an laruapekna reac mbatca Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca, aŇčmo wat gargar mbatek? Ne an reacmo gaind ki ndamŇčire ki, aŇčga ndoniŇčna gargar mbuŇčapa aŇčna ndiarirta t…®pemb kirarir laŇč ki, manmo moa laŇča momo ndopat ki? Aintik aŇčga manmo moa laŇča moca ma ndona orniŇč mbuŇča taŇčre ki? WanaiŇč Ňčgoin, ne ainda kai lamŇči teac.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt NA 3.6, na 3.15, na Mt 22.32, na Lk 23.13-25, na Up 2.23, na 7.32\x*RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma Abraamapa, Aisakapa Iakopap, ma mina RaraŇč Aetaniac, na an RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma aina an Ňčgamrirta RaraŇč Aetaniac. Aintik ma ndona aiŇčna Ramoot Iesusmo, i aniac neaŇčgatna. Ande an ramootmo ne mamo aŇčg…®ra puŇčnaŇčgepta para t…®kca, Pailatta manmo watcarica ma taŇčna moatke. Ne Pailatmo iŇč neaŇčga w…®t…®katke, gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU Iesusmo kai watcarica taŇč teac.‚Äô  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Mt 27.15-23, na Mk 15.6-14, na Lk 23.13-23, na In 19.12-15\x*Aindopatna ramootta, mandeaca ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna kaŇčgauk Ňčgoin maeacreke. Ma ramoot rat wandoŇč Ňčgoin. Na ne IsraelnaŇčgepta meikramta…®r, ne an ramootmo ne manmo iŇč neaŇčgatke, ne Pailatmo aca mambopat, ‚ÄėU ramootta r…®Ňčga menacatna an ramootmo ai ndambuŇča mbag…®rica k…®p.‚Äô  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Up 1.8, na 2.24, na 2.32, na 2.36, na 4.10\x*Na aimo iarwar ndeteacna taup naaŇčg…®ri laruna ramoot laŇčmo, ne aŇčg…®ra manmo moa mamenacat. Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo muk inikca t…®kca mac nda moa Ňčgepatke, aŇčga anna watca nemo an reacna kam wiwitia mboprenan.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Mt 9.22, na Up 4.10, na 14.9\x* Na aŇčga Iesusa r…®pacrina ramootniŇč, aintik Iesusna ina gargar mbuŇča, gan nena lamŇčirena or ŇčgoreacniŇčna ramootta moa laŇča moapekna. Iesusa ndo aŇčna r…®t…®paca moa paŇčpaiŇčiri, an r…®t…®paca ndo an ramootmo moca ma laŇča moapekna. Ainda moca mandeaca ne mamo aind mawatca. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Lk 23.34, na In 16.3, na 1 Ko 2.8, na 1 Ti 1.13\x*‚ÄúMin laiplacar, anna gidik, aku lamŇčirina ne ainda ŇčaŇčari lamŇči Ňčgocor tik, nenapa nena ramta…®r paŇčaindap, ne Iesusmo ainda moatna.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ais 50.6, na 53.5, na Lk 24.27, na 24.44, na Up 26.22, na 1 Pi 1.10-11\x*Ainda moca atua RaraŇč Aetaniaca an kambmo rambca morina ramta…®rta iroar inkara t…®kca, mina an ramootna kambmo aindopatna, RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramootta, ma g…®rg…®r aŇčg…®nande, aindopatna kamma, mandeaca ne an ramootmo ainda moapeke, RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndona mbopatna kambmo moa m…®n mat…®kca. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Up 2.38\x*‚ÄúAintik mandeaca ne ndorita iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica, RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgai te, ma nena t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukarmo ma mo kecarinandet.  
\v 20 Ne ainda mo te, Kacootta ma nenap eac te, ma nenmo w…®kt…®t…®k laŇčapa gargar neaŇčnande. Na an ramoot Ňčgaua RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot. Ande an ramoot, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo larapacatna, ma Iesus.  
\v 21 Aintik mandeaca ma tamuŇčna auŇč maeacreke, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna ŇčganŇčg…®rina, an rana moca malambireke, an ra laru te, ma an reikmo mac nda moi Ňčgaib tarunande. Ainda moca ma atua ndona an reik lataruna kamb topna moca ramta…®r ndepik larapaca mina rambca morina ramta…®r taruatke, ma minmo ndona aiŇč anna mona moca, an kambmo mina upembca t…®kca mbopca laruatna. 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt TW 18.15-19, na Up 7.37\x*‚ÄúNa atu Ňčgoinna Mosesa gaindopatna, ‚ÄėNena Kacoot RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma nena barna ianmo ma larapacnande, na ma aukna kirar tocna ramma morena ramoot ndaruca, ne mana mbopekna kambca waraca ne an kambmo kocnai raŇčgairaŇč.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt TN 23.29\x*Na meikramta…®ra mandaia an ramma morena ramootna kam mbarac Ňčgocor, RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo kocnai mo topnandet. Te, mina Israelnanta inikca mba mac eacitndai.‚Äô\f + \fr 3:23 \fk Ramma morena ramoot: \ft Na an ramma morena ramootna kamma RaraŇč Aetaniaca neaŇčga k…®prinanna, anna ma T…®p Wand…®kna timbigta kap sapta 18 wes 15 taŇčca wes 19na m…®n ndeacrena. Na Pita ma gaindoprina, Iesusa ma ndo Ňčgoinna an ramma morena ramoot.\f* 
\v 24 Na atua RaraŇč Aetaniacna ramma morina ramoot Samuelna m…®napa mana iŇčmbai ndaruatna rambca morina ramta…®ra, muruŇča gade mandeban ndaruapekna reacna kamma mina anna ninirena. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 3:25 \xt RL 12.3, na 18.18, na 22.18, na Ro 9.4, na 9.8, na Gal 3.8, na 3.26\x*‚ÄúNe an rambca morina ramta…®rta mombonik Ňčgamrira, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nena nicara neaŇč ndopca minap kam leaca gagara moatna reikca ne aŇčg…®nande. Ma Abraammo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėUna r…®mb…®nna nuoc mbuŇč tik, aku gan tiacarpaikna meikramta…®rmo muruŇč Ňčgotacnande.‚Äô  
\v 26 \x - \xo 3:26 \xt Mt 10.5, na Lk 24.47, na Up 13.32-33, na 13.46\x*Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndona an aiŇčna ramootmo larapaca manmo nen ndambuŇčmo outmbaica mbag…®rica ma k…®patna, nenmo otaca nena t…®pemb Ňčgorikmo kabe, kabe naŇčgetrikina moca.‚ÄĚ 
\c 4  
\s1 Mina Pitaapa Ion mbaniŇčmo ramta…®r paŇčaindta out naaŇčg…®ra larua maw…®t…®kat 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Lk 22.4, na 22.52\x*Karica Pitaapa Ionna meikramta…®rmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca mbopatna kamb topca eacrinan mbuŇča, taup ndamta…®r ndeidapa, Sadisina tumbunna ramta…®r ndeidapa, RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikna ŇčginaŇča morena lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanap, mina muruŇča maniŇč ndambuŇč mak…®pat.\f + \fr 4:1 \ft RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca ŇčginaŇča morena lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan, anna ma taup ndamoot ian. Na ma an Liwaina ramta…®ra RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikmo, piraŇčna aiŇča morenanmo ma minmo bubuocrena.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Mt 22.23, na Up 23.8\x*Mina gaind ndamŇčiatna, maniŇča meikramta…®rmo gainda riptiatna, Iesusa menaca mutocatnanna ma mac nda maŇčgepri, na an menaca mutocrena meikramta…®ra mina Iesusa mac nda Ňčgepatna kirara mitoco, aind mac nda Ňčgepnande.\f + \fr 4:2 \ft Sadisinanda mina tumbun ian, na Karaisna m…®nna mina i aniacapa gargarap. Na mina T…®p Wand…®kna gagraca raŇčgairena, aintik mina an timbigta kap bagarna timbigta kapna moca mba g…®wac r…®pacrena. Na mina ndeida taup ndamta…®r. Na mina ndeid toco taup ndamta…®r paŇčaind ndeacrena, na ndeida t…®pemb wandik tamŇčina ramta…®r ndeacrena. Na an Sadisina tumbunna mina memenacna ramta…®rmo, mac nda ŇčgeŇčgepca mina mba r…®pacrenan, na mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčerŇčgaurmo eteaca mina mba r…®pacrenanapa, mina Ramoot Mb…®k motoco eteaca mba r…®pacrenan.\f* Aintik mina maniŇčmo nikembkatacarica,  
\v 3 mina Ňčgepca maniŇčmo utiŇčga, maniŇčna mbopatna kambca ritri waparac ndopca moatnanna, ra maiatna mbatca, mina maniŇčmo kac Ňčgoreacna inik naaŇčg…®ra mbukca t…®Ňč kaptikica leaca t…®kcamacariat. Na Ňčorapmbai te, mina maniŇčna kambca waracnande.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Up 2.41\x*Na an meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca, maniŇčna mbopatna kam wembaŇč laŇča waraca, Iesusa r…®pacatna. Na ramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 5,000na m…®n malaruat. 
\s1 Mina Pitaapa Ion mbaniŇčmo ninik waŇčgorapna ramta…®rta lamn…®ac Ňčgout naaŇčg…®ra larua maw…®t…®kat 
\p  
\v 5 Karica kabena ra mbuŇča Iudana ramta…®r paŇčaindapa, minmo outmbaica taŇčrina ramta…®r paŇčaindapa, Iudana t…®pemb wandik tamŇčirena ramta…®rap, mina muruŇča Ierusalem mapuniat.\f + \fr 4:5 \ft Na an puniatna ramta…®ra anna Iudananta ninik waŇčgor. Na mina aiŇča mina Iudana meikramta…®rta mbibiracapa, eteac wandoŇčairena.\f* 
\v 6 Ri, taup ndamoot paŇčan aniac, Anasapa mana barna taup ndamta…®ra an mak…®pat, na an ramta…®ra ande, Kaiapasapa, Ionapa Aleksanderap, na mina barna taup ndamta…®rta tumbunna ramta…®r ndeidap, mina muruŇč nak…®pca punica maica.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Mt 21.23, na Up 7.27\x*Karica mina an up aŇčg…®rena ramootniŇč, Pitaapa Ionmo, aŇčg…®ra larua an ramta…®r paŇčaindta lamnik Ňčgoutta w…®t…®kca, mina maniŇčmo aind madigiat, ‚ÄúOŇčgo titocna gargar aŇčg…®ca, an reikmo ainda moca taŇčrenan? OŇčgo mandaina i mbuŇča ainda moca mbopca taŇčrenan, a?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Mt 10.19-20\x*Ri, Pitamo ŇäeroŇč Ratta mbukca m…®nna t…®kca ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe IsraelnaŇčgepta ramta…®r anikapa ramta…®r paŇčaind,  
\v 9 ne mandeaca gan aŇčga otacapekna or Ňčgoreacna ramootna digia, anna landamŇči aŇčg…®na morena. Ne ndorimo mana landamŇči aŇčg…®na moca, ma tida moapeke ma laŇča moapekna.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Up 2.24, na 3.6, na 3.13-16\x*Aind, nenapa Israelnanda, ne muruŇčcamiŇča gaind Ňčgoin ndamŇči, gan or Ňčgoreacna ramoot, ma Nasaretna ramoot Iesus Karaisna i mbuŇča ma laŇč mamori, mandeaca ma nena meacramoot muruŇčna lamn…®acmo, ma Ňčgepca w…®t…®katna. Na an ramoot Iesus, ne manmo aŇčg…®ra ik nakeraca ma menacatnanna, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo mac nda mukca t…®kca moa maŇčgepri.\f + \fr 4:10 \ft Na an ninik waŇčgor, mina ndori, Pailatmo Iesusa mo menacna kam ndopatna. Luk sapta 22 wes 66 taŇčca sapta 23 wes 5na inikca wat. Na Iesusa menacri, mina meikramta…®rmo mana r…®t…®paca mina mba toŇčgori.\f* 
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Ňäap 118.22, na Ais 28.16, na Mt 21.42\x*Na an ramoot Iesus ma kaca morena wautna wit ian, na an wautna witta kaca morena ramta…®ra anmo Ňčgoreac ndopca aŇčg…®ra roumbmbai nakecarica eacrena wautta, mandeaca ma kacna witta moca paŇčanmbaia w…®t…®kca gagraca maeacreke.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Mt 1.21, na Up 10.43\x*Na ai mac nda aŇčtaŇčg…®na ramoot ian Ňčgocor. WanaiŇč Ňčgoin. An ramootta Iesus niŇčgik, RaraŇč Aetaniaca mamo babuatna, man niŇčgik, ma ndo ai mac nda aŇčg…®nande. Mana i mbuŇča aia gan tiacarpaikna meacramootta, muruŇča mataui eacna m…®n.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 13 Ainda moca ramta…®r paŇčainda malamŇčiat, Pitaapa Ion mbaniŇča landamŇči aŇčg…®rena taup ianna taŇčga anna ripti ianna aŇčg…® Ňčgocor, aintik maniŇča landamŇčiar kocorta ramootniŇč. Na mina watri, maniŇča rugutta mo Ňčgocor, maniŇčna mboprina kambca gargar Ňčgoin, ri, mina tamtam ndamŇčia taŇčga malamŇčiat. Ňägaua maniŇča Iesusap eacrina ramootniŇč.  
\v 14 Ri, mina wattatnanna, an moa laŇča moatna ramootta Pitaapa Ionap w…®t…®kca eacri. Na mina maniŇčmo nda ruti, mbopna kamb kocor. 
\p  
\v 15 Ainda moca an ramta…®r paŇčainda maniŇčmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúOŇčgo gan kambca ritri waparacrena kacna inik t…®kcarica raekmbai pac laruca lambi.‚ÄĚ Aindopca maniŇča taŇčgatke. Mina kam leaca aind mambopat,  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt In 11.47, na Up 3.9-10\x*‚ÄúAia an ramootniŇčmo tida t…®ki moit? ManiŇča Ňčgagatrac ianna Ierusalemma t…®kca moa laruapekke, meikramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇča anna watta mamairi, na aia minmo wawri mbopna towanaiŇč.  
\v 17 Ainda moca an kammo, Ňčarikca meikramta…®r muruŇča warac nari. Aintik aia maniŇčmo gagra mbopca maniŇča kai kabena meikramta…®rmo Iesusna i mbuŇča reikta kambca kai mac nini mbopi taŇč teac, kari Ňčgoin ndacari.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Up 5.28, na 5.40\x*Karica mina maniŇčmo aca k…®pca maniŇčmo wand…®k mat…®kat, oŇčgo kai Iesusna i mbuŇča meikramta…®rmo an reikta kambca kai riptica mbop teac. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt Up 5.29\x*Ri, Pitaapa Ion, maniŇča mina kammo gainda nda rutica mambopat, ‚ÄúNe titoc ndamŇčire, titna t…®p kirara ndo RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®acmo laŇč ndaruit? AŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam mbarac naki, co, aŇčga nena kam mbaracit, ki? Ne ndori an kamniŇčmo ritrica wat.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 4:20 \xt Up 1.8, na 22.15, na 1 Io 1.1-3\x*Na aŇčga mba mac karitndai, aŇčga ndoniŇč watri, waracrina reikta kambca, aŇčga memetmbac ndopca taŇčraŇčnande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 21-22 Karica ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®ra maniŇčmo kabena kam gargar mbuŇča mac tagagarica mbopacarica, mina meikramta…®r tarica rugut mocarica mina maniŇčmo wattacarica maniŇča mataŇčgat. Na an ramoot, maniŇča man mbuŇča Ňčgagatraca moatna ramoot, mana guiarpaika 40na m…®n mbuŇč, ma an or Ňčgoreacna roumbap eaca k…®pca guiarpaika 40na m…®nna t…®katke, maniŇča manmo moa laŇča moatna. Ri, meikramta…®ra an RaraŇč Aetaniacna moapekna Ňčgagatraca watca, mina muruŇč Ňčgoinna mana i aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepatke, na an ramta…®r paŇčainda maniŇča t…®ki mona taupembtake, moa tambacarica toawanaiŇč. 
\s1 Mina mbendeica gargar aŇčg…®ca Iesusna moatna reikta kam ndopna moca mambendeiat 
\p  
\v 23 Karica ninik waŇčgorapna ramta…®ra, Pitaapa Ionmo watcariatke, maniŇča nda taŇčga ndoniŇčna tumbun ndambuŇč ndaruca. ManiŇča minmo taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindapa, ramta…®r paŇčaind mbopatna kambca, minmo an maniniat.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 4:24 \xt NA 20.11, na Nei 9.6, na Ňäap 146.6\x*Ri, mina muruŇča waraca maica, karica mina Ňčgepca aŇčg…®ra iro kabea t…®kca RaraŇč Aetaniacmo gaind mambendeiat, ‚ÄúGagrirta Kacoot Aniac, u riac tamuŇčapa tiacarpaikapa, macaitapa min nambat ndeacrena reikca un moatna.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 4:25 \xt Ňäap 2.1-2\x*Na aina nicau Dewit, ma una aiŇčna ramoot, atua ŇäeroŇč Ratta, iro neaŇčga ma kam ianmo gaindopatna, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄėKaina moca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇča 
\q2 muruŇča nikemb katreke? 
\q1 Na kaina moca an meikramta…®ra 
\q2 t…®pemb Ňčgorikca mona moca 
\q3 anna kamma wanaiŇča leacrena? 
\q1  
\v 26 Na gan tiacarpaik ndeacrena gagrirta ramta…®r paŇčainda 
\q2 ruŇčna kocroca eacreke. 
\q1 Mina ramta…®r paŇčainda muruŇč naaŇčg…®ra punica, 
\q2 RaraŇč Aetanaic Kacootapa mana babuca mbag…®rica 
\q3 ndona meikramta…®r mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot, 
\q3 mina maniŇčmo ruŇčna moca.‚Äô 
\b  
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Mt 27.1-2, na Mk 15.1, na Lk 23.1, na 23.7-11, na In 18.28-29, na Up 3.13\x*‚ÄúAnna gidik Ňčgoin, aintik Erotapa Pontius Pailatap, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčapa Israelnandap, mina muruŇča an auŇč aniac Ierusalemma punica Iesusa mo menacna moca lambirina, an aiŇčna ramoot Iesus, ma una aiŇčna ramoot rat, atua u mamo ndona aiŇča mona moca larapacatna ramoot.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 4:28 \xt Up 2.23, na 3.18\x* Na mina ainda moatna reikca anna mina una iroapa toŇčtoŇč niŇčgikca raŇčgairena. Una gargar mbuŇča atu Ňčgoinna u kam leacatna, an reikmo mo laru ndopatna.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Up 9.27, na 13.46, na 19.8, na Epe 6.19\x*Aintik RaraŇč Aetaniac Kacoot, u mandeaca lamŇčirina mina mboprena kambca, anna mina aimo moi nanambina ndoprenanna, u aimo una mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ramta…®rmo otac. Te, aia mba nanambitndai, aia una kam wembaŇč laŇčna kam ndopna moca paŇčanmbaia mbukraŇčnande.  
\v 30 Te, u ndona gargarmo neaŇč te, meikramta…®rmo, mo laŇča monande, u Iesusna i mbuŇča Ňčgagatracara moi laruraŇč te, mina tamtam ndamŇčiraŇčnandet, ma una aiŇčna ramoot, rat Ňčgoin!‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 4:31 \xt Up 2.4, na 4.29, na 16.26\x*Mina mbendeia maiatke, mina punica eacrina kaca warak mamoat, ri, ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo mbukca lacakeca, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kam aniaca t…®kca mawiwitiat, na mina mba nanambiatke. 
\s1 Meacramoota muruŇča kabena meacramootmo ndiarna t…®pca mo 
\p  
\v 32 \x - \xo 4:32 \xt Up 2.44-45, na 2 Ko 13.11, na 1 Pi 3.8\x*Meikramta…®ra muruŇča Iesusa r…®paceknanna, mina iroar inkara wewettar laiŇč ndeac te, iro kabe aŇčg…®ca iro landamŇči kabe Ňčgoin ndeac. Te, mina kabe, kabena reikca mina ianna an reik mbatca gainda mba lamŇčitndai, an reiki anna mannan. WanaiŇč. Mina gaind ndamŇčinande, an reikca anna mina muruŇčcamiŇčnan.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 4:33 \xt Up 1.8, na 1.22, na 2.45-47\x*Ri, Kacoot Iesusna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, mana nda ŇčgeŇčgepna kam wiwitiri, an kam minanna gargar bagaraniacap. Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniaca min Ňčgopotacna toŇčtoŇč bagaraniacap. Aintik ma minmo muruŇčcamiŇčmo reik laiŇčga mataua morena.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 4:34 \xt Up 2.45\x*Ainda mori, an meikramta…®rta ianna mba amna reac nake, mba koteteri. Mina mandaia ndorita pitrikapnan, co kaikapnan, mina muruŇča an reikmo aŇčg…®ra mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca t…®kca mina oikca aŇčg…®r te, minmo anna kituknduk neaŇč te. Mina an kitukndukar aŇčg…®ra k…®pca,  
\v 35 up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo neaŇč te. Mina an kitukndukar aŇčg…®ca, an koteterina meikramta…®rmo mabiŇčaiat. 
\p  
\v 36 \x - \xo 4:36 \xt Up 11.22-26, na 13.2-3\x*Ri, mina inik ndeacrina ramoot ianna, mana ia Iosep. Ma Liwainanta ian, ma Saiprus mutna ramoot. Na up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra mana i Iosep Ňčgetrikica, manmo i Banambas mat…®kat. Na an i Banambas, mana m…®n…®Ňča gan ina kirar, ‚ÄúIroa moa Gagararena Ramoot.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 Ma ndona pitrik waŇč emtemmo mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca t…®kca ramoot ianna oikatna mbatca, ma an kitukndukar aŇčg…®a k…®pca up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta par mat…®kat. 
\c 5  
\s1 Ananaiasapa Sapaira maniŇča ndoniŇčmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca towai ndopca matowaiat 
\p  
\v 1 Ramoot ian ma toco anna inik ndeacrenanna, mana ia Ananaias, na mana meacna ia Sapaira. Na maniŇča ndoniŇčna pitrik waŇč emtemmo, mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca t…®kca ramoot ianna oikri.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Up 4.34-37\x*Na an kitukndukarta kitukndukna t…®pca Ananaiasa paruca ndo t…®p aŇčg…®racariatke. Na mana meac Sapaira, mana kaŇčgaitta ainda moatna t…®p kirara, ma toco ma lamŇčirina. Ri, Ananaiasa paruca t…®p niŇčgik aŇčg…®rca k…®pca up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo maneaŇčgat.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 5:3 \xt TW 23.21, na Lk 22.3, na In 13.2\x*Ri, Pita manmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAnanaias, u tida mona moca Ramoot Mb…®kmo wattacarica ma unmo towairina, na u mana kamma waraca ma una iro inikca mbukca, u ŇäeroŇč Ratmo paruapekna, na u ndona pitrik waŇčna kitukndukar aŇčg…®ca, ndo t…®p aŇčg…®apekna?  
\v 4 Ňägaua an pitrik waŇča anna unan, na u ndona toŇčtoŇč mbuŇča mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca t…®kca kabena ramootta unanmo oikrico, u ndona an pitrik waŇčna kitukndukarmo u ndona toŇčtoŇčna reikmo u an mbuŇča mo mbe. Na tida mona moca u an iro Ňčgoreac aŇčg…®ca ainda moapekna? U ndomo ramoot wanaiŇč ianna paru ndopca paruapeknanna, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin, u RaraŇč Aetaniac Ňčgoin maparuca.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Ananaiasa an kam mbaraca ma anduna mamenacat. Na meikramta…®ra Ananaias ndaruatna reikta kam wembaŇč mbaraca, mina kocnaia rugdar moamacariat.  
\v 6 Ri, nuik Ňčgaibca k…®pca mana wa…®rmo raraŇčit mbuŇča tamaia maica, mana wa…®rmo aŇčg…®ra taŇčga mamutocat. 
\p  
\v 7 Na eaca k…®dr…®k rocot Ňčgoinna wanaiŇč, Ananaiasna meaca k…®pca mambukat. Ma ndona kaŇčgait ndaruatna reaca, ma lamŇči Ňčgocor.  
\v 8 Ri, Pita manmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúU aukmo mbop, oŇčna pitrik waŇč emtemna kitukndukca an niŇčgik, ki?‚ÄĚ Ri, mana meaca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNat co, anna gidik.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 Ri, Pita manmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúKaica oŇčgo kam leaca ndoniŇč ndopca maica Kacootna ŇäeroŇčmo towaina moca oŇčgo paruapekna? U warac! Una kaŇčgaitna wa…®r mutocrina nuik Ňčgaibca, monde t…®Ňč kam mambukreke. Mina una wa…®r motocmo aŇčg…®ri taŇčnande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Ri, an meaca Pitana or k…®t…®mma anduna kocnaia menaca mat…®kat. Na an nuik Ňčgaibca k…®pca mbukca wattatnanna, ma menaca t…®kca eacri, mina watca mana wa…®rmo aŇčg…®a larua mana kaŇčgaitna muk roumb mamutocat.  
\v 11 Ri, Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunapa raekmbai ndeacrena meikramta…®rap, mina an laruatna reikta kamb mbaraca, mina muruŇča kocnaia rugdar moamacariat. 
\s1 Up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra titocna Ňčgagatracara moa larurena 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Up 2.43, na 4.32, na 14.3, na Ro 15.19, na 2 Ko 12.12\x*Karica up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra ainta Ňčgagatracarmo, meikramta…®rta k…®dr…®kca t…®kca mori. Na meikramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇč Ňčgoinna Kacootta r…®paca, mina muruŇča iro kabe aŇčg…®ca, mina muruŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca, Solomonna wacraet mapuniat.  
\v 13 Ri, mina an inik ndeac Ňčgocorta meikramta…®ra, mina moatna reik mbatca mina iremb aŇčg…®ra maŇčgepat. Na mina ndoria, mina rugdar mocarica, ainda moca mina, an mina inikca k…®pi mbuk Ňčgocor.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Up 2.41, na 21.20\x*Na an meikramta…®r w…®t aniac Ňčgoinna, mina Iesusna kam mbaraca r…®paca, mina k…®pca mana r…®t…®pacna tumbunnandap mambukat. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Mt 9.21, na 14.36, na Up 19.12\x*Ri, an meikramta…®ra up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r morina Ňčgagatracara watarapaca. Ainda moca mina ndorita roumbbebta meikramta…®rmo aŇčg…®ra larua k…®pca, Pitana taŇčrena taupembmo mbimbitamar keca, roumbbebta meikramta…®rmo an mameracri. Mina lamŇčirina Pita an ndiŇč nak…®p te, ra manmo aŇčg…® te, mana ninikna papaca minmo aŇčg…®rnande.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Mk 6.56, na Up 19.11-12\x*Na Ierusalem auŇč aniaca rambuŇčaia eacrina auŇčembta meikramta…®r, mitoca k…®pca up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo watrina. Aintik mitoco ndorita roumbbebta meikramta…®rapa, ŇčerŇčgaur Ňčgorikca mbukca moa ŇčaŇčaorina meikramta…®rap aŇčg…®a k…®patnanna, an meikramta…®ra mina muruŇčcamiŇča laiŇč mamoat. 
\s1 Iudiana ramta…®r paŇčainda up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca moatna 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Up 4.1-2, na 4.6\x*Karica taup ndamoot paŇčan aniacapa mina Sadisina tumbunna aikorta ramta…®rap, mina an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta moatna reikca, watca mina minmo titkara morina.  
\v 18 Mina Ňčgepca an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo, utiŇčca aŇčg…®ra taŇčga t…®p Ňčgoreaca morina meikramta…®r eacrina, kac Ňčgoreacna inikna t…®Ňč gootca, up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo, minap an inik kabea t…®kca, t…®Ňč kaptiki leaca t…®kcamacariat.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Up 12.7-10, na 16.26\x*Na eaca mouŇčmbai mbuŇča Kacootna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna k…®pca kac Ňčgoreacna t…®Ňč gootca minmo aŇčg…®ra laruca raekca t…®kca, minmo gaindopatna,  
\v 20 ‚ÄúNe taŇčca RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca, anna w…®t…®kca meikramta…®rmo iarwar ndeteacna watna kam an wiwiti mbop.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Karica up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, an kam mbaraca maiatna mbatca, ŇčaŇčarmuŇč Ňčgoinna mina taŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca meikramta…®rmo, an kam riptica eacrina. 
\p Na taup ndamoot paŇčan aniacapa mana aikorap, mina kam neaŇčga taŇčga, IsraelnaŇčgepta ramta…®r paŇčaindmo muruŇča k…®p te, mina ninikar waŇčgorta tumbunna mona. Mina kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morena piriŇčmo mbopca taŇčga, minmo up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r aŇčg…® k…®pna moca.  
\v 22 Karica piriŇčga taŇčga kac Ňčgoreacna t…®Ňč gootca wattatnanna, up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra an inikca eac Ňčgocor. Ri, mina mac nda taŇčga ramta…®r paŇčaindta tumbunmo gaind mambopat,  
\v 23 ‚ÄúAia watri mina an kac Ňčgoreacna t…®Ňčmo kaptiki leaca maica, mina anna ŇčginaŇča moa auŇč raruca, ŇčaŇčarmuŇča aia kacna t…®Ňč gootca wattatnanna, an inikca meikramta…®r kocor koind.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 Na RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca aiŇča morena piriŇčta ramta…®rta ramoot paŇčanapa taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindap, mina an kam mbaraca tamtam ndamŇčiri, aindopca, ‚ÄúAn ramta…®ra titoca taŇčgapek? Na kaina reaca ndo laruit?‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Ri, ramoot ianna laruca, minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe warac! An ramta…®ra, ne minmo aŇčg…®rca kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca eacrenanna, mandeaca mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca, w…®t…®kca meikramta…®rmo kam mariptireke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 \x - \xo 5:26 \xt Mt 14.5, na 21.26\x*Ainda moca mina outmbai ndeacrena piriŇčta ramoot paŇčanapa, piriŇčgap, mina taŇčga up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo utiŇčga laŇčan naaŇčg…®ra mak…®pri, na mina minmo kaega mba mori. Mina rugdar moca, Ňčarikca meikramta…®ra minmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňč narica. 
\s1 Up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, mina ninik waŇčgorapna ramta…®rap mbop nake, mba nanambiatke 
\p  
\v 27 Ri, piriŇčga an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo, ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®rta out naaŇčg…®ra larua w…®t…®katke. Na taup ndamoot paŇčan aniaca minmo gaindopatna,  
\v 28 \x - \xo 5:28 \xt Mt 27.25, na Up 2.23, na 2.36, na 4.18, na 7.52\x*‚ÄúAia nemo an ramootna i mbuŇča moatna reikta nininimo, an meikramta…®ra ripti narica, anna wand…®k t…®katna. Na ne an kammo, aimo an ramootta r…®Ňč memenac ndopca aimo anna tuk t…®kca. Na ne meikramta…®rmo an kamma anduna riptica mbopca mataŇčri. Na Ierusalemna inikna meikramta…®ra, an kammo kocnaia waraca mamaiat.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 29 \x - \xo 5:29 \xt Up 4.19\x*Ri, Pitaapa up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, mina mana kammo nda rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAia RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam niŇčgikca raŇčgairaŇčnande. Aia ramoot ianna kamma mba waraca raŇčgaiitndai.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 5:30 \xt Up 3.15, na 10.39, na 13.29, na Gal 3.13, na 1 Pi 2.24\x*Ne Iesusmo ik naaŇčg…®ra keraca manmo r…®Ňčga menacatke, aina nicarta RaraŇč Aetaniac tamuŇčnan, manmo mac nda moa maŇčgepat.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 5:31 \xt Up 2.33-34, na 3.15, na Epe 1.20, na Pil 2.9, na Ib 2.10, na 12.2\x*Mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo aŇčg…®ra gaca, manmo aŇčg…®ra ndona par umbai naaŇčg…®ra mbiraca maeacreke. Ma ndo aina ramoot paŇčan, na ma ndo ai mac nda aŇčg…®na aiŇč ndeacnande, te, ma ndo aimo IsraelnaŇčgepmo otaca aimo moi iroar inkar Ňčgetriki te, aina t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukarmo moi kecarinandet.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 5:32 \xt In 15.26-27, na Up 1.8, na 2.4, na 10.44\x*An reikca aia RaraŇč Aetaniaca moatnanna watta maica. Ainda moca aia an reikta kambca ndorimo wiwitirena. Na ŇäeroŇč Rat toco an reikta kamb kaukica wiwitirena. Na RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma meikramta…®ra mana kam mbaracrenan, na raŇčgairenanmo, ma ŇäeroŇč Rat neaŇčrena.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Gamaliela aindopatna, ne ninik waŇč potaca eacrena ramta…®r, ne up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo laŇčanna t…®ki mo 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 5:33 \xt Up 2.37, na 7.54\x*An ninikar waŇčgorta ramta…®ra Pitana mbopatna kamb mbaraca, mina nikembkatca Ňčgocraica, ndorimo up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra r…®Ňč menacna kam pia mboprina.  
\v 34 Ri, Parisiarta ninik waŇčna ramoot ian, ma maw…®t…®kat, mana ia Gamaliel. Ma Iudana t…®pemb wandik tamŇčirena ramoot, ainda moca meikramta…®ra manmo torirena. Ri, ma ramta…®rmo ma gaindopatna, ne up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo raek naaŇčg…® laruca tekemtem pac eac.\f + \fr 5:34 \ft Pola Iesusmo r…®pac Ňčgocor ndeacrina k…®dr…®kca, Gamaliela ma mana riripti. Na Iesusna Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇčna Nininina Timbigta Kap sapta 22 wes 3na inikca wat.\f* 
\v 35 Mina minmo aŇčg…®ra larua maiatna mbatca, Gamaliela ndona aiŇč kabena ninikar waŇčgormo, gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe IsraelnaŇčgepta ramta…®r, ne an ramta…®rmo reac ianna kai mo teac, ndori matau lamŇči.  
\v 36 \x - \xo 5:36 \xt Up 21.38\x*Na ne malamŇčireke, k…®dr…®k rocot Ňčgoinna wanaiŇč, Teudas ma Ňčgepca gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAku ramoot paŇčan, aku irembta ramoot.‚Äô Na ma aindopatke, mana kamb mbaraca raŇčgaiatna meikramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a maica 400na m…®n aŇčg…®atke. Mina Romna ramoot paŇčan aniaca aind mbatatke, manmo moca ma menacatke, mana r…®paca raŇčgairina meikramta…®ra tamtam nak…®pacariatke, mina an aiŇča andua watamacariat.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 5:37 \xt Lk 2.1-2\x*Ri, iŇčmbaia mina Romna ramoot paŇčan aniaca, meikramta…®rta iremb aŇčg…®ri, Galilina ramoot Iudas, ma an meikramta…®rta iroara moa Ňčgetrikica mina Ňčgepca mana raŇčgaica. Mina an ramoot paŇčan aniacap ruŇčca mana mo irikna moca, moatnanna, wanaiŇč. Mina mana r…®Ňčga menacatke, meikramta…®ra mana r…®paca raŇčgairinanna, mina k…®pcarica tamtamma taŇčga mamaiat.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 5:38 \xt Ais 8.10, na Mt 15.13\x*Aintik mandeaca aku nenmo gaindopnande, ne an ramta…®rmo reac ianna kai mo teac kari, ne minmo watcarica mina eac. An aiŇč, minnanna toŇčtoŇč mbuŇča mo te, ma wanaiŇč ndacarinande.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 5:39 \xt Lk 21.15, na Up 7.51, na 9.5, na 1 Ko 1.25\x*Na an aiŇča RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndo aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepca, mina anna moraŇč te, ne mo irikna m…®nna wanaiŇč. Ne ainda moraŇč te, moca ne RaraŇč Aetaniacap ipuŇčraŇč nari!‚ÄĚ 
\p Aindopatke, an ninikar waŇčgorapna ramta…®r paŇčainda Gamalielna kam mbaraca maraŇčgaiat.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 5:40 \xt Up 4.18\x*Mina up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo aca k…®pca, ramta…®rmo mbopca mina minmo piatke, minmo Iesusna i mbuŇča moatna reikta kam wiwiti narica, minmo anna wand…®k t…®kca minmo wattacarica mina mataŇčgat. \fig Mina ramootniŇčmo an t…®pna kirar mbuŇča laŇča mba pirinan|src="GW150.tif" size="col" copy="Wade" ref="5.40" \fig* 
\v 41 \x - \xo 5:41 \xt Mt 5.10-12, na 1 Pi 4.13\x*Aintik up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra an ninikar waŇčgorta ramta…®r paŇčaind t…®kcarica, laruca mina RaraŇč Aetaniacmo toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin, ma lamŇčirina mina m…®n tik, mina Iesusna i mbuŇča mina kam numbirtan aŇčg…®nande.  
\v 42 \x - \xo 5:42 \xt Up 9.22, na 17.3\x*Na memetmbaca ra kabe, kabea mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca taŇčreke, na meikramta…®rta kaik toco taŇčrenanna, mina minmo mimitpac neaŇčrena. Na mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇč riptinake, mba Ňčaterenanna, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin, mina gaind Ňčgoin ndoprena, ‚ÄúGade gan ramoot Iesus, RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot.‚ÄĚ 
\c 6  
\s1 Mina ramta…®r parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇčmo up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r Ňčgotac ndopca larapacatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Up 2.41, na 4.35, na 5.14, na 9.29\x*An m…®nna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta ndunduna ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a w…®t aniac Ňčgoin ndaruca, Girikna kam mbuŇč ndoprina r…®pacrena tumbunnanda, mina Ňčgepca an Aramna kam mbuŇč ndoprina, r…®pacrena tumbunandmo konmbop repmbopca moca minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe memetmbaca an amta reik kocortacarica koteterena meikramta…®rmo otacreke, na aina meik koinmbarmo mba otacrenanna.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 6:1 \ft Na Aramna kamma anna Iudiana pitrik waŇčapa, Galilina pitrik waŇčna meikramta…®rta auŇčna kam. Na ma Iburuna kamna kirar toc.\f* 
\v 2 Ainda moca an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena tumbunna k…®pca puniatna meikramta…®rmo aca k…®pca tumbunna t…®kca minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAia gan RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kam wiwitirena aiŇč an t…®kcarica meikramta…®rmo amta reikta biŇča moraŇč te, anna laŇča wanaiŇč.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt TW 1.13, na Up 1.21, na 16.2, na 1 Ti 3.7\x*Aintik min laiplacar, ne ndorita inikna ramta…®r parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇčna ramta…®r ndepikca watca, mina nena inik ndeacreke, na mina t…®p Ňčgoreaca mo Ňčgocorta ramta…®r, na minmo ŇäeroŇč Rat mbukca minmo landamŇči laŇč neaŇčga mina t…®pemb kirarir laiŇčga morena, ainta ramta…®r ndepikca watca minmo an aiŇč neaŇč.  
\v 4 Te, aia ndorimo, memetmbaca RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mbendei te, mana kam laŇč wiwitinande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Up 8.5\x*Ainda moca meikramta…®ra an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r mbopatna kamb mbaraca, mina toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Ainda moca mina Stipen lamarapacat, ma r…®t…®pac aniacapa ŇäeroŇč Rat mbukca eacrina ramoot. Na mina kabena ramta…®r ndepikap larapacatna ramta…®ra, Pilip, na Pirokorus, na Nikanor, na Timon, na Parmenas, na Nikolas. Na Nikolas tikca ma Antiokna ramoot ian, na ma Iudana ramootta wanaiŇč, ma Iudananta r…®pacrena r…®t…®paca r…®paca, mina raŇčgaica mina r…®t…®pacna tumbunna inik ndeacrina.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Up 13.3, na 14.23\x*Karica mina an ramta…®rpaikmo larapaca maica, minmo aŇčg…®ra taŇčga up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rta out naaŇčg…®ra larua w…®t…®kca. An up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rpaikca ndorita pa…®ra mina paŇčaind tambatta t…®kca, RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mambendeiat, minmo an aiŇč aŇčg…®ca mona moca larapacatna. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt In 12.42, na Up 2.41, na 12.24, na 16.5, na Kol 1.6\x*Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamma tamtamma taŇčri, na Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena tumbunna meikramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a an Ierusalemna inikca w…®t aniac muruŇč malaruat. Ri, an taup ndamta…®r w…®t aniaca RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamma waraca mitoco mar…®pacat. 
\s1 IudanaŇčgepca Stipenmo aŇčg…®ra ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®rta par mat…®kat 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Up 2.43\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca Stipenmo opotac bagaraniac Ňčgoin neaŇčga, ma gargar aniac aŇčg…®ca, ainda moca ma ainta Ňčgagatracar anikmo meikramta…®rta r…®kca t…®kca mamoat.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Ri, ramta…®r ndeida Ňčgepca Stipenap maipuŇčgat. An ramta…®r tikca, mina Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacna tumbunnan, na an tumbunna ia mina gaind Ňčgacrina, aia k…®k…®pna wiwitta wanaiŇč. Na an ramta…®r tikca, mina Sairini auŇčapa Aleksandria auŇčnan, na ramta…®r ndeid toco, an pitrik aniacniŇčnan Silisiaapa Esianan.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Ais 54.17, na Lk 21.15, na Up 5.39\x*Na ŇäeroŇč Ratta Stipenmo iro landamŇči laŇč Ňčgoin neaŇčga, ri, an ramta…®ra Stipenna mbopekna kamb gagrar anikca k…®taci irikna m…®nna wanaiŇč.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Mt 26.59-61\x*Ainda moca an ramta…®r, mina iŇčgoroci taŇčca ramta…®r ndeidmo wai aoca, minmo paparuna kamb Ňčgorikmo Stipen mbombop ndopca aindopatna, ‚ÄúAia waracatke, Stipenna Mosesapa RaraŇč Aetaniacmo peperena kamb Ňčgorik ndoprena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Mina ndorimo an paparuna kam mbuŇča an meikramta…®rapa, mina outmbaica taŇčrena ramta…®rapa, mina Iudana t…®pemb wandik tamŇčirena ramta…®rap, mina iroara r…®Ňčga minmo Stipen ŇčgutiŇčga aŇčg…®ri taŇčca ninikar waŇčgorta ramta…®rta para t…®kna moca, an kam mbuŇča ainda paruca Stipenmo aŇčg…®rca taŇčga ninikar waŇčgorta out maw…®t…®kat.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Ier 26.11\x*Ri, mina ramta…®r ndeidmo aŇčg…®a laruca. An ramta…®ra mina paparuna kammo gaindoprina, ‚ÄúMemetmbaca gan ramootta RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacmo peperena kam ndoprena, na T…®p Wand…®k motocmo ma peperena kam Ňčgoreac ndoprena.  
\v 14 Aia waracatke, ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAn Nasaretna ramoot Iesus, ma an RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacmo moi Ňčgocrai te, atua Mosesa aimo neaŇčgatna t…®pembca, ma moi Ňčgetriki mainande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 Ri, an ritri waparacrena an inikca mbiraca eacrina ninikar waŇčgorta ramta…®ra, an kambca waraca, mina Ňčgepca Stipenna inpaŇčanna watta taŇčgatnanna, mana inpaŇčanna anna ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna inpaŇčan ian mbatat toc, ma wanaiŇč, ma metacri. 
\c 7  
\s1 Stipenna an ninik waŇčna ramootmo an kamma mbopca malaruat 
\p  
\v 1 Karica taup ndamoot paŇčan aniaca Stipenmo gaind madigiat, ‚ÄúAn kambca ramta…®ra unmo mboprena kambca, anna gidkar, ki, wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 \x - \xo 7:2 \xt RL 11.31\x*\x - \xo 7:2 \xt RL 12.1\x*Ri, ma rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúMin laiplacarapa ater, ne warac. Atua aina nicau Abraamma Mesopotemiana pitrikna inik ndeacrina m…®nna, Abraamma Earan auŇča taŇč Ňčgocor ndeacri mbuŇča. TamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma ndona memetacna tac aniacapa gargar bagaraniacapna ramoot, ma man ndambuŇč malaruat.  
\v 3 Karica RaraŇč Aetaniaca Abraammo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU ndona pitrikapa ndona laiplacarmo t…®kcarica. Na u Ňčgepca kabena pitrikca taŇč, na an pitrik aku unmo wandacnande.‚Äô  
\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4 \xt RL 11.31, na 12.4\x*Aintik Abraamma Kaldiananta pitrik t…®kcarica, ma Ňčgepca Earan auŇč mataŇčgat. Na ma an ndeacrina m…®nna, mana aetta menacatke, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo mandaca, k…®pca mandeaca ne anna mbiraca eacrena pitrikca ma an mambiracat.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt RL 12.7, na 13.15, na 15.3, na 15.18, na 17.8, na 26.3, na 48.4, na TW 2.5\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca an pitrikna emtemmo mba kataca Abraammo mba neaŇčga ma ndona Ňčgomornandap eacnake, mba mbopatke. Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca gaindopatna, iŇčmbai ecte, ma an pitrikmo Abraamapa mana mombonikmo an pitrik neaŇčna, an pitrikca minan Ňčgoin ndeacnande. RaraŇč Aetaniaca an kam ndopatna m…®n mbuŇča, Abraamma mombonik kocor ndeacrina m…®n mbuŇč ndopatna kam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6 \xt RL 15.16, na NA 12.40, na Gal 3.17\x*\x - \xo 7:6 \xt RL 15.13-14\x*Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniaca Abraammo gaindopatna, una mombonik r…®mbnarapa Ňčgamrira taŇčca kabena pitrik ndeac te, anna meikramta…®ra minmo t…®pemb Ňčgorikca monande, na mina minapmo guiarpaika 400na m…®n ndeac te, mina minmo mbaiŇčna aiŇčir anik kamnder neaŇči moraŇčnande.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 7:7 \xt NA 3.12\x*Na ainda moekna ramta…®rmo, iŇčmbaia aku mina nenmo ainda morena t…®pemb kirarirta ritri waparaca, aku monande. Na iŇčmbaia an meikramta…®rta mombonikca an pitrik t…®kcarica mina gan auŇč nda k…®pca an ndeac te, mina aukmo anna t…®ki mbendeiraŇčnande.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt RL 17.10-14, na 21.2-4, na 25.26, na 29.31‚ÄĒ35.18\x*Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniaca Abraammo kam leaca gaindopatna, u tikiŇčit katac, an Ňčgagatraca RaraŇč Aetaniaca Abraamma neaŇčgatna. Te, iŇčmbaia Abraam Aisakna aet ndaruca, Aisakna raia taŇči parmbaiapa mbutremb mbonkac ndaru te, ma Aisakna tikiŇčit katacnande. Na Aisaka Iakopna aet ndaruca, na Iakopa ma aina parniŇčapa mbut mbuniŇčna nicarta aet. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 7:9 \xt RL 37.11, na 37.28, na 39.2, na 39.21\x*‚ÄúNa an nicarpaikca mina Ňčgepca ndorita lap Iosepmo titikca moca mamo t…®p laŇča mba moatke, mina Ňčgepca manmo tuomna aiŇč kamainda morena ramootta, mona moca manmo aŇčg…®ca kabena ramta…®rta para t…®kca, an ramta…®ra manmo oikca Isip naaŇčg…®a taŇčgatke. RaraŇč Aetaniaca manap maeacri.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 7:10 \xt RL 41.37-41\x*Aintik RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo otaca, mana mitkarmo moa kecarica, an m…®nna RaraŇč Aetaniaca Iosepmo landamŇčiar neaŇčga, ma Isipnanta gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Peroap mambopri. Ri, gagrirta ramoot paŇčanna Iosepna mbopatna kambca waracri, ma Iosepmo toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Ainda moca gagrirta ramoot paŇčanna manmo aŇčg…®ra Isipnanta ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®a w…®t…®kca, ma gagrirta ramoot paŇčanna kac inikna reikta ŇčginaŇč mamoat.\f + \fr 7:10 \ft Pero, ma Isipnanta gagrirta ramoot paŇčan. Na an i Pero, anna mina Isipnanta gagrirta ramta…®r paŇčainda neaŇčrena.\f* 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 7:11 \xt RL 41.54, na 42.1-2\x*‚ÄúNa iŇčmbaia nik wapatai aniaca Isipna inik ndaruatnanna, kocnaia taŇčga Kenan pitrikap aŇčg…®ca, anna meikramta…®ra muruŇča an mitik bagaraniac aŇčg…®ca eacri. Na aina nicar toco amta reik kocortacarica kocnaia kotetecarica mori.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 7:12 \xt RL 42.1-5\x*Ainda moca, Iakopa waracatnanna Isipa amta reikca eacrina kam mbaraca, ma aina nicar mbag…®rica mina out Ňčgoinna mina Isip mataŇčgat.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 7:13 \xt RL 45.1, na 45.16\x*Na iŇčmbaia mina mac taŇčgatke, Iosepa ndona lacarpitikmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄėAku Iosep.‚Äô Ri, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Pero, ma an k…®dr…®k mbuŇča ma Iosepna lacarpitikapa lapmbitac kaŇčgumkakatacmo ma watta marapacat.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 7:14 \xt RL 45.9-10, na 45.17-18, na 46.27\x*Ri, Iosepa Ňčgepca ndona aet Iakopmo ndo ndambuŇč nak…®pna moca kam ndopca taŇčga, aindopatna, ‚ÄėU k…®p te, ndona 75na m…®nna meacramootmo muruŇč naaŇčg…®ca k…®p.‚Äô  
\v 15 \x - \xo 7:15 \xt RL 46.1-7, na 49.33\x*Karica Iakopa Ňčgepca Isip Ňčgirikca an ndeaca, iŇčmbaia ma menacatke, aina nicar, mitoco muruŇča mamenacat.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 7:16 \xt RL 23.3-16, na 33.19, na 50.7-13, na Ios 24.32\x*Ri, warir minanmo, mina aŇčg…®ca mac nda taŇčga Sekem auŇčna warir t…®krena taupca t…®kca, an mamutocat. Na an warir t…®krena taupca atua Abraamma Amorna mombonikta pitrik Ňčgoikca, ma mukur mamoat.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 7:17 \xt RL 15.5, na Ňäap 105.24-25, na Up 7.5-7\x*\x - \xo 7:17 \xt NA 1.7-8\x*Karica Stipenna gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniaca ndo atua Abraammap ŇčganŇčg…®a babua mbopatna kamna kirarna rana m…®nna, maica k…®pca rambuŇčairi, IsraelnaŇčgepca Isip ndeacrinanna, mina meikramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a Ňčgepca w…®t Ňčgoinna t…®kcamacariat.  
\v 18 Ri, iŇčmbaia ramoot ianna Isipnanta gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ndaruca, ma Iosepmo, ma manmo lamŇči Ňčgocor.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 7:19 \xt NA 1.10-22\x*Na an gagrirta ramoot paŇčan, ma laruca aina meikramta…®rmo ndona paŇčan gargar mbuŇča paruca, minmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca moatna. Ma minmo mina mombonik tekirca moi menacna moca anna t…®p gargar mat…®kat. Mina minpembmo raekmbaia t…®kca, mina menacrenan.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 7:20 \xt NA 2.2, na Ib 11.23\x*Na an m…®nna Mosesmo mana aemma mana m…®ratke, ma mooŇčnuoc laŇč Ňčgoin, na RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin. Ainda moca mina manmo mana aetna kaca t…®kca raupŇčia eaca taŇčga karwira mbonkac mamoat.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 7:21 \xt NA 2.3-10\x*IŇčmbaia mina manmo aŇčg…®ra larua menacna moca raekca t…®katke, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Perona mooŇča mamo watca, manmo aŇčg…®ca ndona mooŇčnuoc Ňčgoin mamoat.  
\v 22 Ri, ma Ňčgepca Isipnanta t…®pemb kirarirta riptiar mataua aŇčg…®ra maica, mana kam up gargar aniacapa mana aiŇčir gagrar anikca momona ramoot ian malaruat. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 7:23 \xt NA 2.11-15\x*‚ÄúMaica Mosesna guiarpaikna ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 40na m…®n aŇčg…®atke, ma ndona Israelna kamkabear Ňčgokena iro ndamŇčica ma mataŇčgat.  
\v 24 Na ma taŇčga wattatnanna, Isipna ramoot ianna Israelna ramoot ianmo mo Ňčgocraina mori. Na ma aind mbatca Ňčgepca Israelna ramoot Ňčgotaca Isipna ramootmo kaega moca manap ruŇčga manmo pia mamenacat.  
\v 25 Na Moses, ma aind ndamŇčiatna, mana Israelna laiplacarmo gaind ndamŇčina moca, RaraŇč Aetaniaca auk mbuŇča t…®kca min Ňčgotaca aŇčg…®nande. Na mina ainda lamŇči Ňčgocor.  
\v 26 Na kabena ra ianna ma wattatnanna, Israelna ramootniŇča ndoniŇča ruŇčri. Na ma maniŇčna kaega mo menac ndopca, ma tawina taŇčga maniŇčmo k…®raca, aindopatna, ‚ÄėAe, oŇčgo warac, oŇčgo kalapniŇč, kaina moca oŇčgo ndoniŇčmo ainda ruŇčre?‚Äô  
\v 27 Ri, outta t…®kca kaega moa Ňčgepatna ramootta, Mosesmo Ňčgikia kecarica, aindopatna, ‚ÄėUmo mandaia ndo aina ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra larua larapacatna, na aina kambca ritri waparacna ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra w…®t…®katna?  
\v 28 U auk mac, pi, menacna mac moek ki, Ňčour Ňčgoinna u Isipna ramootta pia menacatna kirar?‚Äô  
\v 29 \x - \xo 7:29 \xt NA 2.21-22, na 18.3-4\x*Ri, Mosesa an kam mbaracatke, ma Ňčgepca k…®pcarica mataŇčgat. Na ma taŇčga Midiananta pitrikmo k…®k…®pna ramootna kirar toc ndeacrina. IŇčmbaia ma anna meac laŇčgoca, nuocna mooŇčnuocniŇča t…®kca mam…®rat.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 7:30 \xt NA 3.1-10\x*Karica Stipenna gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúMosesa eaca guiarpaika 40na m…®n maiatke, ma ramta…®r kocorta taup ianna Sainai takurna roumbca rambuŇčaia eacrina taupca taŇčga an ndeacrina. Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna, man ndambuŇčmo an ik tekernocna tac w…®w…®ra mana Ňčaikta k…®dr…®kna tacna mim inikca eacrinanna, man ndambuŇčmo larurinan.  
\v 31 Ri, Mosesa an laruatna reac mbatca, ma an reacna moca tamtam ndamŇčica. Ma ndomo matau watna moca taŇčga rambuŇčairi, RaraŇč Aetaniac Kacootta manmo gaind mambopat,  
\v 32 ‚ÄėUna nicara Abraamapa, Aisakapa, Iakopa aku mina RaraŇč Aetaniac.‚Äô Ri, Mosesa an kamma waraca dumrikica, an reaca wat narica rugut moca nanambiamacariat.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 7:33 \xt Ios 5.15\x*Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniac Kacootta manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU ndona ort…®mb…®k ŇčgapaocniŇč pituk, an pitrik umbumma u anna w…®t…®kca eacrenanna anna auknan, na aukna lamn…®acmo ma rat Ňčgoin.  
\v 34 Aku watrina, aukna meikramta…®ra Isip ndeacrenanna, Isipna meikramta…®ra, minmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca moreke, mina aereke, aku mina nananaea mawaracri. Ainda moca aku minmo Isipnanta para t…®ki, mac nda aŇčg…® ndopca anna Ňčgirikcapekna. Aintik u Ňčgepca Isipa taŇč.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 35 \x - \xo 7:35 \xt NA 2.14, na 14.11-12, na Ndu 20.16\x*Karica Stipenna gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNa outmbaica an ramoot kabe Mosesmo, IsraelnaŇčgepca mana kam mbarac narica, mina manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėUnmo mandaia ndo aina ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra larua larapacatna, na aina kambca ritri waparacna ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra w…®t…®katna?‚Äô Na an ramoot Mosesmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndo mamo ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra w…®t…®kca min mac nda aŇčg…® ndopca mandaca taŇčgatna ramoot. An ramootmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča mamo tacna kirara, raŇč inikca w…®rrina kirar mbuŇč nak…®pca manmo gargar neaŇčgatna.  
\v 36 \x - \xo 7:36 \xt NA 7.3, na 12.41, na 14.21, na 16.1, na 16.35, na Ndu 14.33, na Ňäap 105.27\x*Na Mosesa IsraelnaŇčgepmo Isipa t…®kca aŇčg…®ca mina Ňčgepca Isip t…®kcarica laruca, ma Ňčgagatracar anikapa ainta reac, reaca moa malaruri, an Isipna inikapa Macait Laupapmo, ma an reikca moca mak…®pri. Na an reik kocorta pitrik aniacmo ma guiar 40na m…®nna ma an reikca morina.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 7:37 \xt TW 18.15, na 18.18, na Mt 17.5, na Up 3.22\x*Ande an ramoot Moses, ma ndo ma IsraelnaŇčgepmo ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniaca nena barna ianmo larapacnande, na ma aukna kirar tocna ramma morena ramoot ndarunande.‚Äô  
\v 38 \x - \xo 7:38 \xt NA 19.1‚ÄĒ20.17, na TW 5.1-33, na Ais 63.9, na Up 7.53, na Ro 3.2, na Gal 3.19, na Ib 2.2\x*IŇčmbaia aina nicara mina taŇčga tumbunna t…®kca an ramta…®r kocorta taup ndeacatke, Moses, ma ndo ma minap eacrina. Ainda moca ma min t…®kcarica Sainai Takur tamuŇč nagacatke, RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča mamo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamb maneaŇčgat, an kambca iarwarna eteacna kamb topca maica, ma mac nda irikca nemo an kambca iarwarna eteacna kambca, ma an mawiwitiat.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 39 \x - \xo 7:39 \xt Ndu 14.3\x*Karica ma gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNa aina nicara Mosesna kam mbaparaca mina toŇčgo Ňčgocor, na mina toŇčtoŇča mina ndorimo Isip mac nda tataŇčna landamŇčiap.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 7:40 \xt NA 32.1, na 32.23\x*Ainda moca mina Ňčgepca Aronmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU aina m…®rpembraraiŇčta dawar ndeida moca mina aina outmbaica taŇčraŇčna. Aia Mosesmo lamŇči Ňčgocor! An ramootta ma aimo Isipa t…®kca aŇčg…®ra laruatna ramoot, aia man ndaruapekna reaca aia lamŇči Ňčgocor.‚Äô  
\v 41 \x - \xo 7:41 \xt NA 32.2-6, na TW 9.16, na Ňäap 106.19\x*Ainda moca an m…®nna, mina da ianmo bulmakao nuoc toca moca, manmo aŇčg…®ra ndorita m…®r…®praraŇča moca mana g…®mbamba moca, anna toŇčtoŇča moca anna amtiam rapaca keca mberairina.  
\v 42 \x - \xo 7:42 \xt Ňäap 81.12, na Ier 19.13, na Esi 20.24, na 20.39, na 2 Te 2.11\x*Ri, mina ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo iŇč neaŇčga wattacarica mina guiarapa raapa karwaimo aŇčg…®ri ndorita m…®rpembraraiŇča moca minmo tutpemb r…®mb…®tca mina mbendeinande. An rambca morina ramta…®rta mbopatna kambca mina timbigta kapta inikca tirca eacrena kambta kirara gaindopatna, ‚ÄėNe IsraelnaŇčgep tikca, ne an guiara, 40na m…®nna an ramta…®r kocorta taupemb tiŇčgik ndeacatke, ndorita t…®pemb Ňčgorikca mo kecarina moca bulmakaorapa sipsipara r…®Ňčga moekna g…®mbamba, ne auk ki, ndamŇčica moekna g…®mbam ki, a? Aku aindopnande, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.  
\v 43 An Ndamma ne aŇčg…®ra taŇčrenanna, anna aukna Ndamma wanaiŇč. Anna m…®r…®praraŇč Moleknan. Ri, ne toco guina da ianna moca, an guimo m…®r…®praraŇč Repannan ndopca ne anap aŇčg…®rca taŇčrena. Ne an paparuna reikmo m…®rpembraraiŇč topca moa maica, ne ndorimo mina outmo tutpemb r…®mb…®tca mina mbendeina moca. Aintik aku nenmo nena eacrena pitrikca t…®ki aŇčg…®ri ootca, nenmo mandaca ne taŇčca pitrik aniac Babilonmo werapca monmbai waŇčna pitrikca mandaca ne taŇčca an ndeacnande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ \f + \fr 7:43 \ft An m…®r…®praraŇč Molek, ma Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčna m…®r…®praraŇč. Na Repan toco, ma reac tamuŇčna gui ian, na mina manmo mbendeirena m…®r…®praraŇč ian. Na an kamma Stipenna mbopatnanna, ma ramma morina ramoot Emosna timbigta kap sapta 5 wes 25 taŇčca wes 27na m…®n. Na Emosa gainda ninirina, IsraelnaŇčgepca atu Ňčgoinna mina RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mba mbendeirenanna, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kammo nda mboprena, na an t…®pna kirara mina an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčna m…®rpembraraiŇčmo raŇčgaica mbendeirena. Aintik iŇčmbaia RaraŇč Aetaniaca watrinanna, Israelnanda manmo iŇč neaŇčri, na ma Babilonnanmo wattacarica mina Ňčgepca minapmo ruŇčga, mina Israelnanmo aŇčg…®ca Babilonna pitrikna kaik Ňčgorikca t…®katna.\f* 
\p  
\v 44 \x - \xo 7:44 \xt NA 25.9, na 25.40, na 26.30, na Ib 8.5\x*Ri, Stipenna gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAina nicara an ramta…®r kocorta taup ndeacrina m…®n mbuŇča, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna Ndam aniacap aŇčg…®ra taŇčrina. Ri, an Ndam aniacna inikca RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndo Ňčgoinna an inik ndeacrenan. Na maica mina an Ndamma mona mo te, mina RaraŇč Aetaniaca Mosesmo wandacatna reikta kirar Ňčgoinna raŇčgaica, an RaraŇč Aetaniaca Mosesmo riptica mboprena kirara, mina ainda monande.  
\v 45 \x - \xo 7:45 \xt Ios 3.14-17, na 18.1, na 23.9, na Nei 9.24, na Ňäap 44.2, na Up 13.19\x*IŇčmbaia an nicarta mombonikca an RaraŇč Aetaniacna Ndam aniac aŇčg…®rca, Iosua raŇčgaica mina taŇčca kabena meikramta…®rta pitrikmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca an pitriknaŇčgepta meikramta…®rmo aina nicarta lamn…®ac Ňčgoutta t…®kca, ootta mandacatna pitrikmo, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna Ndam aniacmo an naaŇčg…®ri w…®t…®kca, an Ndam ndeaca taŇčca Dewitta gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ndaruekna m…®nna t…®knande.  
\v 46 \x - \xo 7:46 \xt 1 Sml 16.1, na 2 Sml 7.1-16, na 1 GRP 8.19, na 1 Nin 17.1-14, na Ňäap 89.19, na 132.1-5\x*An ramoot Dewitmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo otaca mataua morena ramoot, aintik ma RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mambendeiat, ndomo watcari te, ma mana kac laŇč ianna moca Iakopna r…®mbnarapa Ňčgamrira an kac inikca mbukca tutpemb r…®mb…®tca tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniaca mbendeiraŇčna moca.  
\v 47 \x - \xo 7:47 \xt 1 GRP 6.1-38, na 8.20, na 1 Nin 17.12, na 2 Nin 3.1-17\x*Aindopatna kaca, Solomonna ndo iŇčmbai mamoat.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 48 \x - \xo 7:48 \xt 1 GRP 8.27, na 2 Nin 2.6, na 6.18\x*Karica Stipenna gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúNa auŇč tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniaca, ramoot par moekna kaca ma gidik, gidik Ňčgoinna mba eacitndai, an kamma anna rambca morina ramta…®rta mbopatna kamb, 
\b  
\q1  
\v 49 \x - \xo 7:49 \xt Mt 5.34-35, na 23.22\x*\x - \xo 7:49 \xt Ais 66.1-2\x*‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniac Kacootta gaindopatna, 
\q2 ‚ÄúTamuŇčna auŇča anna aukna mbiracrena taup, 
\q3 na tiacarpaikca aukna orniŇč lotairena taup, 
\q3 aintik ne aukmo titocna kac Ňčgoinna moit? 
\q2 Na titocna taupca ndo aukna w…®kt…®t…®kna taupca moit? 
\q2  
\v 50 An reikca auk moa maiatna reik.‚ÄĚ‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\b  
\p  
\v 51 \x - \xo 7:51 \xt NA 32.9, na TN 26.41, na TW 10.16, na Ais 48.4, na 63.10, na Ier 6.10, na 9.26\x*Ri, Stipenna ninikar waŇčgorapna ramta…®rmo gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúNe paŇčaind gagrarta ramta…®r koind, ne kam mbarac Ňčgocorta ramta…®rta kirar, nena nikemb inkarta iroara kocnaia watta mboraca, anna ma raekmbai ndeacreke, morena ramta…®rta kirarir koind. Na nena kour inkara kocnaia r…®kdacarica, ne RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamma mba waracrenanna. Ainda moreke, nena nicara atua memetmbaca morina kirara, ne ŇäeroŇč Ratna kam mbarac narica karirina.  
\v 52 \x - \xo 7:52 \xt 2 Nin 36.16, na Mt 21.35, na 23.31, na 1 Te 2.15\x*Na titocna ramma morina ramootmo atua, nena nicara minmo t…®p kirar laŇča moatna? WanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Na rambca morina ramta…®ra minmo gan kam ndopatna, t…®p wandoŇč niŇčgikca morena ramoot ian ma k…®pnande, aindopatna ramta…®rmo nena nicara minmo, r…®Ňčga menaca mamaiat. Mina aindopatna ramootta, ma k…®pca laruatke, ne maŇčgepatnanna manmo aŇčg…®ra puŇčnaŇčgepta, para t…®kca mina mamo r…®Ňčga mamenacat.  
\v 53 \x - \xo 7:53 \xt NA 20.1, na Up 7.38, na Gal 3.19, na Ib 2.2\x*Ne T…®p Wand…®kmo mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčerŇčgaur tambuŇča t…®kca aŇčg…®ratna, na ne anmo mba ŇčaŇčaria raŇčgairinanna.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mina Stipenmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňčga mamenacat 
\p  
\v 54 \x - \xo 7:54 \xt Up 5.33\x*Iudananta ninikar waŇčgorta ramta…®r paŇčainda, mina Stipenna mbopatna kamb mbaraca, manmo nikembkatacarica nda…®rpakemb irikca, ikca maica.  
\v 55 \x - \xo 7:55 \xt Mt 22.44, na Up 2.33-34, na 5.31, na 6.5\x*Ri, Stipenmo ŇäeroŇč Ratta manmo mbukca lacakeca, ma tamuŇčna auŇča raia watca ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna memetacna tac aniaca mawatat. Na Iesusa RaraŇč Aetaniacna par umbaina waŇčga w…®t…®kca eacrenan tocmo ma mawatat.  
\v 56 \x - \xo 7:56 \xt Esi 1.1, na Dan 7.13, na Mt 3.16, na Up 10.11, na Kol 3.1\x*Ri, ma minmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAe, ne warac, tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniacna auŇča gootca maeacreke, aku wattapeknanna Ramootna Nuoca ndona Aetna par umbaia w…®t…®kca maeacreke.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 57 Ri, mina an kambca waracatke, mina an kambca waparaca, toŇčgo Ňčgocor, aintik mina kamb anik keca mina muruŇča, ootta taŇčga Stipenmo muocameraca.  
\v 58 \x - \xo 7:58 \xt TW 13.9, na Lk 4.29, na Up 6.13-14, na 22.20, na Ib 13.12\x*Mina manap aŇčg…®ca wuoc raek naaŇčg…®rca malaruat, manmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňč menac ndopca. AŇčg…®ca larua raekca t…®kca, manmo Ňčgaua paparuta kamb topatna ramta…®ra, mina Ňčgepca ndorita tikemb Ňčgapoik anikmo riaŇčga aŇčg…®ra ramoot Ňčgam ianna k…®t…®mma t…®kcamacariat, na an ramootna ia Sol.\f + \fr 7:58 \ft T…®p Wand…®kca IsraelnaŇčgepmo aindoprena, ramootta t…®p Ňčgoreac Ňčgoinna mo te, mina manmo auŇčmo raekmbai naaŇčg…® laruca, watur puŇčga mamo r…®Ňči taŇči ma menacnandet. Na Taup Ndamta…®rna timbigta kap sapta 24 wes 13 taŇčca wes 16na m…®n, na Ndunduna timbigta kap sapta 15 wes 35na inikca u anna wat, an kam toco an ndeacrena.\f* 
\v 59 \x - \xo 7:59 \xt Ňäap 31.5, na Lk 23.46\x*Na an m…®nna, mina Stipenmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňč menacna r…®Ňčri, Stipenna Kacoot Iesusmo mbendeica aindopatna, ‚ÄúU aukna irikekna ŇčeroŇčmo u aŇčg…®.‚ÄĚ  
\v 60 \x - \xo 7:60 \xt Mt 5.44, na Lk 23.34, na Up 9.40, na 21.5\x*Ri, ma tutupniŇč r…®mb…®tca mbiraca kam aniac keca, gaindopatna, ‚ÄúKacoot, mina aukmo ainda morena t…®p Ňčgoreacna makukmo, u kai lamŇči teac.‚ÄĚ Stipenna aindopacarica, ma mamenacat. 
\c 8  
\nb  
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Up 7.58, na 8.4, na 11.19, na 22.20\x*Ri, Solna lamn…®ac Ňčgoutmo mina Stipenmo ainda moatna t…®p kirara, an t…®p kirarmo ma ainda toŇčgoatna. 
\p Aintik an ra mina Stipenmo r…®Ňčga menacatke, mina andu naŇčgepca Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna Ierusalemna inik ndeacrenanna mbukca, minmo mo Ňčgoreac Ňčgoin mamori. Ainda moatke, an ndeacrina Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna, Ňčgepca k…®pcarica tamtambca taŇčga pitrik Iudiaapa Samariana inikna auŇčembca taŇčga mamaiat. Ri, up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra, mina an Ierusalem maeacri. 
\s1 Sola Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunmo moa Ňčgocrairena 
\p  
\v 2 Ri, ramta…®r ndeida RaraŇč Aetaniacna toŇčgorena kirarira raŇčgairena ramta…®ra, mina Ňčgepca taŇčga Stipenna wa…®r aŇčg…®a taŇčga mutocatke, mana moca nanae bagaraniac mamoat.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 8:3 \xt Up 9.1, na 9.13, na 9.21, na 22.4-5, na 26.9-11, na 1 Ko 15.9, na 1 Ti 1.13\x*Ri, Sola Ňčgepca Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunna, inikca mbukca minmo moa Ňčgocraiatke, anna meik co ramta…®rta, kaikta inkara mbukca minmo anna t…®kca pia muoca aŇčg…®ra taŇčga kac Ňčgoreacna inik mat…®kat. 
\ms1 Up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra Iesusna moatna reikta kambmo, Iudiaapa Samariana inikca mbukca anna t…®kca wiwitiatna 
\mr (8.4‚ÄĒ12.25) 
\s1 Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo mina Samaria t…®kca mawiwitiat 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 8:4 \xt Mt 10.23, na Up 6.5, na 11.19\x*An k…®pcarica auŇčembca tamtambca taŇčga maiatna meikramta…®r, mina ndori eacatna auŇčembca t…®kca kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo, anna t…®kca mawiwitiat.  
\v 5 Ri, Pilipa, ma taŇčga Samariarta auŇč aniac ian Ňčgirikca an ndeacrina. Na ma mina meikramta…®rmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramootna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma, anna t…®kca mawiwitiat.  
\v 6 Ri, meikramta…®r w…®t aniac Ňčgoinna, Pilipna mbopatna kambca waracri, mana moatna Ňčgagatracara watca, mina matau Ňčgoinna mbiraca ndorita kour ikca mana mboprina kamb mawaracri.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt Mt 10.1, na Mk 16.17\x*Na mina watri, Pilipa an meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreaca moa Ňčgocraica eacrinanmo, ma moa kecariatke. An ŇčerŇčgaur Ňčgorikca min kecarina mori, kamb anikca wanaiŇča lar…®kca irikca minmo t…®kcamacariat. Ri, meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca orapa…®r menaca eacrinanapa, orapa…®r Ňčgocraica eacrinanda, ma minmo moa laiŇč mac mamoat.  
\v 8 Ainda moca an m…®nna an auŇčna meikramta…®ra toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin laruca eacrina. 
\p  
\v 9 Na an auŇčna ramoot ian, mana ia Saimon. Ma Ňčgaua ainta reac, reacna ndururca morenan, ri, SamarianaŇčgepta meikramta…®ra an mana morina reikca watri, mina tamtam malamŇčiat. Ri, ma minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAku ramoot aet.‚ÄĚ Na ma aindopatna reikapa kamna moca, mina tamtam malamŇčiat.  
\v 10 Ri, ramta…®r paŇčaindapa meikramta…®r wananira, mana kamb mbaracri, ndorimo memetmbac mbaracraŇčna moca morena. Na mina gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúSaimon ma m…®r…®praraŇč ian, aintik RaraŇč Aetaniacna Gargar Bagaraniaca manap eacrena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Aintik ma ainta reac, reaca mori, mina memetmbaca watca, ainda moca mina ndorimo mana ndur mbuŇča morina reikca memetmbaca watna moca tamtam Ňčgoin pac malamŇčiri.  
\v 12 Na an m…®nna Pilipa RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuocna kammapa Iesus Karaisna kam ndopatke, meikramta…®ra an kam mbaraca muruŇča anna r…®pacatna, na mina puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat.  
\v 13 Ri, Saimon toco, aind mbatca ma toco r…®paca minap k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat. Karica ma Ňčgepca Pilipap taŇčri, mana morina Ňčgagatracarca watca tamtam pac malamŇčiri. 
\p  
\v 14 Ri, Samariana meikramta…®ra RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam aŇčg…®ratke, na Ierusalem ndeacatna up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®ra an kam mawaracat. Ainda moca mina Ňčgepca Pitaapa Ion mbaniŇčmo min ndambuŇča mbag…®rica maniŇča mataŇčgat.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Up 2.38\x*Karica maniŇča taŇčga laruca. An Samarianandmo ŇäeroŇč Rat aŇčg…®na moca, maniŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mambendeiat.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 8:16 \xt Mt 28.19, na Up 10.48, na 19.2\x*Na an ŇäeroŇč Ratta Ňčgaua min nambatta mba irikatke, mina Iesusna i niŇčgik mbuŇča k…®tac puk niŇčgik aŇčg…®ratna.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt Up 6.6, na 19.6, na Ib 6.2\x*Na maniŇča mbendeia maica, ndoniŇčna parniŇčmo mina paŇčaind tambatta t…®katke, mina ŇäeroŇč Rat maaŇčg…®rat. 
\p  
\v 18 Ri, Saimonna watri, an up aŇčg…®rena ramootniŇča ndoniŇčna parniŇčmo min nambatta t…®katke, mina ŇäeroŇč Rat maaŇčg…®at. Ainda moca ma kituknduk aŇčg…®ca k…®pca maniŇč ndambuŇč ndaruca, an gargar Ňčgoikna moca ma maniŇčmo gaindopatna,  
\v 19 ‚ÄúOŇčgo auk motocmo an gargar neaŇč, aku an oŇčgo morina kirara aku ndona parmo meikramta…®rta paŇčaind tambatta t…®k te, mina muruŇča ŇäeroŇč Rat aŇčg…®nandet.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 8:20 \xt Mt 10.8, na Up 2.38, na 10.45\x*Ri, Pita Saimonmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúUna an kitukndukara anna unap Ňčgocrainandet! Titocna reikca RaraŇč Aetaniaca wanaiŇča neaŇčrena reikmo, u ndomo an reikmo kitukndukar puŇčga opoik ndamŇčicat ki, a? WanaiŇč Ňčgoin.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Ňäap 78.37\x*Una iro inik unanna RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®acmo laŇča eac Ňčgocor, ainda moca u gan RaraŇč Aetaniacna aiŇča aia morenanna, u anna inikca mbukna toawanaiŇč.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 8:22 \xt Dan 4.27, na 2 Ti 2.25\x*U iro inik Ňčgetrikica an ndona t…®p Ňčgoreacmo iŇč neaŇčgarica, u Kacootmo mbendeica digi te, ma an una iro inik ndeacreke, umo an iro Ňčgoreac neaŇčga morena iro Ňčgoreac anmo, ma mo kecarinande.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 8:23 \xt Ib 12.15\x*Aku aindopapekna kamna m…®n…®Ňča gaind, aku watreke, una iro aniac unanna, u ndomo RaraŇč Aetaniacna wanaiŇča neaŇčrena opotacna reikta mamatŇči aniac Ňčgoin, ainda moca an mamatŇčina wapatna kirara u t…®p Ňčgoreacna makuk inik maeacreke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 24 \x - \xo 8:24 \xt NA 8.8, na Ndu 21.7, na 1 GRP 13.6, na Ie 5.16\x*Ri, Saimonna nda rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOŇčgo RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mbendei mbopca ma aukna moca kadmai. Te, an oŇčna mboprena reikca aukmo mba laruitndai.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 25 Karica up aŇčg…®ratna ramootniŇča, meikramta…®rmo, maniŇča ndoniŇč ndaruatna RaraŇč Aetaniacna reikta kam ndopca maica. IŇčmbaia maniŇča Ierusalemma taŇčna taŇčgatke. ManiŇča Kacootna kambmo, Samariana inikna auŇčembmo an kam wembaŇč laŇčna kambca an wiwitia mbopca Ierusalem mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Pilipa Itiopiana ramoot ianmo kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma, manmo an mawiwitiat 
\p  
\v 26 Kacootna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna Pilipmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU Ňčgepca maŇčarmbaina waŇčga taŇčca taup ianna Ierusalem kunda taŇčga eacekna taupca, u an taup ndiŇča taŇč te, Gasa auŇč ndarunande.‚ÄĚ An taup t…®kca meikramta…®r kocorta k…®dr…®k ndeacrena.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 8:27 \xt Ais 56.3-7, na Sep 3.10, na In 12.20\x*Karica Pilipa Ňčgepca an taup ndiŇča taŇč, taŇčga anna t…®kca Itiopiana ramoot ian mawatat, na an ramoot tikca ma Itiopiana gagrirta meac paŇčan Kandasina aiŇča morena ramoot paŇčan ian, na ma an meac paŇčanna kitukndukarapa mana reik aŇčg…®ra wembacrena ramoot. Na ma ndo Ierusalemmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam mbaracna taŇčgatna.\f + \fr 8:27 \ft An ramoot paŇčan ma Itiopiana meac paŇčanna kitcartukar raupŇčirena ramoot, mina mana utniŇčmo waiŇčtocatna. Na Itiopiana ramta…®r paŇčaind ndeida, ramta…®r ndeida mina, mina aiŇča morena motoco, mina minmo ainda morina.\f* 
\v 28 Na ma ndomo Itiopia mac nda taŇč ndopca, ma taup ndiŇča taŇčrina. Ri ma ndona os w…®Ňčga taŇčrena bara mbiraca taŇčri, ma ramma morina ramoot Aisaiana timbigta kap aŇčg…®ca an mawatri.  
\v 29 Karica, ŇäeroŇč Ratta Pilipmo an ramootna os ndambuŇča taŇči rambuŇčaina iro neaŇčca.\fig Ossa w…®Ňčga taŇčrena bar|src="GW157.tif" size="col" copy="Wade" ref="8.29" \fig* 
\v 30 Karica Pilipa taŇčga rambuŇčaica waracatnanna, an ramootta ramma morina ramoot Aisaiana timbigta kap aŇčg…®ca anna watca mbopca taŇčri, na Pilipa gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOe, u an watapekna kambta m…®n…®Ňča lamŇčia garac reiki, wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ  
\v 31 \x - \xo 8:31 \xt In 16.13\x*Ri, an ramootta mana kammo gainda nda rutiatna, ‚ÄúRamoot ianna aukmo an kamna m…®n…®Ňča mbopi warac Ňčgocor, aku an kamna m…®n…®Ňčmo titoc ndamŇčit?‚ÄĚ Aindopacarica ma Pilipmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU k…®pca aukna ossa w…®Ňčga taŇčrena bar naŇčgabukca, aukna k…®t…®mma mbirac.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 32 \x - \xo 8:32 \xt Ais 53.7-8\x*Na ma an RaraŇč Aetaniacna timbigta kapca ma gootca watatna kam t…®pca, gan kam ndopatna, ‚ÄúMina manmo mo menacna moca aŇčg…®ra taŇčri, ma sipsipna kirar, ma kam ianna mbop Ňčgocor, na ma sipsipna mooŇčnuocna kirar, mina mana r…®kar katacri, ma kam ianna mo Ňčgocor.  
\v 33 Ri, mina mana ia moŇčgocraiatke, an reac wanaiŇčna moca manmo ritri waparacna moca ramootna par mat…®kat. Na mina manmo moa menacatna, na ma mba eacri. Aintik ma mombonik kocor, na meikramta…®ra minmo mbopca waracatna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 34 An ramootta an kambca watta maica, karica ma Pilipmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAku unmo gainda diginande, gan kambca ramma morina ramootta mandaina ndopca mbopatna, kamb? Ramma morina ramootta ma ndona ndopatna ki, co, ma kabena ramootna ndopatna?‚ÄĚ  
\v 35 \x - \xo 8:35 \xt Lk 24.27, na Up 18.28\x*Ri, Pilipa an ramootmo mana watatna kambta m…®niŇčta kamb topacarica, iŇčmbaia ma manmo Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamb ndeidap mac mambopat.  
\v 36-37 \x - \xo 8:36-37 \xt Up 10.47\x*Karica maniŇča an taup ndiŇča taŇč, taŇčga, taŇčga puk tapen ian ndaruri, na an ramootta aindopatna, ‚ÄúU wat puk tapen ianna monde. Reac ianna aukna taupca wawaraca eac Ňčgocor? Aku k…®tac puk aŇčg…®na m…®n.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 8:36-37 \ft LandamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida gaind ndamŇčirena, kabena kam t…®p ian toco maeacreke. Na an kamma gaindoprina, \fq ‚ÄúNa Pilipa aindopatna, ‚ÄėU ndona iro inik mbuŇča r…®pac te, u k…®tac puk aŇčg…®nandet.‚Äô Na an Itiopiana ramootta ma mana kammo gainda rutiatna, ‚ÄėAku Iesus Karaismo r…®pacrena ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Nuoc.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\f* 
\p  
\v 38 Karica an ramootta, an osna tiŇčara morina ramootmo mbopca, ma os w…®Ňčga taŇčrina ossarta Ňčgat…®k w…®Ňčga t…®kri, an ossara w…®t…®katna mbatca, Pilipapa an ramootta, maniŇča puk Ňčgirikca. Pilipa an ramootmo puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk maneaŇčgat.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 8:39 \xt 1 GRP 18.12, na 2 GRP 2.16, na Esi 3.12-14\x*Karica maniŇča tapenna puk t…®kcarica nda gacatke, Kacootna ŇäeroŇč Ratta Pilipmo tawina naaŇčg…®rca taŇčgatke, an ramootta Pilipna moca, ma watta tambca. Na an ramoot tikca toŇčgocarica Ňčgepca ndona ossa w…®Ňčga taŇčrena bar naŇčgabukca ndona k…®patna taupca raŇčgaica mataŇčgat.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 8:40 \xt Up 21.8\x*Ri, Pilipa wattatnanna, ma Asdot auŇča w…®t…®kca maeacat. Karica ma Ňčgepca an inikna auŇčemb anikmo tamtambca taŇčri, Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo an auŇčembca wiwitia taŇčga maica, iŇčmbaia ma taŇčga Sisaria auŇč aniac malaruat. 
\c 9  
\s1 Sol ma iro nikinik Ňčgetrikiatna 
\r (Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇč 22.4-16 na 26.9-18) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt Up 8.3, na Gal 1.13, na 1 Ti 1.13\x*An m…®nna Sola Kacoot Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo, mo Ňčgocraina moca, ma minmo moi menacna kam gargar ndopca, ma kam maleacat. Ri, ma Ňčgepca taup ndamoot paŇčan aniaca watna mataŇčgat.  
\v 2 Na ma taŇčga laruca, taup ndamoot paŇčan aniaca watca, manmo gainda digica mambopat, ‚ÄúU mandeaca Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaik raupŇčirena ramta…®r paŇčainda, Damaskusna inik ndeacrenanmo timbiŇč raprir ndeida tirna.‚ÄĚ Aindopatke, taup ndamoot paŇčan aniaca Ňčgepca timbiŇč raprir ndeid tirca maica, aŇčg…®ra Sol maneaŇčgat. Na an timbiŇč raprirta kambca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúSola meacramoota mandaia Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgaieknanna wat te, ma an meacramootmo muoca, leaca Ierusalem mac nda aŇčg…®r taŇčnande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3 \xt Up 22.6, na 26.12, na 1 Ko 15.8\x*Ainda moca Sola Ierusalem t…®kcarica Ňčgepca Damaskus auŇča taŇčna taŇčga. Maica ma Damaskusa auŇčmo rambuŇčaiatke, RaraŇč Aetaniacna tamuŇčna auŇč ndiŇča memetac ianna man nambatta tawi Ňčgoin motemma man nambatta metacatna, memetaca gargar Ňčgoin.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Mt 25.40\x*Ri, ma pitrik Ňčgirikca keca, ma waracri mbuŇča, ramoot ianna kamma, manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúO Sol, u aukmo tida mona moca, u aukmo ainda moa Ňčgocraica taŇčre?‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt Up 5.39, na 1 Ko 15.8\x*Ri, ma aind madigiat, ‚ÄúKacoot, u mandai?‚ÄĚ Ri, an ramootna kamma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAku Iesus, u aukmo Ňčgoreac Ňčgoin mamoreke.  
\v 6 Karica u Ňčgepca an auŇčna inikca mbuk, iŇčmbai ecte, ramoot ianna una momona reikta kambca ma umo mbopnande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Up 22.9, na 26.13\x*Ri, Solap taŇčgatna ramta…®ra Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca, kam ianna mba mbopatke, mina an mbopatna kambca mina mawaracri, na mina an kam ndoprina ramoot nake watwatta tambca, ramoot ianmo wat Ňčgocor.  
\v 8 Karica Sola Ňčgepca wat ndopca wattatnanna, towanaiŇč. Mana lamn…®acniŇča nenepucarica reac ianna watna m…®nna wanaiŇč. Ainda moca mina mana par ŇčgutiŇčga manmo Damaskus auŇč aniac naaŇčg…®ra mambukat.  
\v 9 Na ma an ndeaca raia mbonkac mamoat, na mana lamn…®acniŇča pupuroca aind maeacri, na ma amna reacapa pukca mba ambatke. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt Up 22.12\x*Na Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena ramoot ianna, ma toca an Damaskus auŇč ndeacrina, mana ia Ananaias. Na ma manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča watrina tamramma, Kacootta mana i maacat, ‚ÄúAnanaias.‚ÄĚ Ri, ma rutica aindopatna, ‚ÄúKacoot, aku gade.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt Up 16.9, na 21.39, na 22.3\x*Ri, Kacootta manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU Ňčgepca taup ianna, aia Taup WandoŇč Ňčgacrena taupca, u anna taŇč. Iudasna kacna Ňčgore taŇčca wat te, u digi, Tarasus auŇčna ramoot ian, ma an kacna inik ndeacreke, mandeaca ma mambendeireke, mana ia Sol.  
\v 12 Mana lamn…®acniŇč mananna nenepucarica watna toawanaiŇč, na ma toca ma manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča watrina tamramma, ma ramoot ian mawatat, mana ia Ananaias, ma k…®pca mbukca, ndona parmo man nambatta t…®k te, mana lamn…®acniŇča laŇč mac monande! Ma anmo manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča watrina tamram.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Up 8.3\x*Na Ananaiasa nda rutica aindopatna, ‚ÄúKacoot, aku waracreke memetmbaca meikramta…®r, an ramootna nininimo ainda ninirena, ma una Ierusalem ndeacrena meikramta…®rmo t…®p laŇča mba morenanna, ma minmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca morena.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 9:14 \xt Up 9.1-2, na 9.21, na 22.16, na 1 Ko 1.2, na 2 Ti 2.22\x*Ma taup ndamta…®r paŇčaind tambuŇča kam landamŇči laŇč maaŇčg…®ri, gan Damaskus auŇč ndeacrena meikramta…®ra mandaia una raŇčgaireke, una i mbuŇča r…®pacrenanna wat te, ma minmo utiŇčnande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 \x - \xo 9:15 \xt Up 25.13, na 25.22, na 26.17, na 27.24, na Ro 1.5, na 1 Ko 15.10, na Gal 2.7-8, na 1 Ti 2.7\x*Ri, Kacootta manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU Ňčgepca taŇč! An ramootta mandeaca ma aukna aiŇčna ramootta monande. Aku manmo larapacri, manmo Ňčgepca taŇčca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčapa gagrirta ramta…®r paŇčaindapa Israelnandap, ma minmo aukna ia wiwiti ndopca larapacri.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 9:16 \xt Up 20.23, na 21.11, na 2 Ko 11.23-28\x*Ma aukna i aŇčg…®ca mbukca moca taŇčgekna m…®n mbuŇča, aku manmo ainta g…®g…®grarapa ainta makukar t…®ki wandac te, ma aŇčg…® Ňčgoin naaŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 9:17 \xt Up 13.52, na 22.12-13\x*Ainda moca Ananaiasa mataŇčgat. Na ma taŇčga an kac inikca mbukca, ndona parniŇčmo Solna paŇčan nambatta t…®kca manmo aind mambopat, ‚ÄúKaka Sol, Kacoot Iesus, ma unmo taupca t…®kca wattatna ramoot, ma mandeaca aukmo una wat ndopca mbag…®rica, aku k…®papekna, una lamn…®acniŇčmo mo laŇča moca u watna, te, ŇäeroŇč Ratta umo mbuki m…®nna t…®knande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Ananaiasa aindopca maiatke, Ňčgoaemna rir tocna reaca mana lamn…®acniŇčmo mboraca eacrinanna, tawina mbutukatke, na lamn…®acniŇč mananna laŇč mamoat. Mbatca ma taŇčga k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat.  
\v 19 Na iŇčmbaia ma amna reac amba gargar nan mac nda maaŇčg…®rat. 
\s1 Sola Damaskusnandmo kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma ma an mawiwitiat 
\p Ri, ma Damaskus auŇč aniaca Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rapmo rai ndepikca minap maeacat.  
\v 20 Na iŇčmbaia ma Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaik inkara mbukca, ma minmo mawiwitiat, ‚ÄúIesus ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Nuoc.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 \x - \xo 9:21 \xt Up 8.3, na Gal 1.13, na 1.23\x*Ri, meikramta…®ra muruŇča Solna mbopatna an kambca waraca, mina Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca tamtam ndamŇčica mina Ňčgepca aind mambopat, ‚ÄúAnde an ramoot, ma Ierusalemnandmo, ma meikramta…®ra Iesusa r…®paca eacrenanna, na mana kamb mbaracri, na mana i mbuŇča mbendeirinandmo, ma moa maŇčgocrairi. Na an iro kabea moatna, na mandeaca ma gan nak…®papeknanna, ma ndomo an meikramta…®rmo muoc leaca taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindta para t…®k ndopca anna nak…®papek ki.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 9:22 \xt Up 17.3, na 18.5, na 18.28\x*Ainda mori Solna gargara kocnaia gagracarica, ma an Damaskus ndeacrina Iudanandmo, ma aindopatna, ‚ÄúIesusa ande RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot.‚ÄĚ Na Iudananda manap ipuŇči mbop ndopca moatna kambca, ma an kamb ndopatke, mina waraca Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca, manap mbop ndopca moatna kambca, andu waracamacariat, kam ianna mba mbopatke. 
\s1 Iudananda Solap kaega moca, ma k…®pcamacariat 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 9:23 \xt Up 23.12, na 25.3, na 2 Ko 11.23\x*\x - \xo 9:23 \xt 2 Ko 11.32-33\x*Karica rai ndepik taŇčga maiatke, Iudana meikramta…®ra tumbun ian ŇčgutiŇčga kam maleacat, Sola mo menacna moca.  
\v 24 Ri, mina Sola mona moca mbopatna reikta kambca ma anna waraca eacri, na mina ndorimo an auŇč aniacna wuocna t…®Ňčembta ŇčginaŇča mouŇč ra moa eacrina, Solmo anna t…®kca mo menacna ndopca, mori.  
\v 25 Na Solna iŇča raŇčgairena ramta…®ra mamo mouŇč naaŇčg…®ra k…®pcarica, ga an auŇč aniacna wuocna tamuŇč naaŇčg…®ra gaca, manmo larkam aniac ianna inikca manmo mbopca ma an inik Ňčgirikca mbiracatna mbatca, mina larkam mo Ňčga…®r ikca manmo an wuocna raekmbaina kacrepca irikca rapaca ma mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Sola Ierusalemma taŇčga an maeacat 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 9:26 \xt Up 22.17, na Gal 1.17-19\x*Ainda mocarica, iŇčmbaia Sola taŇčga Ierusalem ndaruca, ndomo Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r tambuŇča taŇč mbuk ndopca taŇčgatke, an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra Sol mbatca, nanambica manmo ndori tambuŇč nak…®p mbumbukca mina toŇčgo Ňčgocor, mina r…®t…®paca mina gaind ndamŇčirina, an ramootta Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena ramoot ianna wanaiŇč.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 9:27 \xt Up 4.36, na 9.4, na 9.20-22, na 1 Ko 9.1, na 15.8\x*Ainda moatke, Banambasa Ňčgepca Solap aŇčg…®ca manmo up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r tambuŇča warkica mataŇčgat. Na ma minmo Kacoot Iesusa Solmo taupca t…®kca watca, Kacootta manmo mbopatna kambmo, ma an ndopacarica. IŇčmbaia Sola Damaskusa t…®kca rugutta mo Ňčgocora Iesusna i aŇčg…®ra, Ňčgepatna nininia ma an mac maniniat.  
\v 28 Ainda moca Sola minap an Ierusalem ndeacri. Ma minap taŇč k…®p t…®kri. Na ma min narica mba nanambiri. Na ma Iesusna imo rugutta mo Ňčgocora memetmbaca wiwitia gagaraca taŇčrina.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 9:29 \xt Up 6.1, na 9.23, na 11.20, na 2 Ko 11.26\x*Ri, Girikna kam ndoprina Iudanandmo Sola mba wewettarinanna, ma minmo kam gargara neaŇčga taŇčri. Na mina mana mo menacna taupembta maoreri.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 9:30 \xt Gal 1.21\x*Ainda moca Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara aind mbaracatke, mina Ňčgepca Solmo aŇčg…®ca warkica irikca Sisaria auŇč aniaca t…®kri, na annanda manmo Tarasus auŇč aniaca mandaca ma mataŇčgat. 
\p  
\v 31 Aintik an Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumnambca an Iudiaapa, Galiliapa, Samariaap, mina inik ndeacrina an r…®paca eacrinanda, ainta reac ianna minmo mba laruri, mina nikinik iro wetwet laŇč maeacat. Ainda moca mina Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumnambca an ndeacrenanda mina w…®t…®kca magagaracat. Ainda moca mina Kacootna kamb mbaraca, mana kaŇčgauk ndeteacna kirar ndeacre tik, ŇäeroŇč Ratta mina iroar inkarmo moa paŇčpaiŇčica eacreke, na meikramta…®ra anna watca k…®pca an tumbunna inikca mbukrena. 
\s1 Pita ma Ainiasa moa laŇča moatna 
\p  
\v 32 Ri, Pita, an m…®nna ma an inikna auŇčembca muruŇča taŇčrina. Na ma ndomo RaraŇč Aetaniacna meikramta…®ra Lida auŇčnan Ňčgoke te, ndomo minap an Lida ndeac ndopca mairikat.  
\v 33 Ma an auŇč ndeacri, watatna ramoot ianna, mana ia Ainias mana gagrira kocnaia menaca, ma mba taŇčrenanna, ma rai roctira ma bar niŇčgikca meraca taŇč, taŇčga, guiara parmbaiapa mbutremb mbonkacna m…®nna, ma aind maeacat.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 9:34 \xt Up 3.6, na 3.16, na 4.10\x*Ri, Pita manmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAinias, mandeaca Iesus Karais, ma unmo mac moi laŇča monandet. U Ňčgep w…®t…®kca ndona meraca eacrena bar aŇčg…®ri waŇčgop.‚ÄĚ Ri, ma anduna Ňčgepca maw…®t…®kat.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 9:35 \xt 1 Nin 5.16, na Up 11.21\x*Na Lida auŇčna meikramta…®rapa Saronna pitrik wandoŇč ndeacrina meikramta…®rap, mina muruŇča watri, Ainiasa laŇča moatnanna watca, mina iroar inkar uriraca Kacoot maraŇčgaiat. 
\s1 Pita Tabitamo mac nda moa Ňčgepatna 
\p  
\v 36 \x - \xo 9:36 \xt 1 Ti 2.10, na Ta 3.8\x*Na mon Iopa auŇč aniacna inikca, Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta meac ianna mana ia Tabita. Na Girikna kam mbuŇča mina mamo Dokas Ňčgacrena. Na mana t…®p kirara, ma t…®p kirar laŇča morena meac, ma memetmbaca meikramta…®ra reik kocortanmo, ma minmo reac, reac Ňčgotacrenan.  
\v 37 Ainda morina meac, na an m…®nna Pita an Lida auŇč ndeacri mbuŇča Tabita roumb aŇčg…®ca menacatke, mina mana wa…®rmo rua mataua maica, aŇčg…®ra gaca diab tamuŇčna inik mat…®kat, na mana wa…®ra an ndeacri.  
\v 38 Na Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra an Iopa ndeacrinanna, Pitamo Lida ndeac ndopatna kam mbaraca, mina Ňčgepca ramoot mbuniŇčmo, Pita aŇčg…® ndopca Lida auŇč mambag…®riat. Na Iopa t…®kca Lida auŇča tataŇča tawanna wanaiŇč, ri, an ramootniŇča taŇčga Pita ndambuŇč ndaruca, manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúPita, u muindira kai mo teac tawi Ňčgepca aia nda taŇčna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Ri, Pita Ňčgepca maniŇčap mac nda taŇčga. TaŇčga laruri, mina manap aŇčg…®ca gaca an wa…®r eacrina diab tamuŇčna inikca mbukatke, an kaŇčter menaca eacrina meik koinmbara, k…®pca Pitamo paria aŇčg…®ca aeri mambopri, ‚ÄúU wat, gan tik Ňčgapoikca an meac Tabita moatna reik, aia an aocrena, mandeaca ma aimo t…®kcamacarica.‚ÄĚ  
\v 40 \x - \xo 9:40 \xt Mt 9.25, na Mk 5.40-41, na In 11.43, na Up 7.60\x*Ri, Pita an motemma punica eacrina meikramta…®rmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe gan motemma kacrepca ne raekmbai ndarumai.‚ÄĚ Ri, mina laruatna mbatca ma tutupniŇč r…®mb…®tca mbiraca mbendeia maica, ma kumbakeca Tabitana wa…®ra watta taŇčca mambopat, ‚ÄúTabita u Ňčgep.‚ÄĚ Ri, ma lamn…®acniŇč watukca watri, ma Pitamo watca ma Ňčgepca mambiracat.  
\v 41 Ri, Pita mana par ŇčgutiŇčga, manmo aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepri, na ma Ňčgepca maw…®t…®kat. Ri, Pita RaraŇč Aetaniacna meikramta…®rapa meik koinmbarap, minmo mac aca punica minmo Tabita wandaca aindopatna, ‚ÄúTabita ma wat mac nda maaŇčg…®ri.‚ÄĚ  
\v 42 Karica Pitana ainda moatna reacna kam wembaŇča, an Iopa auŇč aniacna inikca an kambca taŇčga acnairi. Na meikramta…®ra anna waraca, mina w…®tta Kacoot mar…®pacat.  
\v 43 \x - \xo 9:43 \xt Up 10.6\x*Na Pita, ma Iopa auŇč aniaca ma Saimonap rai w…®tpaikca, ma an maeacat, na Saimon tikca ma amna Ňčgoaebta iŇčir iukca reikca morena ramoot. 
\c 10  
\s1 Pita Koniliusmo ririptia moatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Mt 8.5, na Up 27.1-3\x*Mon Sisaria auŇč aniac ndeacrina ramoot ian, mana ia Konilius. Ma Romna lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra 100na m…®nna, tumbunnanda Itali ndeacrinan, na mandeaca mina gan ndeacrenan, na ma an tumbunna lapocna tiŇčara morina ramoot paŇčan.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 10:2 \xt Up 8.2, na 10.22, na 10.35, na 22.12\x*Na an ramoot, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna toŇčgorena kirara matau Ňčgoinna raŇčgaia morina. Na manapa mana kac ndeacrina meikramta…®rap, mina muruŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacmo torirenan. Ri, memetmbaca ma Iudana meikramta…®ra reik kocortanmo, kitukndukar kotaca mina ndorita reik koikrena. Na ma RaraŇč Aetaniacmo memetmbaca mbendeirena.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 10:3 \xt Up 3.1, na 10.30, na 11.13\x* Karica oit ianna wigwaca, rana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a irikca mbonkac mbuŇč toca t…®kri, Koniliusa eacri, ma manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča tamram ianna wattatna. An manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča tamram ianna wattatnanna, ma reikmo waekeke mawatat. Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna man ndambuŇč nak…®pca mamo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúKonilius!‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 Ri, Koniliusa an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇčmo mataua ŇčginaŇčikca, ma rugut mocarica manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúRamoot aniac, u kaia toŇčgorina?‚ÄĚ 
\p Ri, an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča mamo aindopatna, ‚ÄúUna mbembendeia RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma mawaracri. Na una reik kocorta meikramta…®r kotacrena t…®pemb kirarir unanna RaraŇč Aetaniaca malamŇčireke.  
\v 5 Aintik mandebanna u ramta…®r ndeidmo tawina mbag…®rica mina Iopa auŇča taŇčca, ramoot ianna mana ia Saimon, na mana i ianna Pita. Mina manmo mbopca ma k…®p.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 10:6 \xt Up 9.43\x*Na kabena ramoot ianna mana i toco Saimon, mana aiŇča ma amta Ňčgoaebta iŇčir iukca reikca morena ramoot. Ma manapmo mana kac maeacreke, na an ramootna kaca ande macait roumb maeacreke.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 7 Na RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča Koniliusmo, aindopacarica ma taŇčgatke. Koniliusa Ňčgepca ndona mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ramootniŇčapa, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot ianap, minmo aca mak…®pat. Na an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot tikca, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamma waraca raŇčgaireke, na ma Koniliusap eacrena.  
\v 8 Ri, Koniliusa an ramta…®r mbonkacmo, ndo ndaruatna reikta kambca minmo mataua mbopca maica, minmo mbag…®rica mina Iopa auŇč mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Pita ma manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča tamram ianna watatna 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 10:9 \xt Up 11.5\x*Na an ramta…®r, mina taŇčga r…®k naŇčgoca. Kabena ra mbuŇča mina taŇč, taŇčga maica Iopa auŇč aniaca rambuŇčairi, ra toco maica gaca r…®mb…®Ňča r…®Ňčna rambuŇčaina mori. Karica an m…®nna Pita mbendeina moca kacna kopik nagaca eacri.\fig Pita ma kac kopik tamuŇča t…®kca mbendeirena|src="GW162.tif" size="col" copy="Wade" ref="10.9" \fig* 
\v 10 Na ma nik wataica eacri, na mina amna reac kocrori, ma an amna reac amna ndabia eacaca manmb…®anmemraŇč mbuŇča tamram ian mawattat.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 10:11 \xt Up 11.5-17\x*Na an tambatna inikca ma wattatnanna, RaraŇč Aetaniacna tamuŇčna auŇča goottakeca, reac ianna an ŇčgetacndiŇča, anna ma raraŇčit aniaca ramta…®ra mana t…®pemb paur ŇčgutiŇčga aŇčg…®ra wambaraca keca, gan tiacarpaik nakacrepa irikri toc mairikri.  
\v 12 Na an raraŇčitna inikca, ainta orapa…®r paurna Ňčgoaebapa k…®rpirapa ainta reac, reacapa ainta Ňčgorikcap, anna inik ndeacrina.  
\v 13 Na Pita waracatnanna, kam ianna manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúPita, u Ňčgepca an amta Ňčgoaebmo mo menaca am.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 \x - \xo 10:14 \xt TN 11.1-47, na TW 14.3, na 14.7, na Esi 4.14\x*Ri, Pita rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúKacoot, gidik Ňčgoin aku karica! Memetmbaca aku eacreke, u watrena, aku mba an rat Ňčgocorta reikca mba ambrenanna. Na an ainta wand…®k t…®kca eacrena reikca aku mba ambrenanna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 \x - \xo 10:15 \xt Mt 15.11, na Mk 7.15, na 7.19, na Up 10.28, na Ro 14.14-20, na 1 Ko 10.25\x*Ri, an kamma manmo gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúAn reikmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca moa ratrinanna, u anmo rat Ňčgocorta reikca kai mbop teac.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 An reaca k…®dr…®k mbonkaca ainda mocarica. Karica an raraŇčitta tawi Ňčgoin motemma tamuŇčna auŇč mac nda magat. 
\p  
\v 17 Ainda moca Pita an reacna moca tamtam ndamŇčica aindopatna, ‚ÄúAuk watapekna manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamramma anna kaina m…®n…®Ňč?‚ÄĚ Pita, ma an manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamramna moca, tamtam ndamŇčiri mbuŇča, Koniliusna mbag…®riatna ramta…®r, mina k…®pca malarucat. Karica mina madigiat, ‚ÄúSaimonna kaca te?‚ÄĚ Ainda digica mina mimo wandacatna mbatca, an k…®patna ramta…®ra k…®pca t…®Ňč kamma w…®t…®kca.  
\v 18 Karica mina madigiat, ‚ÄúSaimonna wa, mana i ianna Pita, ma gan ndeacre ki, wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 \x - \xo 10:19 \xt Up 11.12, na 13.2\x*Ri, Pita ma ndona watatna manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamramna Ňčgagatracna moca anna ndamŇčiri, ŇäeroŇč Ratta manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU warac. Ramta…®r mbonkaca una moca orea k…®pca maeacreke.  
\v 20 Aintik u Ňčgepca irikca mina watca ne taŇč. U kai tamtami lamŇči teac. An ramta…®rmo auk mandaca k…®prina.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 21 Ri, Pita irikca an ramta…®ra watca minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNena orea taŇčrena ramoot, aku gade, na ne kaina nak…®prina?‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 \x - \xo 10:22 \xt Up 10.1-2, na 22.12\x*Ri, mina manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAn lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan Konilius, ma un aŇčg…®na ndopca aia k…®prina. An ramoot, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna torireke ma wandoŇč ndeacrena ramoot. Aintik Iudananda manmo ramoot laŇč ndoprena. Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč rat ianna, manmo un ndopna, u man ndambuŇča taŇčca, u mbop te, ma un mbopekna kam mbaracna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 \x - \xo 10:23 \xt Up 10.45, na 11.12\x*Karica Pita minmo aca mbukca mina an mouŇča manap Ňčgocarica, iŇčmbaia kabena ra mbuŇča ma minap Ňčgepca mina mataŇčgat. Na Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar ndeida an Iopa auŇč ndeacrenanna, mitoco Ňčgepca manap t…®kca minap mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Pita Konilius ndambuŇča taŇčgatna 
\p  
\v 24 Na Konilius, ma mana ndabiri, na ma ndona laiplacarapa ndona kamkabearmo aŇčg…®ra punica mina mana ndabiri, Pitaapa an ramta…®ra k…®p, k…®pca r…®k naŇčgoca, kabena ra mbuŇča mina k…®pca Sisaria auŇč aniac malaruat.  
\v 25 Karica Pita an t…®Ňča mbukatke, Koniliusa mana watca, Ňčgepca taŇčga mana outta tutupniŇč r…®mb…®tca mbiraca paŇčan maramtukat.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 10:26 \xt Up 14.13-15, na KIEK 19.10\x*Ri, Pita manmo mac nda aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepca aindopatna, ‚ÄúAuk toco, aku una kirar.‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Ri, Pita manap mbopa mbukatnanna, meikramta…®ra tumbun aniac t…®kca eacrinanna watca. 
\p  
\v 28 \x - \xo 10:28 \xt In 4.9, na Up 15.8-9, na Gal 2.12-14, na Epe 3.6\x*Ma minmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAina Iudananta t…®p kirara ne malamŇčireke, aia mba Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇč tambuŇčap mba eacrenanna, na min ndambuŇč toco mba taŇčga rambuŇčairenanna, anna wand…®k bagaraniac. Na tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniac ma aukmo manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇča wandaca aindopatna, ‚ÄėU aukna lamn…®ac watrenanna kabena meikramta…®rmo, gainda kai mbop teac, ne rat Ňčgocor, co minmo gainda mba lamŇčitndai, mina ramta…®r wand…®k, te, aia min tambuŇča kai taŇči m…®k teac. Aia ainda kai mo teac.‚Äô  
\v 29 Aintik nena kamma k…®papeke, aku karia mba mbopri, aku aindopatna, ‚ÄėLaŇč aku k…®pnande,‚Äô aindopca aku k…®prina. Na aku nenmo ainda diginande, ne kaina moca aukna moca mbaiŇč t…®krina, ne aukmo mbop?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 10:30 \xt Up 1.10, na 3.1\x*Ri, Koniliusa manmo aind mambopat, rai paur taŇčgapekna wigwaca, aukmo reac ianna laruatna, na an laruatna reaca gaind, maica rana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a irikca mbonkac toca t…®kri, aku ndona kac inikca t…®kca mbendeia eacri, na auk wattatnanna ramoot ianna reik gogror aoca maica aukna outta w…®t…®kca eacri, tik Ňčgapaoc mananna anna ma reac metacrina.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 10:31 \xt Dan 10.12, na Ib 6.10\x*Ri, ma aukmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúKonilius, RaraŇč Aetaniaca una mbembendeia ma waracrina. Na u reik kocorta meikramta…®r kotacrena kirarir unanna, RaraŇč Aetaniaca anna watca ma una moca malamŇčireke.  
\v 32 Aintik u ramta…®r ndeidmo mbag…®rica mina Iopa auŇča taŇčca Saimon Pitamo mbopca ma k…®p, an ramoot ma ndona i kabe Saimonap maeacreke, mana kaca ande macait roumbmbai maeacreke. An ramootta amta Ňčgoaebta iŇčir iukca reikca morena ramoot.  
\v 33 Aindopatna mbatca, aku una moca ramta…®rmo anduna mbag…®rica mina taŇčga unmo mbopca, u karia mba mbopri, u k…®prinan, na anna laŇč Ňčgoin. Na mandeaca aia muruŇča ganna t…®kca RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®ac Ňčgoutta u aimo Kacootta ai ndop ndopca unmo mbopatna kambca u aimo mbop te, aia waracna.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pita mbopatna kamb 
\p  
\v 34 \x - \xo 10:34 \xt TW 10.17, na 1 Sml 16.7, na Ro 2.11, na Gal 2.6, na Epe 6.9, na Kol 3.25, na 1 Pi 1.17\x*Ri, Pita Ňčgepca gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúGidik Ňčgoin, mandeac tik aku malamŇčica, RaraŇč Aetaniaca meikramta…®rmo, ma minmo muruŇča an kirar kabea morinan, mindacniŇč mandaia titocna tumbun ndeacrena meacramoot, ma minmo muruŇča an kirar kabea morina.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 10:35 \xt In 9.31, na Ro 2.13, na 1 Ko 12.13, na Gal 3.28, na Epe 3.6\x* Ainda moca an meikramta…®ra mandaibinna, tenna pitrik waŇč ndiŇč nak…®prinanda, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kamna kambca waraca t…®pemb kirarir wandoik teacrena meikramta…®r, ma ainta meikramta…®ra toŇčgorenan.  
\v 36 \x - \xo 10:36 \xt Ňäap 107.20, na Ais 52.7, na 57.19, na Mt 28.18, na Ro 10.12, na KIEK 17.14\x*Na gan kamma ne malamŇčireke, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nenmo IsraelnaŇčgepca neaŇčgatna kamma, ma an nikinik iro wetwetna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo Iesus mbuŇča neaŇčga nenmo gaindopatna, Iesus Karais ma meikramta…®r muruŇčna Kacoot. Na ma nenmo meikramta…®rmo, muruŇča moi aŇčg…®ri RaraŇč Aetaniacap iro kabea t…®kna morena ramoot.  
\v 37 \x - \xo 10:37 \xt Mt 4.12-17, na Lk 4.14\x*Na ne ndori malamŇčiri, an reikca Iudiana pitrik inikca muruŇč ndaruatke, ne watatna, na an reikca out Ňčgoinna Galili pitrik ndaruca eacri, na anna iŇčmbaia Ionna Ňčgaua meikramta…®rmo puk mbuŇča k…®tac pukca momona kam wembaŇč laŇča ma an wiwitiatna.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 10:38 \xt Mt 3.16, na Lk 4.17-20, na In 3.2, na Ib 1.9\x*Na ne Iesusmo lamŇčirena ma Nasaretna ramoot, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo larapaca ŇäeroŇč Ratapa gargar neaŇčgatna. Ri, ma an inikna auŇčembca tamtamma taŇčga meikramta…®rmo, opotac aniaca moatna. Ri, an m…®nna RaraŇč Aetaniaca Iesusap eacri, ma Paparuna Ramootta moa Ňčgocraiatna meikramta…®rmo, ma mac nda moa laiŇč mamoat.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 10:39 \xt Up 2.32, na 5.30\x*Ri, aia mana morina reikta kamb toprina ramta…®r, aintik ma aina Iudana pitrikapa, Ierusalemna inikna auŇč aniac t…®kca moatna reikta kam ndopatna. Na an ramootmo mina manmo ik naaŇčg…®a keraca, manmo ainda t…®kca moca moa mamenacat.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 10:40 \xt Up 2.24, na 1 Ko 15.4-7\x*Na karica ra mbuniŇč maica mbonkaca moatke, RaraŇč Aetaniaca Iesusmo mac nda moa Ňčgepca, ma meikramta…®rmo watna moca, ma manmo wattacarica ma minmo raek malaruat.  
\v 41 \x - \xo 10:41 \xt Lk 24.42-43, na In 14.17-24, na 15.27, na Up 1.8, na 13.31\x*Na ma aind ndaruatnanna, ma meikramta…®r tambuŇčmo muruŇča mba laruatke, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Ma muk ŇčgetacndiŇč naŇčgepca laruatnanna, ma RaraŇč Aetaniaca Ňčgaua ndona kam wiwiti ndopca larapacatna ramta…®r tambuŇč Ňčgoin malaruat. Na an larapacatna ramta…®ra, gade ai, na ma muk ndiŇč mac nda Ňčgepatke ma aiap mbiraca ambatna.  
\v 42 \x - \xo 10:42 \xt Mt 28.19-20, na Up 17.31, na Ro 14.9-10, na 2 Ko 5.10, na 2 Ti 4.1, na 1 Pi 4.5\x*Na ma aimo gaindopatna, ne meikramta…®rmo gaind Ňčgoinna wiwit mbop, ‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniac, ma an ramoot niŇčgikmo menaca maica eacrenanapa menac Ňčgocor ndeacrena meikramta…®rta ritri waparaca, mo ndopca larapacatna ramootta ande.‚Äô  
\v 43 \x - \xo 10:43 \xt Ais 33.24, na 53.5-6, na 53.11, na Ier 31.34, na Dan 9.24, na Mai 7.18, na Sek 13.1, na Ro 10.11, na Gal 3.22\x*Aintik RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morina ramta…®ra, an ramootna momona reikta kambca mina gainda wiwitiatna, ‚ÄėAn ramoot niŇčgikca meikramta…®ra mana r…®pac te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca mana i mbuŇča mina t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukara mo kecarinande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇča mina ŇäeroŇč Rat maaŇčg…®at 
\p  
\v 44 \x - \xo 10:44 \xt Up 4.31, na 8.15-16, na 11.15, na 15.8\x*Ri, Pita an kam ndopri mbuŇča, ŇäeroŇč Ratta min nambat Ňčgirikatnanna, an RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam mbaracri punica eacrena meikramta…®rmo, muruŇčcamiŇča mbukca m…®n mat…®kat.  
\v 45-46 \x - \xo 10:45-46 \xt Up 2.4, na 10.23, na 11.18, na 19.6, na Gal 3.14\x*Ri, Iudana r…®t…®pacapna ramta…®ra Pitaap k…®patnanna, an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇča ŇäeroŇč Ratta mbukca mina watri, an auŇčembta meikramta…®rta kamb puŇč topri, na RaraŇč Aetaniacna imo aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepri, mina anna waracatke, mina tamtam ndamŇčica aindopatna, ‚ÄúWatwa, an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca min motocmo otaca minmo ŇäeroŇč Ratta wanaiŇč ma neaŇčgat.‚ÄĚ Ri, Pita gaind mambopat,  
\v 47 \x - \xo 10:47 \xt Up 8.36, na 11.17, na 15.8-9, na Ro 10.12\x*‚ÄúAn meikramta…®ra opotacna ŇäeroŇč Rat maaŇčg…®ri, ainda moca aimo ramoot ianna minmo puk mbuŇča k…®tac pukca mo nake anna wand…®k t…®kna m…®nna wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ  
\v 48 \x - \xo 10:48 \xt Up 2.38\x*Ri, Pita an ŇäeroŇč Rat aŇčg…®rca eacrina meikramta…®rmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe ŇäeroŇč Rat maaŇčg…®ri, ne Iesus Karaisna i mbuŇča k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat.‚ÄĚ Ri, mina k…®tac puk aŇčg…®ra maica, mina Pitamo gainda digiatna, ‚ÄúU aiapmo raeniŇčap pac eac.‚ÄĚ 
\c 11  
\s1 Pita Ierusalemma taŇčga ndo ndaruatna reikta ninini mamoat 
\p  
\v 1 Karica an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rapa, Iudiana inikca tamtam ndeacrena Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara waracrina kamma, an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčna ndeid toco, RaraŇč Aetaniacna riptina kambca mina maaŇčg…®at.  
\v 2 Na an m…®nna Pita ma Ierusalem nagacatke, an Iesusa r…®pacrena ramta…®r ndeida mina Iudana r…®t…®pacapna ramta…®rmo mina manap ipuŇčga,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 11:3 \xt Up 10.28, na Gal 2.12\x*mina manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU kaina moca taŇčga an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčna auŇčembta ramta…®rap mbukca u minap amba taŇčrena?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 4 Ri, Pita mimo Ňčgepca ndo ndaruatna reikta nininimo ma gaind maniniat,  
\v 5 \x - \xo 11:5 \xt Up 10.9-48\x*‚ÄúAku Iopa auŇč aniacna inik ndeacatke, na an m…®nna aku mbendeia eacri, aku manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇča Ňčgagatrac ian mawatat. Na an Ňčgagatracna inikca aku wattatnanna, riac tamuŇč ŇčgetacndiŇča raraŇčit aniac tocna reac ianna anna ma ramta…®ra mana t…®pemb paur ŇčgutiŇčga gan w…®k…®nna auk ndambuŇč nakacrepa mairikat.  
\v 6 Na aku an raraŇčitna inikca wattatnanna, gan tiacarpaikna orapa…®r paurna reikapa, an meikramta…®ra neaŇčgabrena orapa…®r paurapa, raŇčna amta Ňčgoaebapa, k…®rpirapa riac tamuŇčna Ňčgorikcap eacri.  
\v 7 Na kam ianna aukmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėPita, u Ňčgepca an amta Ňčgoaebmo mo menaca am.‚Äô  
\v 8 Ri, aku nda rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄėKacoot, gidik Ňčgoin aku karica! Memetmbaca aku eacreke, u watrena aku mba an rat Ňčgocorta reikca mba ambrenanna. Na an ainta wand…®k t…®kca eacrena reik toca aukna upa mba mbukrenanna, wanaiŇč, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.‚Äô  
\v 9 Ri, an tamuŇčna auŇčna kamma aukmo gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄėAn reikmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca moa ratrinanna, u anmo rat Ňčgocorta reikca kai mbop teac.‚Äô  
\v 10 Na an reikca k…®dr…®kar mbonkac ndaruca, karica an reikca muruŇča tamuŇčna auŇč mac nda magat. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúNa an m…®n Ňčgoinna Sisaria auŇčna ramoot ianna, ma ramta…®r mbonkacmo auk ndambuŇča mbag…®rica k…®pca auk eacrena kac ndambuŇč malaruat.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 11:12 \xt In 16.13, na Up 10.19, na 10.23, na 10.45\x*Na ŇäeroŇč Ratta aukmo minap taŇčna moca gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU minap taŇč, u iroa tamtamma kai lamŇči teac.‚Äô Karica gan Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar parmbaiapa mbut kabea mina aukap Ňčgepca, aia an ramootna kaca taŇčga mambukat.  
\v 13 Ri, Koniliusa aimo an RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča mana kac inikca mbukca ma watatna kam ndopca, na an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča mamo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU ramta…®r ndeidmo mbag…®rica Iopa auŇča taŇčca Saimonna mbaiŇč t…®kca ma k…®p. Na mana i ianna Pita.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 11:14 \xt Up 16.31\x*Te, ma nenmo kamb ndeid topnande, na an kamma anna unapa una w…®w…®tnanmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nenmo muruŇč mac nda aŇčg…®nandet.‚Äô  
\v 15 \x - \xo 11:15 \xt Up 2.4\x*Karica aukmo aca k…®patna ramootta an kam ndopca maiatke, aku maica kam ndopri mbuŇča, ŇäeroŇč Ratta min nambat mairikat. Na Ňčgaua ma ai nambat, Ňčgirikatna kirarir toc mairikat.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 11:16 \xt Iol 2.28, na Mt 3.11, na In 1.26, na 1.33, na Up 1.5\x*Ainda moatke, aku Kacootta Ňčgau ndopatna kam mac nda malamŇčiat. Ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄėIonna ma meikramta…®rmo puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk neaŇčrena, na ne ŇäeroŇč Rat mbuŇča k…®tac puk aŇčg…®nande.‚Äô  
\v 17 \x - \xo 11:17 \xt Up 10.47, na 15.8-9\x*Na Ňčgaua aia Kacoot Iesus Karaismo r…®pacat tik, RaraŇč Aetaniaca aimo opotaca moca aimo ŇäeroŇč Ratta wanaiŇča neaŇčgatna. Ainda moca mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca min motocmo ma ainta opotacna kirar kabea moca, minmo ŇäeroŇč Ratta wanaiŇč maneaŇčgat. Aintik aku mandai, na aku an RaraŇč Aetaniaca mimo moatna aiŇčirmo, k…®racit?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 11:18 \xt Up 13.48, na 14.27, na Ro 10.12-13, na 15.9, na 15.16\x*Ainda moca an meikramta…®ra, nikembkatacarica ndorimo ipuŇčgrinanna, Pitana mbopatna kambca waracatke, mina runduikta iroar kecariatke, mina Ňčgepca RaraŇč Aetaniacna i aŇčg…®ra Ňčgepca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúMandeac tik aia RaraŇč Aetaniacna morena kirarira aia malamŇčica, ma an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanmo watcarica, mitoca iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica an iarwar ndeteacna wat aŇčg…®na moca.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Antiokna meikramta…®ra mar…®pacat 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 11:19 \xt Up 8.1-4\x*Ri, an m…®nna, mina Stipenmo moa menacatke, mina Iesusa r…®pacrena meikramta…®r motocmo, laŇča mba mori. Aintik mina w…®t aniaca Ňčgepca k…®pcarica auŇčembmo tamtam mataŇčgat. Ri, mina ndeida pitrik Ponisia taŇčgatke, ndeida mut Saiprusa taŇčgatke, ndeida auŇč aniaca Antiok mataŇčgat. Na mina ainda taŇčri, mina Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kabena meikramta…®rmo mba wiwitiri, wanaiŇč, mina Iudana wiwitna meikramta…®r tiŇčgikca wiwitiatna.  
\v 20 Na mina inikna tumbunna ramta…®r ndeida, mut Saiprusapa auŇč aniac Sairininan mitoco Ňčgepca Antiok auŇč aniaca taŇčga, mitoco Kacoot Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnan motocmo, an kam wembaŇč laŇč mawiwitiat.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 11:21 \xt Up 2.41\x*Ri, r…®pacrina meikramta…®rmo, Kacootta minmo otacri, an meikramta…®r w…®t aniacna tumbunna iroar inkar uriraca mina Ňčgepca Kacoot maraŇčgaiat. 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 11:22 \xt Up 4.36\x*Ri, an Ierusalem ndeacrina Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna, an kam wembaŇč mbaraca, ainda moca mina Ňčgepca Banambas mbag…®rica, ma Ňčgepca Antiok mairikat.  
\v 23-24 \x - \xo 11:23-24 \xt Up 2.41, na 5.14, na 6.5, na 11.21, na 13.43\x*Na Banambas ma ramoot laŇč Ňčgoin, ŇäeroŇč Ratta manmo mbukca lacakeca eacrena r…®t…®pac gargar aniacapna ramoot. Na ma Antioka taŇčga laruca wattatnanna, RaraŇč Aetaniaca an Antiok auŇčna meikramta…®r kotacrina kirarira watca, ma toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Ainda moca ma an Antiok auŇčna r…®pacatna meikramta…®rmo, mimitpacna kam ndopna naaŇčg…®ra punica, ma minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Kacoot Iesusa r…®pacrinanna, ndorita an r…®t…®paikca kai kecari teac.‚ÄĚ Ainda moca meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca k…®pca Kacoot maraŇčgaiat. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 11:25 \xt Up 9.30\x*Karica Banambasa Solna Ňčgorena moca Tarasus auŇč aniac mataŇčgat.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 11:26 \xt 1 Pi 4.16\x*Na ma taŇčga larua Solmo anna t…®kca watca, ma manap aŇčg…®ca maniŇča Antiok auŇč mac nda taŇčga, anna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunap eaca, maniŇča meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo riptia mori, minapmo gui kabena m…®nna minap maeacat. Na Antiok auŇč aniaca mina Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo mina minmo an i, Ňčgam neaŇčrinan, na an ia, ‚ÄúKaraisnand.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 11:27 \xt Up 13.1, na 15.32, na 21.9, na 1 Ko 12.28, na Epe 4.11\x*Ri, an m…®n mbuŇča rambca morena ramta…®r ndeida, Ierusalem t…®kcarica, mina Antiok auŇč mairikat.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 11:28 \xt Up 21.10\x*Ri, ramma morina ramoot ian, mina mana imo gaind Ňčgacrena Agabus, an ramoot ma ŇäeroŇč Ratna gargar mbuŇč naŇčgepca w…®t…®kca, ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúGan tiacarpaikna pitrikarta auŇčembca, nik wapataina makuk bagaraniac aŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ Aindopatna kamma eaca k…®pca Sisa Kolodiusa gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ndaruatna m…®n mbuŇča, an nik wapataina makukca an m…®n malaruat.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 11:29 \xt Ro 15.26, na 1 Ko 16.1, na 2 Ko 9.1\x*Ri, an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra Agabusna mboprina kam mbaraca, karica mina Ňčgepca ndorimo an Iudiana Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo kitukndukar puŇč Ňčgotacna kam leaca maica, mina Ňčgepca kitukndukarmo ndori t…®t…®kna m…®n naaŇčg…®ra t…®kca mamaiat.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 11:30 \xt Up 12.25\x*Karica mina Ňčgepca, Banambasapa Sol mbaniŇčmo an kitukndukar aŇčg…®ri taŇčna ndopca maniŇčna para t…®kca, maniŇča aŇčg…®ca taŇčga, Iudiananta r…®t…®pacna tumbunna outmbai ndeacrena ramta…®r paŇčaindta par mat…®kat. 
\c 12  
\s1 Erotta Iemismo moa menacatke, na Pitamo kac Ňčgoreac mat…®kat 
\p  
\v 1 An m…®n mbuŇča gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Erot, ma Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbun ndeidmo, t…®pemb Ňčgorik koindar mamori.\f + \fr 12:1 \ft Na an gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Erot Ag…®ripa, ma Ňčgauna Erot aniacna r…®mb…®n, na ma Ňčgaua gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ndeacri, Maria ma Iesusmo m…®ratna. Na an Erot Ag…®ripa ma gan gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripana aet.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 12:2 \xt Mt 4.21, na 20.23\x*Na ma ndo mbopca, mina Ionna lacaumbitac, Iemismo, mina bugrim mbuŇča manmo moa menacatna.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 12:3 \xt Up 4.3\x*Na Erot, ma ainda moatna t…®p mananna, Iudananda ainda watca, mina toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Aintik Erotta aind mac watatke, ma Ňčgepca Pitamo utiŇčga aŇčg…®ra kac Ňčgoreac mat…®kat. An t…®pna kirara, mina is kocorta tapac ambrena rai anikta ra ma an t…®p kirara morina.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 12:4 \xt NA 12.1-27\x*Erotta Pitamo utiŇčga aŇčg…®a kac Ňčgoreac mat…®kat. Na ma mana ŇčginaŇča mona moca lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®r parniŇčapa parmbaiapa mbut kabe aŇčg…®ca, minmo titaca paurpaurna tumnambca paura moca, mina Pitana ŇčginaŇča moa eacri. Na Erotta, mana toŇčtoŇča ma Pitamo an Pasowana Ra mai te, ma Pitamo aŇčg…®ri laruca meikramta…®r w…®t aniacna lamn…®acmo mana kambca ritri waparaca mona.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 12:5 \xt Ie 5.16\x*Ainda moca mina Pitamo aŇčg…®ca kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca ma an ndeacri. Na lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra mana ŇčginaŇča morina. Ri, Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mbembendei gargar Ňčgoin mamoat, te, RaraŇč Aetaniacmo man Ňčgotacna moca. 
\s1 MbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča Pitamo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca otaca ma malaruat 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 12:6 \xt Up 5.23\x*Karica Erot, ma Pitamo ritri waparacna moca, ra ian ŇčganŇčg…®a laruatke, an ra laruna moca moatna mouŇča, Pitamo mina mana parniŇčmo lawirta Ňčgat…®k mbuniŇč mbuŇča lapoca ruŇčrena ramootniŇčna parniŇčmo lamndea leaca maica, mamo aŇčg…®ra lapoca ruŇčrena ramootniŇčna k…®dr…®kca meraca ma maŇčgori. Na maniŇča mana ŇčginaŇča moa maeacri. Na an kac Ňčgoreacna t…®Ňča, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot mbuniŇč toco, anna ŇčginaŇča moa w…®t…®kca maeacri.\fig Mina Pitamo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca manmo lawirta Ňčgat…®k mbuŇča leacrina|src="GW165.tif" size="col" copy="Wade" ref="12.6" \fig* 
\v 7 Ainda moatke, RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča anduna nak…®pca laruca maw…®t…®kat. Na tacna memetaca an kac Ňčgoreacna inik mametacat. Na an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča Pitana kanmbacarpaik pica keca mamo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU tawina Ňčgep!‚ÄĚ Ri, an lawirta Ňčgat…®kca Pitana parniŇča leaca eacrinanna, anduna p…®arca mairikat.  
\v 8 Karica an RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU ndona waukmo leac te, ndona or ŇčgapaocniŇč aoc.‚ÄĚ Aindopca Pita ainda moatke. An mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča manmo gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúU ndona tik Ňčgapaoc rocot aoca Ňčgepca aukmo raŇčgai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 9 \x - \xo 12:9 \xt Up 10.3, na 10.17, na 11.5\x*Ri, Pita mana kamma waraca kac Ňčgoreac t…®kcarica mana raŇčgaica malaruat. Na an reikca an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč mbopca ma ainda moatnanna, ma anmo, ndomo manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇča wapat ndopca.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 12:10 \xt Ňäap 34.7, na Dan 3.28, na 6.22, na Up 5.19, na Ib 1.14, na 2 Pi 2.9\x*Karica maniŇča taŇčga an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morena ramootta mandaia t…®Ňčmo outmbaica w…®t…®kca eacrinanmo kunda, mac taŇčga kabenan mac kunda, maniŇča k…®pca an t…®Ňč gargar aniac ndaruca, na an t…®Ňča ma ndo garaca magootat, na an t…®Ňča ma auŇč aniaca taŇčrena taupmbai ndeacrenanna, maniŇča laruca taup an ndiŇča taŇčri. Na RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča Pitamo anduna t…®kcarica mataŇčgat. 
\p  
\v 11 Pitamo ainda moatke, an reikca mamo laruatke, ma iro aŇčg…®ca, ma gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAku mandeaca malamŇčica anna gidik Ňčgoin! Ganna Kacootta ndona mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇčmo mandaca auk ndambuŇč nak…®pca aukmo otaca Erotapa Iudananta meikramta…®ra aukmo, mo ndoprina reikca mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča aukmo aŇčg…®ra iukaiapeke, an reikca mba laruapekke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 \x - \xo 12:12 \xt Up 4.23, na 12.5, na 12.25, na 15.37\x*Karica ma Ňčgepca taŇčga Ionna aem Maria ndambuŇč malaruat, na Ionna i ianna Mak, na ma an kacn…®m ndaruatnanna, an kac inikca meikramta…®ra kocnaia mbukca punica mambendeiri.  
\v 13 Na Pita taŇčga raekca w…®t…®kca t…®Ňčmo piatke, an mbaiŇča morena mooŇč ianna mana ia Roda, ma t…®Ňč gootna nak…®patnanna.  
\v 14 Ma Pitana kamma warac rapaca ma toŇčgocarica, ma t…®Ňč goot nake mba lamŇčiatke. Ma nda ootta mbukca an meikramta…®rmo aind mambopat, ‚ÄúPita ande t…®Ňč kam maeacreke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 15 \x - \xo 12:15 \xt Mt 18.10, na Up 26.24\x*Ri, mina manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU ŇčaŇčaore ki?‚ÄĚ Ri, ma anduna gagra mambopri, ‚ÄúWanaiŇč! Pita monde t…®Ňč kamma w…®t…®kca maeacreke.‚ÄĚ Ri, mina manmo Ňčgepca aindopatna, ‚ÄúU mana ŇčeroŇča watapekna.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 12:15 \ft An m…®nna IudanaŇčgepta w…®tta mina gaind ndamŇčirena, mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčerŇčgaura mina ramoot kabe, kabena ŇčginaŇča mona aiŇčap. Na an ŇčeroŇč toco, ma ramootna kirar toc ndarurena.\f* 
\p  
\v 16 Mina ainda moatke, Pita ma t…®Ňčmo anduna mapiri, na mina t…®Ňč gootca wattatnanna ma anna w…®t…®kca eacri, mina Ňčgep Ňčgoreac maŇčgepat.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 12:17 \xt Up 13.16, na 19.33, na 21.40\x*Ri, Pita minmo watitina moca, ma par mbuŇč naaŇčg…®ra Ňčgagoa mambopat. Minmo, an Kacootta manmo otaca kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca aŇčg…®a laruatna nininimo ninia maica, ri, ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe taŇčca Iemisapa Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo mbop.‚ÄĚ Na iŇčmbaia ma minmo t…®kcarica kabena auŇč mataŇčgat.\f + \fr 12:17 \ft Na an Iemisa ma Iesusna lapmbitac. U Galesia sapta 1 wes 19na timbiŇčna raparna inikmo wat. Na ma Ierusalemna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunna ramoot paŇčanna larurina.\f* 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 12:18 \xt Up 5.22-24\x*Karica ŇčaŇčarmuŇča an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra, Pitana moca an inikca wattatnanna, ma kamaind. Ri, mina rugdar moca Ňčgepca ndorimo tamtamma digica aindopatna, ‚ÄúMa titoca taŇčgapek?‚ÄĚ  
\v 19 Ri, Erotta ramta…®r ndeid mbag…®rica mina Pitana moca, an auŇč inikmo muruŇča orea tambca, manmo wat Ňčgocor. Aintik Erot, ma an kac Ňčgoreacna, ŇčginaŇča morena lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rmo digia tambacariatke, ma minmo mo menacna kam mambopat. Na iŇčmbaia Erotta Iudia pitrik t…®kcarica ma irikca Sisaria auŇč aniac ndaruca ma an maeacat. 
\s1 Erotta mamenacat 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 12:20 \xt 1 GRP 5.9-11, na Esi 27.17\x*Na gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Erot tikca, ma auŇč aniacniŇč Tairapa Saidonna meikramta…®rmo nikkakat aniacap eacreke. Aintik mina man bubuocrena pitrikna amta reik aŇčg…®renan tik, mina anna moca, ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica taŇčca mana watca ndorita kakadmai wandaca an kaega moi menacna moca. Na out Ňčgoinna, mina taŇčca mana Ňčgogona diabna inikna ŇčginaŇča morena ramoot paŇčan Blastusmo mbopca, ma minmo laŇč ndopatna mbatca. IŇčmbaia mina taŇčga Erotmo watca manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU aina nakadmaica aia an kaega moi menacna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 21 Ri, Erotta minmo ra ian lamarapacat, na an ra laruatke, ma ndona gagrirta lamboi aoca ndona gagrirta ramta…®ra mbiracrina taupca mbiraca, meikramta…®rmo kam aniaca keca mambopat.  
\v 22 Ri, an meikramta…®ra mana kamma waraca, mina kamb keca aindopatna, ‚ÄúGanna ramootna kamma wanaiŇč, anna m…®r…®praraŇč ianna kam.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 \x - \xo 12:23 \xt 1 Sml 25.38, na 2 Sml 24.17, na Ňäap 115.1, na Dan 5.20\x*Karica ma mina kambca waraca maica ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna i aniacmo mba aŇčg…®a Ňčgepatke. Aintik RaraŇč Aetaniacna mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča anduna manmo roumb Ňčgoreac ian maneaŇčgat. Na anduna nduip tekira mana nikinik inikca ambacarica ma mamenacat. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 12:24 \xt Ais 55.11, na Up 6.7, na 19.20, na Kol 1.6\x*Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma, kocnaia gagaraca taŇčga meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca waraca mamaiat. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 12:25 \xt Up 11.29-30, na 12.12, na 13.5, na 13.13, na 15.37\x*Ri, Banambasapa Sola ndoniŇčna Ierusalem nak…®patna aiŇč maiatna mbatca, maniŇča Antiok auŇč aniaca taŇčna moatke, maniŇča, Ionap aŇčg…®ca mataŇčgat, na mana i ianna mina Mak Ňčgacrena. 
\c 13  
\ms1 Pola Iesusna kambca pitrik w…®t aniaca t…®kca mambopat 
\mr (13.1‚ÄĒ21.14) 
\s1 Mina Banambasapa Sol mbaniŇčmo kam wembaŇč laŇčna kam ndopna moca larapacatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Up 11.27\x*Na an Antiok auŇčna, Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna, mina ndeida RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morenan, na mina ndeida ririptica morena ramta…®r, mina anna inik ndeacrena. Mina iremb tikca, ianna Banambas, na ianna Simeon, mina manmo Tik Mb…®kmb…®kna ramoot Ňčgacrena, na ianna Lusius ma Sairini auŇč aniacna ramoot, na ianna Sol, na ianna Manain, ma gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Erotna bubuocna kaŇčgauk ndeacrena ramoot ian.\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Na an i Tik Mb…®kmb…®kna ramoot, anna mina gaind ndamŇčirena ma Apirikana pitrikna ramoot.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 13:2 \xt Up 9.15, na Ro 10.15, na Gal 1.15, na Epe 3.7-8, na 1 Ti 2.7, na Ib 5.4\x*Na oit ianna meikramta…®ra Kacootta raŇčgairinanna, manmo tutpemb r…®mb…®tca mbendeiri, amna reacmo wariraca eacri. Na ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Banambasapa Solmo larapac, maniŇčmo aku an aiŇča mona aca k…®patna ramootniŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 \x - \xo 13:3 \xt Up 6.6\x*Ainda moca mina gagamna reikmo wariracri, na mina ndorita pa…®rmo maniŇč nambatta t…®kca mbendeia maica, karica maniŇčmo mbag…®rica maniŇča mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Banambasapa Sol mbaniŇča Saiprus muta t…®kca, kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma anna t…®kca mawiwitiri 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 13:4 \xt Up 15.39\x*Karica ŇäeroŇč Ratta maniŇčmo mandaca maniŇča taŇčga Selusia auŇč aniac Ňčgirikca an ndaruca, anna t…®kca maniŇča laŇčgum mbuŇča lembaia taŇčga Saiprus Ňčgacrina mut nagaca.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 13:5 \xt Up 12.12, na 12.25, na 13.13, na 13.46, na 15.37\x*Karica maniŇča taŇčga Salamis auŇč aniac ndaruca, maniŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo, an Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaik inkara t…®kca mawiwitiri. Na Ion Mak, ma toco maniŇčap taŇčga, maniŇčmo otacrina. 
\p  
\v 6 Karica maniŇča an Saiprus mut kataca an inikna auŇčembca taŇč, taŇčga, taŇčga Papos auŇč aniac ndaruca. An auŇč inikna ramoot ian mawattat, na mana ia Bariesus. Na an ramoot tikca, ma reac, reacna ndururca morinan, na ma toco Iudananta paparuna ramma morena ramoot.  
\v 7 Na an ramoot tikca, memetmbaca ma ramoot paŇčan Sergius Paulusap eacrena. Na Sergius Paulus tikca iro landamŇči laŇčapna ramoot, na ma Ňčgepca ndomo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam mbarac ndopca, Banambasapa Solna mbaiŇč t…®kca.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 13:8 \xt 2 Ti 3.8\x*Ri, an ndururca morena ramootmo, mina mana aimo Girikna kam mbuŇča i Elimas t…®kca maacat. Na ma Banambasapa Sol mbaniŇčna mbopekna kam wembaŇč laŇča ramoot paŇčanmo Ňčarikca anna waraca Iesusa r…®pac narica, ma maniŇčna morina aiŇčira moa maŇčgocrairi.  
\v 9 Na wanaiŇč, ŇäeroŇč Ratta Solmo mbukca lacamakecat, na mana i ianna Pol. Na Pola Elimasmo wat gargar Ňčgoinna watta taŇčga manmo gaind mambopat,  
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Mt 13.38, na In 8.44, na 1 Io 3.8\x*‚ÄúU Paparuna Ramootna nuoc Ňčgoin. Ainda moreke, u t…®pemb kirarir wandoik laiŇčmo aŇčg…®ra ndona puŇčndamootta moca, anna moa Ňčgocrairena. Ri, an paparuarta iroara una iro inikca m…®n Ňčgoin ndeacreke. Na u memetmbaca parureke, u Kacootna kamb gidkarta taupmo u memetmbaca moa Ňčgocrairena. Na u an iro Ňčgoreaca t…®kcarina toawanaiŇč ki?  
\v 11 \x - \xo 13:11 \xt NA 9.3, na 1 Sml 5.6, na Up 9.8\x*Mandeaca u warac. Kacootta una lamn…®acniŇčmo mandeaca ndona gargar mbuŇča mo te, una lamn…®acniŇča Ňčgocrainande, na u mba watitndai. Kocnai nenepucarica u mba rana memetac emtemma mba mac watitndai. U ainda raeniŇč ndeacnande.‚ÄĚ Pola aindopca maiatke, anduna, reac ianna anna ma wau toc Ňčgirikca manenepucat, ri, Elimasna lamn…®acniŇčmo aŇčg…®ra mboraca ma watna m…®nna wanaiŇč. Ainda moca ma ramta…®rmo ndo Ňčgutica taup wandac ndopca, Ňčgepca ramta…®rta moca wanaiŇč mabadairi.  
\v 12 Na ramoot paŇčanna aind ndaruapekna reikca watca, iro mananna an Pola Kacootna mbopapekna kamb wembaŇč laŇča waraca, ma Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca ma mar…®pacat. 
\s1 Polapa Banambasa Pisidiana pitrikca taŇčga Antiok auŇč aniacmo kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwitina mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 13:13 \xt Up 13.5, na 15.38\x*Karica Polapa manap taŇčrina ramta…®ra Papos auŇč t…®kcarica, laŇčgumma minmo aŇčg…®rca mataŇčgat. Na mina taŇčga Perga auŇč aniacna inikna pitrik Pampilia nagaca. Ri, Ion Makca min t…®kcarica Ierusalemma nda mataŇčgat.  
\v 14 Mina Perga auŇč t…®kcarica, mina kocnaia taŇčga Pisidiana pitrik inikna auŇč aniac Antiok ndaruca. Ri, W…®kt…®t…®kna Ra mina taŇčga Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mbukca anna mbiracrina.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 13:15 \xt Lk 4.16, na Up 13.27, na 15.21, na Ib 13.22\x*Ri, an Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaikta ramta…®r paŇčainda, an T…®p Wand…®kapa RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morina ramta…®rta tirca eacrina kamb topca maica. Karica mina Polapa manap taŇčrena ramta…®rmo kam emtem ndopna moca, ramoot ian mbag…®rica ma taŇčga minmo mbaiŇč t…®kca aindopatna, ‚ÄúLaiplacar, ne gan meikramta…®rmo kam emtemma mbop ndop te, kam kocor ne mbop.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 13:16 \xt Up 12.17\x*Karica Pola Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca par mbuŇča minmo k…®raca gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNe IsraelnaŇčgepapa an RaraŇč Aetaniacmo torirena ramta…®ra, ne matau warac.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 13:17 \xt NA 1.7, na 6.6, na TW 7.6-7, na Ňäap 105.23-24\x*IsraelnaŇčgepta RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma aina nicar Ňčgamrirmo atuna larapaca babuatna, mina mana meikramta…®r koind. Aintik mina ndorita auŇč tiacarpaik t…®kcarica taŇčga Isip ndeacri, ma minmo moa meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca malaruat. Na iŇčmbaia mana gargar mbuŇča, ma IsraelnaŇčgepmo Isipa t…®kca mac nda aŇčg…®rca, minmo taup wandaca minmo aŇčg…®ra mak…®pat.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 13:18 \xt NA 16.35, na Ndu 14.34, na TW 1.31, na Ňäap 95.10, na Up 7.36\x*Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo an ramta…®r kocorta taupca t…®kca, ma mina makukara aŇčg…®ca taŇčga guiara 40na m…®n mat…®kat.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 13:19 \xt TW 7.1, na Ios 14.1, na Ňäap 78.55\x*Na an Kenan tiacarpaikna inik ndeacrina parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇčna pitrik waŇčna meikramta…®rmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo moa topatke, an mina tiacarpaikmo, ma aŇčg…®ca ndona IsraelnaŇčgepta meikramta…®r neaŇčga an tiacarpaikca minan mamoat.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 13:20 \xt RP 2.16, na 1 Sml 3.20\x*Na an reikca laruatnanna, anna 450na guiarpaikna inik mbuŇč ndarua mamaiat. Na an guiarpaikna iŇčmbaia IsraelnaŇčgepca tiacarpaik aŇčg…®ca eacri, RaraŇč Aetaniaca IsraelnaŇčgep raupŇčina moca ramta…®r paŇčaind anik ndepik larapaca mina IsraelnaŇčgepmo raupŇčia k…®pca aŇčg…®ra Samuela RaraŇč Aetaniacna ramma morina ramootta eacrina m…®n malaruat. 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 13:21 \xt 1 Sml 8.5, na 8.19, na 10.1, na 10.21\x*‚ÄúKarica an m…®nna an meikramta…®ra ndorimo gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ian larapac ndopca, RaraŇč Aetaniacmo digiatna mbatca, RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo Kisna nuoc Solmo lamarapacat, na an ramoot tikca ma Bensamenna barna ramoot, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo larapaca ma mina gagrirta ramoot paŇčanna moca, min raupŇčia k…®pca guiara 40na m…®n.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Sml 13.14, na 15.23-26, na 16.12-13, na 2 Sml 2.4, na Ňäap 89.20, na Osi 13.11\x*Karica anna iŇčmbaia RaraŇč Aetaniaca Solmo moa kecariatke, ma Dewitmo mina gagrirta ramoot paŇčan naaŇčg…®ra larua lamarapacat. Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca meikramta…®rmo Dewitna morina kirarirta kam laŇčmo ma an wiwitiatna, ‚ÄėAku, Iesina nuoc Dewitna iro inikca atuna watta lamŇčirina, ainda moca aukna iro inikca an ramootmo toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. Aku lamŇčirena, ma aukna toŇčgorena reikca aku mamo mo ndopekna reikca ma monande.‚Äô  
\v 23 \x - \xo 13:23 \xt 2 Sml 7.12-16, na Ňäap 132.11, na Ais 11.1, na Lk 1.32, na 1.69, na Ro 11.26\x*Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma ndomo ainda mo ndopca atuna babuatna kirara, ma aind mamoat. Na an ramootta ma Dewitna barna ramoot ian, aintik RaraŇč Aetaniaca ai mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot ianmo an IsraelnaŇčgep maneaŇčgat, na an ramoot tikca Iesus. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 13:24 \xt Mt 3.1-2, na Mk 1.4, na Lk 3.3, na Ro 11.26\x*‚ÄúAn m…®nna Iesusa ndona aiŇča mo Ňčgocor ndeacri, k…®tac pukca neaŇčrena ramoot Ion, ma IsraelnaŇčgepmo iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica k…®tac puk aŇčtaŇčg…®na kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma an mawiwitiat.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 13:25 \xt Mt 3.11, na Mk 1.7, na Lk 3.16, na In 1.20-27\x*Na maica Ionna ndona aiŇč maina moatke, ma gaind madigiat, ‚ÄėNe aukmo mandai ndamŇčire? Aku an nena lambirena ramootta, mandaia nemo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramootta, wanaiŇč. Na ne matau warac. Aku ramoot laŇč Ňčgoinna wanaiŇč, na aukna iŇčmbai nak…®pekna ramootta, ma aukmo tamuŇč Ňčgoin. Aintik aku mana ort…®mb…®kniŇč aoca eacrena Ňčgat…®kniŇč p…®arna m…®nna wanaiŇč.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 13:26 \xt Mt 10.6, na Lk 24.47, na Up 13.16, na 13.46\x*‚ÄúAintik min laiplacar, ne Abraamna bar ndeacrenanapa an RaraŇč Aetaniaca torirena ramta…®r, ne muruŇča warac. Gan kamma RaraŇč Aetaniaca meikramta…®r mac nda aŇčg…® ndopatna kamma, anna RaraŇč Aetaniaca aimo neaŇčga k…®patna kam.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 13:27 \xt Lk 23.34, na 24.20, na 24.44, na In 16.3, na Up 3.17, na 15.21, na 1 Ko 2.8\x*Na an meikramta…®ra Ierusalem ndeacrinandapa, mina ramta…®r paŇčaindap, mina memetmbaca W…®kt…®t…®kna Raia mina an rambca morina ramta…®rta mbopatna kambca mina waracrina, na an ramoot Iesusmo ndori mac nda aŇčtaŇčg…®na kambca, mina mba lamŇčia rapacatke, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Ainda moca mina manmo mo menacna moca matimndacat. Na mina ainda moatnanna, mina atuna an rambca morina ramta…®ra mbopatna ramta…®rta kambca mina ainda moatke, mina an kambmo moa m…®n mat…®kat.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 13:28 \xt Mt 27.22-23, na Mk 15.13-14, na Lk 23.21-23, na In 19.15\x*Na mina Iesusna moatna t…®p Ňčgoreac ianna wat Ňčgocor, na mina manmo wanaiŇč Ňčgoinna mo menacna moca, Pailatmo mana mo menacna moca wanaiŇč Ňčgoin matimndacat.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 13:29 \xt Mt 27.57-61, na Mk 15.42-47, na Lk 18.31, na 23.50-56, na In 19.28-30, na 19.36-42\x*Na mina manmo atuna rambca moca mbopatna ramta…®rta kambta kirar Ňčgoinna, ramta…®ra manmo ainda moca maiatna mbatca, mana raŇčgairena ramta…®ra manmo ik nakeraca eacrinanna t…®kca aŇčg…®ra irikca, aŇčg…®ra taŇčga mamutocat.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 13:30 \xt Mt 28.6, na Up 2.24\x*Mina manmo ainda moatke, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo muk inikca t…®kca mac nda moa maŇčgepat.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 13:31 \xt Up 1.3, na 1.8\x*Karica rai w…®t aniaca meikramta…®ra Galili Ňčgetaca ndiŇča Ierusalemma Iesusap taŇčgatnanda, anna watta maica. An meikramta…®ra Iudana meikramta…®rmo an wiwitiatna. 
\p  
\v 32 \x - \xo 13:32 \xt RL 12.3, na Up 13.23, na Ro 4.13, na Gal 3.16\x*‚ÄúAinda moca aia nenmo an bababuna kam wembaŇč laŇča, RaraŇč Aetaniaca aina nicar Ňčgamrirca babuatnanna, aia nemo an ndoprena.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 13:33 \xt Ňäap 2.7, na Ro 1.4, na Ib 1.5, na 5.5\x*Na mandeaca ma Iesusmo muk inikca t…®kca mac nda moa Ňčgepapeknanna, ma ndona an bababua aimo mina mombonik puŇčga t…®kca moa m…®n mat…®kri. Na an reacna kamma, Ňäap 2na inikna timbigta kapna Ňäaparta inik maeacreke. Na an kamma gaindoprina, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄėU aukna nuoc. 
\q1 Na mandeaca aku una aet malaruri.‚Äô 
\b  
\m  
\v 34 \x - \xo 13:34 \xt Ais 55.3\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma Iesusmo mukca t…®kca mac nda moa Ňčgeprinanna, ma mba muk inikca mba mac nda irikca anna mba mac kotiminkitndai. Ainda moca RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma aindopatna, ‚ÄėAku nenmo mataui raupŇči te, nenmo reik laiŇč, laiŇč neaŇčnande, na atua aku gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Dewitap babua mbopatna kirar. Na an reikca aku mbopapeknanna, iŇčmbaia ma gidik Ňčgoin ndarunande, gade aku mbopapekna kirar Ňčgoin ndarunandet.‚Äô  
\v 35 \x - \xo 13:35 \xt Ňäap 16.10, na Up 2.27, na 2.31\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapna inik ndeacrena kam t…®p ian toca gaind, ‚ÄėU ndona babuekna Ramoot Ratmo, u mba watcarica ma mba muk inikca mba mac kotiminkitndai.‚Äô  
\v 36 \x - \xo 13:36 \xt 1 GRP 2.10, na Up 2.29\x*Na aia muruŇč malamŇčireke, Dewitta, atua ma gan tiacarpaik ndeacri, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna kambca ma mataua raŇčgairina ramoot. Na iŇčmbaia ma menacatke, mina mana wa…®rmo aŇčg…®ra taŇčga mana nicar mutocatna taupca mutoca mana wa…®ra an maminkiat.  
\v 37 Na an ramoot, RaraŇč Aetaniaca manmo muk inikca t…®kca mac nda moa Ňčgepatna ramootta, ma mba muk inikca mba t…®kca kootatke, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.  
\v 38-39 \x - \xo 13:38-39 \xt Ais 53.11, na Dan 9.24, na Lk 24.47, na Up 10.43, na Ro 3.28, na 8.3, na 10.4, na Ib 7.19, na 1 Io 2.12\x*Ainda moca laiplacar, aia nenmo an kambca aindoprenanna, ne anmo matau lamŇči rapac. An ramoot, ma nena t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukara mo kecarina nak…®patna. Na Mosesna T…®p Wand…®kca nenmo mba otaca nena makukara mba mo kecarica, ne ramta…®r laiŇčga mba mac laruitndai. Na gan ramoot Iesus mbuŇča meikramta…®ra mandaia mana ia waraca r…®pac te, nena makukara ma mo kecarinande.  
\v 40 \x - \xo 13:40 \xt Ais 29.14\x*Ainda moca ne ndoritake mataui wat. Atua RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morina ramta…®r mbopatna reikca Ňčarikca nen mbuŇč ndaru nari. Mina aindopatna,  
\v 41 \x - \xo 13:41 \xt Aba 1.5\x*‚ÄėNe peperearta kamb toprena meikramta…®r, aku an reikmo, nena k…®dr…®kara t…®kca mo te, na ne wati rugdar monandet, na ne menacnande. Ramoot ian ma nenmo an auk momona reikta kambca, an wiwiti te, ne warac te, ne mba mac r…®pacitndai.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 42 Pola an kamb topca maica, karica manapa Banambas, maniŇča min t…®kcarica Ňčgepca raek ndaruna mori, na meikramta…®ra maniŇčmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOŇčgo taŇčca gan raita Ňčgatna W…®kt…®t…®kna Ra mbuŇča, oŇčgo mac nda k…®pca aimo an reikta ninini ndeid mac nini te, aia waracna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 43 \x - \xo 13:43 \xt Up 11.23, na 14.22, na Ta 2.11, na Ib 12.15, na 1 Pi 5.12\x*Karica mina an Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kac t…®kcarica raekmbai malaruat, ri, Iudana meikramta…®r w…®t aniacapa Iudamo raekmbaina Iudananta r…®pacrina r…®t…®paca, r…®pacrena ramta…®ra mina Ňčgepca Polapa Banambasa raŇčgaica, maniŇčap laruatke. ManiŇča an meikramta…®rmo kamb an mac wiwitia mbopca malaruri, na mina iroar inkarca moa Ňčgepca, minmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgaica mana kakadmaina kirarira raŇčgaina moca. 
\p  
\v 44 Karica an W…®kt…®t…®kna Ra laruatke, maica an auŇčna meikramta…®ra mina muruŇčcamiŇča k…®pca punica, Polapa Banambasmo Kacootna kam ndop te, mina ndorimo anna waracna.  
\v 45 \x - \xo 13:45 \xt Up 14.2, na 18.6, na 1 Pi 4.4, na Iu 1.10\x*Na Iudananda aind mbatatke, mina minmo titikca moca mina Ňčgepca Polna mboprina kambta Ňčaia, manmo peperena kamb Ňčgorik mambopat.  
\v 46 \x - \xo 13:46 \xt Ais 55.5, na Lk 7.30, na Up 3.26, na 18.6, na Ro 1.16, na 10.19\x*Ainda moca Polapa Banambas, maniŇča Ňčgepca minmo kam gargar mbuŇča gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAnna gidik, aŇčga nemo Iudanandmo out Ňčgoinna nenmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam ndopatke, ne an kam mbarac narica, anna moca ne iŇč maneaŇčri, na an kirara ne ainda moapeknanna, anna ne gaindopapekna, ‚ÄėAia iarwarna eteacna wat aŇčtaŇčg…®a aia karica,‚Äô aintik ne matau warac. AŇčga mandeaca nenmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam ianna mba mac mbopitndai, aŇčga Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnand tiŇčgik ndopnande.  
\v 47 \x - \xo 13:47 \xt Ais 42.6, na 49.6, na Lk 2.32\x*Aintik Kacootta aimo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAku un mbuŇča Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo memetac neaŇč te, u aukna gan tiacarpaikna auŇčembta meikramta…®rmo muruŇč Ňčgotac te, aku minmo muruŇč mac nda aŇčg…®nande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 48 \x - \xo 13:48 \xt Up 11.18\x*Ri, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda an kam mbaraca, mina toŇčtoŇč aniac Ňčgoin, na mina Kacootna kam wembaŇč laŇč aŇčg…®ra Ňčgeprina. Na Kacootna iarwarna eteacna wat aŇčg…®na larapacrina meikramta…®r mina mar…®pacat.  
\v 49 Na mina Ňčgepca Kacootna kam aŇčg…®ca Ňčgepca an pitrikna inikca mbukca an kam wiwitia mbopca mataŇčri.  
\v 50 \x - \xo 13:50 \xt Up 17.4, na 17.12\x*Na Iudana meikramta…®rapa mina inikna irembapna meikca RaraŇč Aetaniacmo torirenanapa, mina auŇčna ŇčginaŇča morena ramta…®r paŇčaindap, an auŇčna meikramta…®rta iroara moa Ňčgepca mina nikembkatca mina Ňčgepca Polapa Banambasmo kaega moca, maniŇčmo an auŇč ndeac narica mbopca maniŇča mataŇčgat.  
\v 51 \x - \xo 13:51 \xt Mt 10.14, na Mk 6.11, na Lk 9.5, na 10.11, na Up 18.6\x*Ainda moatke, maniŇča Ňčgepca ndoniŇčna orniŇčna tiacar makacopat, na an kirara an auŇčna meikramta…®ra moapeknanna, anna t…®p laŇča wanaiŇč. Karica maniŇča Antiok auŇč t…®kcarica, maniŇča Ňčgepca Aikoniam auŇč mataŇčgat.\f + \fr 13:51 \ft IudanaŇčgepna t…®pca gaind, an orniŇčna tiacar kacoprenanna, anna mina an auŇčmo mba mac nda taŇčitndai. Na aina our tukica taŇčrena t…®p toco anna kirar.\f* 
\v 52 \x - \xo 13:52 \xt Mt 5.12, na In 16.22, na Up 2.46\x*Na an Antiok auŇčna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r tikca, ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo mbukca m…®nna t…®kca mina toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin. 
\c 14  
\s1 Polap Banambasa Aikoniam auŇč aniaca mbukca minmo kam wiwitiatna 
\p  
\v 1 Mon Aikoniam auŇč aniaca Polapa Banambas, maniŇča an auŇč aniacna inikca mbukca an nandmo, maniŇča Antiok auŇč ndeacatke, mbopatna kambta kirarir koinda, maniŇča Aikoniamnandmo Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacna inikca taŇčga mbukca, minmo an kambta m…®niŇč koind topri, na IudanaŇčgepapa Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda mina w…®t toco, mina muruŇča mar…®pacat.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 14:2 \xt Up 13.45\x*Ri, Iudana meikramta…®r ndeida Iesusmo r…®pac Ňčgocor, mina Ňčgepca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta ndeidta iroar inkarca moa Ňčgepca, mina iroar Ňčgorik aŇčg…®ca Ňčgepca, an Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo maipuŇčgat.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 14:3 \xt Mk 16.20, na Up 19.11, na Ib 2.4\x*Ri, Polapa Banambas, maniŇča Aikoniam auŇčna inikmo k…®dr…®k rocot Ňčgoinna, maniŇča an ndeacri, na maniŇča Kacoot Iesusna kakadmaina kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwiti nake, rugutta mo Ňčgocor, maniŇča ainda morina. Na Kacoot Iesusa maniŇčmo Ňčgagatracara momona gargar neaŇčga, maniŇča ainta Ňčgagatracar ndeid t…®kca malaruat. Na an t…®pna kirara Kacoot Iesusa maniŇč mbuŇča meikramta…®ra wandacatna. Na an kambca maniŇča mboprenanna, anna paparua wanaiŇč, anna gidik, gidik Ňčgoin.  
\v 4 Aintik an auŇč aniacna meikramta…®ra, titaca tumbun mbuniŇč mamoat. Ndeida Iudananda raŇčgaiatke, ndeida an up aŇčg…®rena ramootniŇč maraŇčgaiat.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 14:5 \xt Up 14.19, na 2 Ti 3.11\x*Ainda moatke, iŇčmbaia Iudanandapa Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandap mina Ňčgepca ndorita ramta…®r paŇčaindap t…®kca, kam leaca mina Polapa Banambasmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca moca, maniŇčmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňč menacna mori. 
\s1 Polapa Banambasa Likonia pitrikca mbukca anna meikramta…®rmo an kamb wembaŇč laŇčna kam mawiwitiat 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 14:6 \xt Mt 10.23\x*Karica Polapa Banambasmo an meikramta…®ra maniŇčmo ainda mona moatna kamma, maniŇča anna waracatke, maniŇča k…®pcarica Likonia pitrik aniacna auŇčniŇč Listaraapa Derbeapa an inikna auŇčemb mataŇčgat.  
\v 7 Ri, maniŇča an auŇčemb motocmo an kam wembaŇč laŇčna kam anmo wiwitia mbopca mataŇčri. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 14:8 \xt In 9.1, na Up 3.2\x*Ri, Listara auŇčna inikna ramoot ianna, mana aemma manmo ainda m…®ratna, na ma mooŇčnuoc tekernoc ndeacri, mana ort…®mb…®kniŇča menaca ma mba Ňčgepca taŇčrenanna.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 14:9 \xt Mt 8.10, na 9.28-29, na Up 3.4\x*Ri, an ramootta Pola wiwitirina kamma, ma waraca eacri, na Pola an ramoot Ňčgoinna watna taŇčna malamŇčiat, an ramootta ma r…®pacrina RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma manmo moi laŇča monande.  
\v 10 Aintik Pola kam aniac Ňčgoin keca an ramootmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU Ňčgepca ndona ort…®mb…®kniŇč mbuŇča w…®t…®k.‚ÄĚ Ri, an ramootta putrikica Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca ndona ort…®mb…®kniŇč mbuŇč mataŇčri. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 14:11 \xt Up 8.10, na 28.6\x*Ri, meikramta…®rta tumbunna Polna moatna Ňčgagatraca watca, mina Likoniana kamb mbuŇča gaindopatna, ‚ÄúMandeaca m…®rpembraraiŇčga ramootna kirarir toca moca, ai ndambuŇč mairikri!‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Ri, an meikramta…®ra Ňčgepca Banambasmo i Sus maacat, na Pol tikca ma kam ndopna ramoot ian, aintik mina manmo i Ermes mat…®kat.\f + \fr 14:12 \ft Girikna meikramta…®ra gainda r…®pacrena, m…®rpembraraiŇč w…®t toco eacrena. Na m…®r…®praraŇč Sus ma mina gagrirta m…®r…®praraŇč paŇčan, na Ermes, ma kamb aŇčg…®ra taŇč k…®prena m…®r…®praraŇč.\f* 
\v 13 Na m…®r…®praraŇč Sus, mana mbendeina kaca an auŇč aniacna wuocna t…®Ňč roumbmo raekmbai ndeacri, an kacna ŇčginaŇča morina taup ndamootapa, meikramta…®ra Ňčgepca bulmakao ramooteniŇčapa witacatna kokocarap aŇčg…®ca, mina ndorimo taŇčga Polapa Banambasmo an mbuŇča g…®mbamba mo ndopca mamori. 
\p  
\v 14 Ainda moca, maniŇča an kam mbaracatke, maniŇča Ňčgepca ndoniŇčna tik ŇčgapaocniŇč w…®Ňčga titaca, maniŇča ootta taŇčga an meikramta…®rta tumbunna inikca mbukca, minmo kam aniac keca gaind mambopat,  
\v 15 \x - \xo 14:15 \xt NA 20.11, na 2 Sml 12.21, na Ňäap 33.6, na 146.6, na Up 10.26, na 1 Ko 8.4, na 1 Te 1.9, na Ie 5.17\x*‚ÄúMin ramta…®r, kaina moca ne aŇčmo ainda mona moek? AŇč toco ramootniŇč, aŇčga nena kirar. Na aŇčga nenmo gan kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo gainda wiwitinande, ne an m…®rpembraraiŇčta reikmo kai raŇčgai teac, ne iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgai, an RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma iarwarna eteacna watapna RaraŇč Aetaniac. Na an RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma ndo ma gan tiacarpaikapa riac tamuŇčapa macaitapa mina inik ndeacrena reac, reaca moatna RaraŇč Aetaniac.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 14:16 \xt Ňäap 81.12, na Up 17.30, na 1 Pi 4.3\x*Gidik, atuna nicar Ňčgamrirta m…®nna gan tiacarpaikna pitrik waŇčgorta meikramta…®ra, RaraŇč Aetaniaca minmo wattacarica, mina ndorita toŇčtoŇčgara taŇčgatna.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 14:17 \xt Ňäap 147.8, na Ier 5.24, na 14.22, na Up 17.27, na Ro 1.20\x*Ri, RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma minmo mba iŇčgorocatke. WanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Ma minmo ndo nagaracna moca, ma minmo memetmbaca ma minmo opotaca morina. Ri, ma nemo puk watcarica pukca riac tamuŇč ndiŇča rapaca irikri, nena war…®Ňčembta amta reikca moa gaca, nena amta reikca m…®n Ňčgoin ndeacrina, na ne an amba gautpemb putuca toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin maeacat.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Na maniŇča minmo an kam ndopacarica, maniŇča minmo Ňčarikca ndoniŇčmo g…®mbamba mo narica, minmo mak…®racri. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 14:19 \xt Up 13.45, na 17.13, na 2 Ko 11.25, na 2 Ti 3.11\x*Na iŇčmbaia Iudana meikramta…®r ndeida, auŇč aniacniŇčnan, Antiokapa Aikoniamna inik ndeacrina, mina k…®pca an meikramta…®rmo moa mina iroar Ňčgetrikica, mina Polmo ndorita puŇčndamoot mamoat. Ainda moca mina Ňčgepca Polmo watur puŇčga r…®Ňčga Ňčgocraica, anmo mamo memenac ndopca, mana wa…®rmo w…®Ňčga larua an auŇčna wuocna raekmbaia t…®kcamacariat.  
\v 20 Ri, Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra eacrenanna, taŇčga Polna wa…®rmo paria w…®t…®kca maica eacrinanna, Pola mac nda patr…®kiakeca Ňčgepca an auŇčna inik mac mambukat. Na iŇčmbaina ra, ma Banambasap aŇčg…®ca maniŇča Ňčgepca Derbe auŇč mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Polapa Banambasa Iesusna r…®pacrina meikramta…®rta r…®t…®paikmo moa paŇčpaiŇčiatna 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Mt 28.19\x*Karica maniŇča Derbe auŇčna meikramta…®rmo kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo minmo wiwitia taŇčga, maniŇča anna meikramta…®r w…®t aniacna iroara moa Ňčgepca, mina iroar Ňčgetrikica mina Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r malaruat. Ri, maniŇča Listaraapa Aikoniammapa Antiok mac nda mataŇčgat.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 14:22 \xt Mt 7.14, na Up 11.23, na 15.32, na 18.23, na 1 Te 3.3\x*Na maniŇča an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta iroara moi paŇčpaiŇčina moca, maniŇča minmo kam gargara aindopatna, ‚ÄúAia Iesusa r…®pacrena meikramta…®r, aia matau w…®t…®k paŇčpaiŇči, aia RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuoca mbuknande. Anna outmbaica aia makukar anikta inikca mbuknande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 \x - \xo 14:23 \xt Up 13.1-3, na 15.40\x*Karica maniŇča Ňčgepca mina Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumnambta ramta…®r paŇčaind ndeid larapacna moca, maniŇča amna reac wariraca maniŇča mambendeiat, maniŇča ainda moatnanna, maniŇča an Kacootta r…®pacatna ramta…®rmo aŇčg…®ra Kacootna par mat…®kat. 
\s1 Karica Polapa Banambasa nda taŇčga Siriana pitrikna inikna auŇč aniac Antiok mac nda mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 24 Na Polapa Banambas, maniŇča taŇčga Pisidiana pitrikna r…®kndiŇča taŇčga Pampiliana pitrik malaruat.  
\v 25 Karica maniŇča Ňčgepca Kacootna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo, Perga auŇča t…®kca wiwitia mbopacarica, iŇčmbaia maniŇča mac nda irikca Atalia auŇč malarucat.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 14:26 \xt Up 13.1-3, na 15.40\x*Karica maniŇča anna t…®kca laŇčgum naŇčgabukca Antiok auŇč aniac mac nda mataŇčgat. Na Ňčgaua an auŇčnanna Iesusa r…®pacatna meikramta…®r, mina maniŇčmo an aiŇča mo ndopca aŇčg…®ra RaraŇč Aetaniacna para t…®kca, mbag…®rica maniŇča an aiŇča moa taŇčri, na RaraŇč Aetaniaca maniŇčmo wawara taŇč, taŇčga maniŇč an aiŇčmo korwiatna mbatca, maniŇča Antiok mac nda mak…®pat.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 14:27 \xt Up 11.18, na 15.4, na 15.12\x*Ainda moca maniŇča Antiok auŇč ndaruca eacatke, maniŇča anna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbun aŇčg…®ra punica, minmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca maniŇčap morina reikta nininimo maniŇča minmo aind maniniat, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniac, ma taupca moca an kam wembaŇč laŇča Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta tambuŇča mbukca, mina mar…®pacat.‚ÄĚ  
\v 28 Ri, maniŇča an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rapmo, k…®dr…®k rocot Ňčgoinna maniŇča minapmo an Antiok auŇč aniac maeacat. 
\c 15  
\s1 Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarta tumbun aniac ianna Ierusalem mapuniat 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 15:1 \xt TN 12.3, na In 7.22, na Gal 2.12, na 5.2, na Kol 2.11, na 2.16\x*Ainda moatke, Iudiana ramta…®r ndeida Antiok auŇč Ňčgirikca, Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo ainda riptiatna, ‚ÄúNe Mosesna T…®p Wand…®kca raŇčgaica mina nena tikemb iŇčir katac Ňčgocor te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca nenmo mba mac nda aŇčg…®ritndai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 \x - \xo 15:2 \xt Up 11.30, na Gal 2.1\x*Ri, Polapa Banambasa an kamma waracatke, maniŇča Ňčgepca minap kam mbuŇča kaeg bagaraniaca moca, minap ipuŇčga mbopri, na Iesusa r…®pacatna meikramta…®ra Ňčgepca an reacna kekelamun irikatke, an Iesusa r…®pacatna meikramta…®r, mina Ňčgepca Polapa Banambas mbaniŇčmo minap Ierusalemma taŇčca an kammo up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rap, mina mimitpac aŇčg…®rena ramta…®r paŇčaind tambuŇč ndaruca, an kam wandoŇčaina moca, minmo mambag…®riat. 
\p  
\v 3 Ri, an Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna, mina ainda moca mbag…®rica mina taŇč, taŇčga, taŇčga Ponisiaapa Samaria ndaruca, an pitrik waŇčna r…®kndiŇča taŇčgatke, an Iesusa raŇčgairina meikramta…®rmo gan kam mambopat, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniaca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta tumbunna iroara r…®Ňčga, mina iroar maŇčgetrikiat.‚ÄĚ Ri, an auŇčna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara an kam mbaracatke, mina toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 15:4 \xt Up 14.27\x*Karica mina taŇčga Ierusalem auŇč ndaruatke, an ndeacrina Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunapa mina ramta…®r paŇčaindapa, up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rap. Mina Polapa Banambas mbaniŇča watca maniŇčmo ra laŇč neaŇčg…®rina. Ri, maniŇča minmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca maniŇčap morina reikta kambca, maniŇč minmo an mambopat.  
\v 5 Ri, Parisina tumbunna ndeida an inikca Iesusa r…®pacrenan, an ndeacrinan Ňčgepca aindopatna, ‚ÄúAn Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda, mina ndorimo aina tumbun nak…®pi mbuk ndop te, ne mina tikemb iŇčir katac, te, minmo mbopca mina Mosesna T…®p Wand…®kca raŇčgai.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 Ri, an up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rapa ramta…®r paŇčainda, ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica an kam wandoŇčaina moca.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 15:7 \xt Up 10.1-43\x*Karica mina ndorimo an kam wandoŇčai ndopca mamoatnanna, Ňčgepca ndorimo iptipuŇč aniaca moa taŇč, taŇčga maiatna mbatca, Pita Ňčgepca minmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNe Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar, ne malamŇčireke, Ňčgaua RaraŇč Aetaniaca aimo an aiŇča mona moca nduca maica, ma aukmo an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo waraca ndona kam wembaŇč laŇčna kammo, aukmo an ndop te, mina ndori waraca ndorita r…®t…®paikca ndori puŇčga mo ndopca aukmo larapacatna.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 15:8 \xt 1 Nin 28.9, na Up 1.24, na 2.4, na 10.44, na 11.15\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma ndo ma meikramta…®rta iroar inkara ma lamŇčirena, aintik ma minmo ŇäeroŇč Rat neaŇčgatna. Na anna ma aia neaŇčgatna kirar. Na an iroa ma ainda moatnanna, ma aimo gaind ndamŇčina moca, ma an meikramta…®r aŇčtaŇčg…®na toŇčtoŇčap.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 15:9 \xt Up 10.15, na 10.28, na 10.34-35, na Ro 10.11, na 1 Ko 1.2, na 1 Pi 1.22\x*Na ma gainda mba morenanna, ma aimo kirar damma mo te, min motocmo ma kirar damma monande, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Mina RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®pacre tik, mina an r…®t…®pacna taup mbuŇča RaraŇč Aetaniaca mina makukara moa kecarica, mina mana lamn…®aca meacramoot wandoŇč laŇč ndarurina.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 15:10 \xt Mt 11.30, na 23.4, na Lk 11.46, na Gal 3.10, na 5.1\x*Aintik kaina moca ne RaraŇč Aetaniacmo ainta totowaia mona moek? An Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r tambatmo ainta makukara kai leac teac, atua aina nicarapa, gan aina m…®n toco, aia ainta makukara mbukna m…®nna wanaiŇč.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Ro 3.24, na Gal 2.16, na Epe 2.5-8, na Ta 2.11\x*Na aia Kacoot Iesus Karaisa r…®pacrenan tik, mana kakadmaica ndo aina makukara mo kecari te, Kacootta aimo mac nda aŇčg…®nande, aintik RaraŇč Aetaniac ma an meikramta…®r motocmo ma aŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 15:12 \xt Up 14.27\x*Na Pita an kam mambopat, ri, an meikramta…®ra punica Polapa Banambas mbaniŇčmo, RaraŇč Aetaniaca maniŇč mbuŇča ainta Ňčgagatracara an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta k…®dr…®kca t…®kca moatna reikta nininia mori, na mina mbiraca maica kour ikca mawaracri. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 15:13 \xt Up 12.17, na Gal 2.9\x*Karica maniŇča mbopca maiatna mbatca, Iemis tuk Ňčgepca aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar, ne gan auk mbopekna kam mbarac!  
\v 14 \x - \xo 15:14 \xt Up 15.7-9\x*Saimon Pita ma nemo outta mboprinan, ‚ÄėRaraŇč Aetaniac ma mina an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta k…®dr…®k Ňčgirikatna, mina ndeidmo moi iroar inkar uriraca ma minmo aŇčg…®nande. Te, mina iroar Ňčgetrikica mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna meacramoot Ňčgoin ndarunande.‚Äô  
\v 15 Na an RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morina ramta…®r toco, mina an RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kap mboprina, an kam iro kabe ndopatna.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 15:16 \xt Emo 9.11-12\x*‚ÄėAinda moca Kacootta aindopatna, ‚ÄúDewitna barna meikramta…®ra anna ma kac bagar witkia irikca eacrena kirar maeacreke. Na iŇčmbaia, aku mac nda k…®p te, aku an kacmo mana Ňčgocrairina reik mac nda rutica moi laŇča moca, manmo mac nda aŇčg…®ri Ňčgepi w…®t…®knande.  
\v 17-18 Ainda mo te, gan tiacarpaikna meikramta…®ra Kacootna moca ndada Ňčgorenande, aintik an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda aku baburinan, mina aukna meikramta…®r koind.‚ÄĚ An kamma anna parua wanaiŇč, anna gidik, an kamma Kacootta atu Ňčgoinna ndopatna kamma mba Ňčgetrikitndai, an reikca gidik Ňčgoin ndarunande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 19 Karica Iemisa gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúAukna iroa gaind ndamŇčirina, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda RaraŇč Aetaniac ndambuŇča uriraca taŇčrenanmo, aia minmo iro Ňčgoreaca kai aŇčg…®ca, na minmo makukara kai neaŇč teac.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 15:20 \xt RL 9.4, na NA 34.15-17, na TN 17.10-16, na 18.6-23, na 1 Ko 6.9, na 6.18, na 8.1, na Gal 5.19, na Epe 5.3, na Kol 3.5, na 1 Pi 4.3\x*Aia minmo gainda mo te, anna laŇč, minmo timbiŇč rapar ianna tirca gaindopna, ne m…®rpembraraiŇčta dawarta outta t…®krena g…®mbamba morena amta reikca kai aŇčg…® teac, na meacramootna kaŇčtertaapna t…®p kirara morena meikramta…®rta t…®pemb kirarira kai mo teac, na orapa…®r paurna Ňčgoaemma mina mana logotmo kaorikca ma menaceknanna, ainta Ňčgoaemma ma racaindap maeacreke, ne ainta racaindta Ňčgoaemma kai am teac.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 15:21 \xt Up 13.15\x*Anna aia lamŇčirena, atu Ňčgoinna t…®kca k…®pca mandeacna m…®n, an auŇčemb anik ndeida mina ramta…®ra, mina memetmbaca Mosesna T…®p Wand…®kna kamma, mina memetmbaca W…®kt…®t…®kna Raia, mina Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaikca mbukca mina memetmbaca mina an kam ndoprena.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Mina Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda r…®pacrinanmo timbiŇč rapar ianna tirca neaŇčga mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 22 Karica up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rapa, mina outmbaica taŇčrena ramta…®r paŇčaindapa, na an Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunap, mina ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica, mina kam leaca Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo outmbaica taŇčrena ramootniŇčmo larapacatna. ManiŇčna iniŇča iannanna Iudas, na mana i ian toco Barsabas, na ianna ia Sailas. Mina maniŇčmo Antiok auŇča mandaca Polapa Banambasap mbag…®rica mina mataŇčgat.  
\v 23 Ri, an timbiŇč rapara mina maniŇčna para t…®katna timbiŇč raparna kamma mina gaindopatna, 
\b  
\mi ‚ÄúAia up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rapa ramta…®r paŇčaind, aia nena Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar, aia nenmo gan timbiŇč rapara tirca neaŇčga k…®prinanna, aia nenmo Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda Iesusa r…®pacrenan, ne Antiok auŇč ndeacrenanapa, mon pitrik aniacniŇč Siriapa Silisia, maniŇčna inik ndeacrena Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar, nenmo muruŇčcamiŇča ra laŇč Ňčgoin neaŇčrina.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 15:24 \xt Up 15.1\x*Na aia gaind mbaracrina, aina ramta…®r ndeida nen ndambuŇč nak…®pca, mina mbopatna kambca ne anna waraca, ne anna moca makukuatnanna, aia minmo ainda mo nake mba mbopatke.  
\v 25 Mina nenmo ainda moatna kamma aia aind mbaraca, ainda moca aia ndorimo aŇčg…®ra punica anna kam ndopca taŇčga, aina toŇčgoca matŇčirena ramootniŇč Banambasapa Polap mbag…®rica k…®prinanna, aia larapacrina ramootniŇčmo maniŇčap mbag…®rica k…®prina.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 15:26 \xt Up 13.50, na 14.19, na 1 Ko 15.30, na 2 Ko 11.23, na 11.26\x*Na an ramootniŇč Polapa Banambas, maniŇča ndoniŇčna tikniŇčmo Ňčgoreac aŇčtaŇčg…®nake rugutta mba mori, na maniŇča aina Kacoot Iesus Karaisna ina reikta nininia momoa, maniŇča reac ian nake, mba nanambirenan.  
\v 27 Ainda moca aia Iudasapa Sailasmo mbag…®rica k…®prina, maniŇča nenmo an timbiŇč raparna kamna kirara, maniŇča nenmo up mbuŇča mbopnande.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 15:28 \xt Mt 23.4\x*ŇäeroŇč Ratta aiap eacreke, ainda moca aia kam leaca gaindopatna, aia nenmo kabena makukar ndeida mba mac moitndai. Aintik ne an ndorita eacrena kirara aind niŇčgik ndeacraŇč.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 15:29 \xt TN 17.14, na Up 15.20, na 21.25, na KIEK 2.14, na 2.20\x*Te, ne mina r…®Ňčga menaca ndorita m…®rpembraraiŇčta dawarta outta t…®krena g…®mbamba morena Ňčgoaebca ne kai am teac, na orapa…®r paurna Ňčgoaemma mina mana logotmo kaorikca ma menaceknanna, ainta Ňčgoaemma ma racaindap maeacreke, ne ainta racaindta Ňčgoaemma kai am teac, na ne meacramootna kaŇčtertaapna t…®p kirara morena meikramta…®rta t…®pemb kirarira kai mo teac. Na ne an t…®pemb tarica iukairaŇč te, anna laŇč. Na aina kamma an niŇčgik, na ne ndorimo mataui raupŇči eac. An niŇčgik. Ra laŇč.‚ÄĚ 
\b  
\p  
\v 30 Karica an Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbuna an ramta…®r paurmo mbag…®rica mina irikca Antiok auŇč ndaruca. An Antiok auŇčna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunmo aŇčg…®ra punica, mina minmo an timbiŇč rapar aŇčg…®ra maneaŇčgat.  
\v 31 Ri, mina an timbiŇč raparmo gootca watatna kamma, anna mina moi gagrana kam, mina anna watca toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 15:32 \xt Up 11.27, na 13.1, na 14.22\x*Na Iudasapa Sailasa RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morena ramootniŇč, aintik maniŇča an Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo, mina r…®t…®paikca moi gagarana kamb w…®t aniac mambopat, na maniŇč ainda mo te, mina r…®t…®paikca moi gagarana moatna.  
\v 33-34 Karica maniŇča minapmo k…®dr…®k rocot motemma minap eaca maica, iŇčmbaia mina maniŇčap t…®kca mbiraca, maniŇčmo mbag…®rica maniŇča k…®patna meikramta…®r tambuŇča nda mbag…®rica maniŇča mataŇčgat. Ri, mina maniŇčmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOŇčgo RaraŇč Aetaniacna opotaca laŇčap taŇč.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 15:33-34 \ft LandamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida gaind ndamŇčirena, kabena kam t…®p ian toco maeacreke. Na an kamma gaindoprena, \fq ‚ÄúNa Sailasa ndona iro Ňčgetrikica ma Antiok auŇč aniac maeacri.‚ÄĚ\f* 
\v 35 Ri, Polapa Banambas mbaniŇča Antiok auŇč ndeacri, maniŇča ramta…®r ndeidap t…®kca, mina meikramta…®rmo Kacootna kamna mimitpac neaŇčgatke, minmo Kacootna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma an wiwitia mambopat. 
\s1 Polapa Banambas maniŇča iro kabea mba eacri 
\p  
\v 36 Karica raeniŇč taŇčga maiatke, anna iŇčmbai mbuŇča, Pola Banambasmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAŇčga mac nda taŇčca ndoniŇčna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara, mon auŇčemb anik ndeacrenanmo oke watna, Ňčgaua aŇčga taŇčga minmo Kacootna kam ndopatna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo watna, mina laŇč ndeacre, co, wanaiŇč, anna garacna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 \x - \xo 15:37 \xt Up 12.12, na 12.25, na Kol 4.10, na 2 Ti 4.11\x*Ri, Banambasa ndomo Ion Makap aŇčg…®ca ndoniŇčap taŇčna ndopri.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 15:38 \xt Up 13.13, na Kol 4.10\x*Ri, Pola gaindopca, ‚ÄúAn ramoot, ma Ňčgaua Pampilia pitrikca t…®kca, ma an aiŇča mo narica kariatna ramoot, aintik ma aŇčgap mba taŇčitndai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Aindopca maniŇča ndoniŇčmo Ion Makna moca iptipuŇč aniaca moca ndoniŇčmo titaca, ndamniŇč mataŇčgat, Banambasa Ňčgepca Ion Mak aŇčg…®ca maniŇča taŇčga laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Saiprus mut mairikat.  
\v 40 Ri, Pola Sailas aŇčg…®ca, maniŇča taŇčna mori, Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara maniŇčmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúKacootna kakadmaica oŇčgap eacnandet.‚ÄĚ Ri, maniŇč toco mataŇčgat.  
\v 41 Ri, maniŇča Ňčgepca taŇčga Silisiaapa Siriana r…®kniŇčna pitrikca mbukca, anna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumnambmo, Pola mina r…®t…®paikca moa gagrari, paŇčpaiŇčica mataŇčri. 
\c 16  
\s1 Timotia Polap mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 16:1 \xt Up 14.6, na 2 Ti 1.5\x*Karica Pola taŇčga auŇč aniacniŇč Derbeapa Listara ndaruca, na Listara auŇč aniac inik ndeacrina ramoot ianna, ma Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena ramoot, na mana ia Timoti. Na mana m…®ratna meaca, anna Iudananta meac, ma Iesusa r…®pacrena, na mana aetta anna Giriknanta ramoot.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 16:2 \xt Pil 2.19-22\x*Ri, an Listarananapa Aikoniam auŇčniŇčna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara, Timotina morina t…®pemb kirarir mananna watca, mina gaindoprena, ‚ÄúMa ramoot laŇč Ňčgoin.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 \x - \xo 16:3 \xt 1 Ko 9.20, na Gal 2.3-5\x*Ri, Pola ma Iudananda an auŇčemb teacrenanna ndamŇčica, ma ndomo Timotiap aŇčg…®ca taŇčna ndamŇčiri, ainda moca ma mana tikiŇčit makatacat. Na Pola manmo ainda moatnanna, Iudananda mina aind ndamŇčirenan, Timotina aetta ma Giriknanta ramoot.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 16:4 \xt Up 15.23-29\x*Karica up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rapa mina ramta…®r paŇčainda Ierusalemma t…®kca mbopca gagara moatna kamb anmo, Polapa an ramootniŇč, mina an auŇčembca mbukca taŇčri, an auŇčembta r…®pacrena meikramta…®rmo, an kam wiwitia mbopca taŇčri. Na minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe tamtamma kai mo teac, ne an tiŇčgikca raŇčgai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 \x - \xo 16:5 \xt Up 2.47\x*Ainda moatke, an Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumnambca, mina r…®t…®paikca kocnaia gagramacariat. Na mina ndundu toco kocnaia ra kabe, kabea katuca aind nagacri, mina taŇčga w…®t aniaca moa macariat. 
\s1 Pola Masedoniana ramoot ianmo manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇča watatna 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 16:6 \xt Up 18.23\x*Ri, an m…®nna Polapa, Sailasapa, Timoti, minmo ŇäeroŇč Ratta Esiana pitrik waŇčmbaia taŇč narica, wattacarica mina an kam wembaŇč laŇča an pitrik waŇčembaia, mina mba taŇčga wiwitiatke, ainda moca mina Pirigiapa Galesiana pitrik r…®kndiŇča taŇčrina.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 16:7 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Ainda moca mina taŇčga Misia pitrik aniacna m…®nna t…®kca, ndorimo Bitinia pitrik aniac mbuk ndopca mori, Iesusna ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo k…®raca mina mba taŇčgatke.  
\v 8 Ainda moca mina an Misia pitrik t…®kcarica Ňčgepca Toroas auŇč aniac Ňčgirikca.  
\v 9 Karica mina Ňčgoca an mouŇča, Pola manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram ianna wattatnanna, Masedoniana ramoot ianna w…®t…®kca manmo aca aindopatna, ‚ÄúU macait aniac an kataca ganmbai nagaca aimo Masedoniana meikramta…®r kotacna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 \x - \xo 16:10 \xt 2 Ko 2.13\x*Ri, Pola an manmb…®anmemraŇč tocna tamram ianna aind mbatatke, aia Ňčgepca malamŇčiat, an tamramma anna RaraŇč Aetaniaca aimo Masedonia taŇčca anna meikramta…®rmo ndona kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwiti te, anna meikramta…®rmo anna waracna moca, wandacapekna tamram, ainda moca aia anduna Ňčgepca anna taŇčna moca taupembta maoreat. 
\s1 Lidia ndona iro Ňčgetrikica kam wembaŇč laŇč mar…®pacat 
\p  
\v 11 Ainda moca aia Toroas auŇč aniac t…®kca laŇčgum naŇčgabukca, laŇčgumma aimo wandoŇč Ňčgoin naaŇčg…®ra taŇčga Samoteres mutmo kunda kabena ra, aia mac taŇčga Neapolis auŇč magacat.  
\v 12 Na an ŇčgetacndiŇč naŇčgepatnanna, aia mbatŇčdiŇča taŇčga Pilipai auŇč aniac malaruat. Na an auŇč aniaca anna RomnaŇčgepca out Ňčgoinna, mina an mambiracat, na an auŇč Masedoniana pitrik waŇčna inik ndeacrena auŇč aniac ma irembta auŇč. Na aia an auŇčmo, rai ndepikca aia an maeacat.  
\v 13 Karica RaraŇč Aetaniacna W…®kt…®t…®kna Ra laruatke, aia laruca an auŇč aniacna wuoc t…®Ňč ndaruca, aia oc ian mataŇčgat. Na aia an ocmo roumbmbaica mbiraca mbendeirena taup ndopca taŇčgatnanna, meikpitikca ndori punica eacri, aintik aia taŇčca minap mbiraca minap mambopri.  
\v 14 Ri, raraŇčgir laupemb puŇčga mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca t…®kca kituknduk aŇčtaŇčg…®na aiŇča morina meac ianna, mana ia Lidia, ma Taiataira auŇč aniacnan, ma RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgairina meac. Na ma Pol mboprina kam wembaŇč laŇčna moca koar nan ikca mataua waraca maica, manmo Kacootta mana iroa moa Ňčgetrikica.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 16:15 \xt Up 16.33, na 18.8\x*Karica ma k…®tac puk aŇčg…®ri, na manap an kac kabe ndeacrinan toco, k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®rat. Ma ainda mocarica, iŇčmbaia ma Ňčgepca aimo ndona kaca taŇčna toŇčgoca ma aimo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNena wapatta aku gidikca Kacootmo r…®pacrena meac ecte, ne k…®pca aukna kac ndeac.‚ÄĚ Ma aimo ndo ndambuŇča taŇčna moca aimo ainda gagra mbopatna mbatca, aia Ňčgepca mana toŇčtoŇč maraŇčgaiat. 
\s1 Polapa Sailasa mon Pilipaina kac Ňčgoreacmo mina maniŇčmo anna t…®katna 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 16:16 \xt Up 19.24\x*Karica oit ianna aia mbendeirena taupca taŇčna taŇč, taŇčga, tuomna aiŇč kamainda morena mooŇč Ňčgam ianna aimo taupca t…®kca mandauprikiat. Na an mooŇč Ňčgam tikca, ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreaca man Ňčgaoca, ma iŇčmbai ndataruna reikta kamb topreke, mina manmo kitukndukar anik puŇč koikreke, mana ŇčginaŇča morena ramta…®r paŇčainda, mana ainda moa aŇčg…®rena kitukndukar anik aŇčg…®rena.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 16:17 \xt Mk 1.24, na 1.34\x*Ri, an meaca Polapa aina iŇčmbaia taŇčri, na ma kam aniac keca gaind mambopri, ‚ÄúGan ramta…®r, mina tamuŇč ndeacrena RaraŇč Aetaniacna aiŇča morena ramta…®r. Mina nenmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca nen mac nda aŇčtaŇčg…®na kamma mina an ndoprena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 \x - \xo 16:18 \xt Mk 16.17\x*Memetmbaca ma ra, ra katuca an meaca kamb anikca ainda momoa, Pola mana aindoprena kam garara warac, waraca Ňčateca, ma nda repakeca an ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreacmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúMandeaca aku Iesus Karaisna i mbuŇča unmo aindopnande, ‚ÄėMandebanna u an meacmo t…®kcarica u taŇč!‚Äô‚ÄĚ Ri, an ŇčeroŇča manmo anduna t…®kcamacariat. 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 16:19 \xt Up 19.25-26, na 2 Ko 6.5\x*Ri, an meacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramta…®r paŇčainda, an meacna ainda moreke, mina anna kitukndukar anik aŇčg…®rena taupca Pola anna moa kecariapeke, an ramta…®r paŇčainda ainda watca, ainda moca mina Ňčgepca Polapa Sailasmo muoca utiŇčga w…®Ňčgatataca aŇčg…®ra taŇčga an w…®t aniac punica eacrina auŇč r…®k naaŇčg…®ra taŇčga anna ramta…®r paŇčaind tambuŇč naaŇčg…®ra mataŇčgat.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 16:20 \xt 1 GRP 18.17, na Mt 5.11, na Mk 13.9, na Up 17.6\x*Na mina ramootniŇčmo aŇčg…®ra taŇčga an Romna ritri waparaca morena ramta…®r tambuŇč ndaruca, mina an ritri waparaca morena ramta…®rmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúGan Iudana ramootniŇča, k…®pca aina auŇč aniacmo t…®pemb kirarir Ňčgorik aŇčg…®ra mbukapekna.  
\v 21 Na maniŇča meikramta…®rmo riptirena t…®pemb kirarir damara, anna aina Romnanta wand…®k t…®krena t…®pemb kirarirmo riptirena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 \x - \xo 16:22 \xt 2 Ko 6.5, na 11.23-25, na Pil 1.30, na 1 Te 2.2\x*Karica an k…®pca punica eacrina meikramta…®ra, muruŇč naŇčgepca maniŇčmo mapiat. Ri, ritri waparaca morena ramta…®ra, Ňčgepca maniŇčna tik ŇčgapaocniŇč pitukca aŇčg…®atke, maniŇča pina ramta…®r ndeid mbag…®rica maniŇčmo monac mbuŇča pirina.  
\v 23 Ri, an ramta…®ra maniŇčmo monac t…®p mbuŇča mba gegereatke, pi Ňčgoreac Ňčgoinna pia maiatna mbatca, ritri waparaca morena ramta…®ra Ňčgepca maniŇčmo aŇčg…®ra taŇčga kac Ňčgoreacna inik mat…®kat. Karica an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootmo, maniŇčna ŇčginaŇča matau momona kam mambopat.  
\v 24 Ri, an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootta, an ritri waparaca morena ramootna mbopatna kam mbaraca maiatna mbatca, ma Ňčgepca Polapa Sailas aŇčg…®ra taŇčga an kac Ňčgoreacna r…®kna diabna inikca t…®kca, maniŇčna or kumbutniŇčmo ik waŇčniŇčna waea t…®kca lawirta Ňčga…®r puŇčga mataua leaca maica maniŇča an maeacat.\fig Polapa Sailasa kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrina|src="Gw176.tif" size="span" copy="Wade" ref="16.24" \fig* 
\p  
\v 25 Ri, maniŇča an mouŇč r…®kniŇča, maniŇča RaraŇč Aetaniaca mbendeiri, Ňčapar kumbri, na an maniŇčap an kac Ňčgoreacna inik ndeacrina ramta…®ra, maniŇčna ainda morina reik mawaracri.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 16:26 \xt Up 4.31, na 5.19, na 12.7, na 12.10\x*Ri, an motemma numnum bagaraniac ianna laruatnanna, an kacmo aŇčg…®ra numaiatke, an kacna witira taŇčga m…®Ňčgracri, na t…®Ňčgi gootta mamaiat. Ri, an kacna inik ndeacrina meikramta…®rta our kumbutarmo leaca maica eacrina paraiŇč t…®pembta waremba t…®kca leac eacrina lawirta Ňčga…®ra, kocnaia kataca mamaiat.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 16:27 \xt Up 12.18-19\x*Ri, an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootta Ňčgepca wattatnanna, t…®Ňčembca muruŇčcamiŇča gootta maica eacri, na ma aind mbatca anmo an kacna inik ndeacrina meikramta…®rmo k…®pcarica taŇčga mairi ndopca, ma Ňčgepca ndona bugrim aŇčg…®ca ndomo r…®Ňč menacna moatna.  
\v 28 Ri, Pola lar…®kca aind mambopat, ‚ÄúAe, u ndomo kai mo menac teac, aia mba k…®pcariri, aia muruŇčcamiŇča maeacreke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 Karica an ŇčginaŇča morina ramootta ramta…®rmo ndomo tac aŇčg…®r k…®pna Ňčgacri, mina tac aŇčg…®ra k…®patke, ma Polapa Sailasna eacrina diab inikca taŇčga mbukca, ma rugut moa Ňčgocraica reik nekcarica, ma maniŇčna or k…®t…®m Ňčgirikca mameracat.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 16:30 \xt Lk 3.10, na Up 2.37, na 9.6\x*Karica ma Ňčgepca maniŇčmo aŇčg…®ca mina larua raekca t…®katke, ma maniŇčmo gaind madigiat, ‚ÄúRamoot aniacniŇč aku tida mo te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca aukmo mac nda aŇčg…®rit?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 16:31 \xt In 3.16, na 3.36, na 6.47, na 1 Io 5.10\x*Ri, maniŇča manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU Kacoot Iesusmo r…®pac te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca unapa una racaindpaiknandap, ma nenmo muruŇč Ňčgotaca nemo mac nda aŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 Karica Polapa Sailasa an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootapa mana racaindpaiknandmo, Kacoot Iesusna kam wembaŇč laŇčna kamma, minmo an mawiwitiat.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 16:33 \xt Up 16.15\x*Karica an mouŇč r…®kniŇča, an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootta maniŇčmo aŇčg…®ra laruca, maniŇčna pitir tukia maiatna mbatca, maniŇča manapa mana racaindpaikna meikramta…®rap, minmo puk mbuŇča k…®tac puk maneaŇčgat.  
\v 34 Ri, ma maniŇčmo aca aŇčg…®ca maniŇča manap, mina mana kaca taŇčga, ma maniŇčmo amna reac neaŇčga maniŇča ambri, manapa mana kac ndeacrinan, mana racaindpaikna meikramta…®rap, mina mandeaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®paca, an r…®t…®pacna toŇčtoŇč bagaraniac Ňčgoin. 
\p  
\v 35 Karica eaca auŇč raruatke ŇčaŇčarmuŇč motemma, ritri waparaca morena ramta…®r paŇčainda Polapa Sailasmo aŇčg…®na moca, piriŇč mbag…®rica mina maniŇč aŇčg…®na k…®pca laruca an kac Ňčgoreacna ŇčginaŇča morina ramoot ndambuŇč ndaruca, manmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúRitri waparaca morena ramta…®ra gaindoprina, ‚ÄėU an ramootniŇčmo watcarica maniŇča taŇč.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 36 Ri, maniŇčna ŇčginaŇča morina ramootta, Ňčgepca taŇčga Polmo gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAn ritri waparaca morena ramta…®ra gaindoprina, ‚ÄėAia oŇčmo reac ianna mba moitndaiit, oŇčgo gan kac Ňčgoreac t…®kcarica laŇčan ndaruca taŇč.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 37 Ri, Pola an piriŇčmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAŇčga gan auŇč Romna ramootniŇč, na aŇčga kaia moa Ňčgocraica mina anna moca aŇčmo anna ŇčgutiŇčga meikramta…®rta lamnik Ňčgoutta t…®kca pica aŇčg…®ra kac Ňčgoreaca t…®krina, na an ritri waparaca morena ramta…®ra mina mba k…®pca aŇčna morina reaca aŇčgap mbop Ňčgocor, mina anna garacna aŇčga reac ianna moa Ňčgocrairi ki, co wanaiŇč. Mina an nagaracarica iŇčmbaia mina aŇčmo wanaiŇča watcarica aŇčga taŇčna, na ganna mina aŇčmo wanaiŇča watcarica taŇč ndopapeknanna, aŇčga mba taŇčitndai? Ne taŇčca minmo mbopca mina ndori k…®pca aŇčmo gan kac Ňčgoreaca t…®ki aŇčg…® laruca, aŇčmo mbag…®rica te, aŇčga taŇčnande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 38 Karica an piriŇčga Polna mbopatna kam mac nda aŇčg…®ra taŇčga ritri waparaca morena ramta…®rmo aind mambopat, Pola ma gaindoprina, ‚ÄúSailas aŇčga Romna ramootniŇč.‚ÄĚ Ri, mina aind mbaracatke, mina rugdar mamoat.  
\v 39 \x - \xo 16:39 \xt Mt 8.34\x*Ainda moca ritri waparaca morena ramta…®ra taŇčga Polapa Sailasmo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca watca, maniŇčmo ndori moatna t…®pemb kirarirta kambta kam kakadmai ndopacarica, mina maniŇčmo an kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca aŇčg…®ra laruca mambopat, ‚ÄúLaŇč oŇčgo mandeaca gan auŇč t…®kcarica oŇčgo taŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 40 Karica maniŇča an kac Ňčgoreac t…®kcarica maniŇča Ňčgepca taŇčga Lidiana kac ndeacrina Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo okeca watca minmo mina iroara moi gagrana moca minmo kamb ndeid ndopca maica. Karica maniŇča an auŇč aniac t…®kcarica maniŇča mataŇčgat. 
\c 17  
\s1 Polapa Sailasa Tesalonika auŇč aniaca taŇčgatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt 1 Te 1.1-2, na 2.1-2\x*Karica Polapa Sailasa Ampipolis auŇč mataŇčgat, an ŇčgedacndiŇča Apolonia auŇč mac mataŇčgat, na an ŇčgedacndiŇča mina k…®pca Tesalonika auŇč aniac malaruat. Na an auŇča ma Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacap.  
\v 2 Ri, Pola ndona morina kirara moca ma Ňčgepca Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kac mataŇčgat. Na an W…®kt…®t…®kna Rai mbonkaca ma an mina Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca t…®kca, RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapna kambmo meikramta…®rap gagra mboprina.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 17:3 \xt Lk 24.26, na Up 3.18, na 9.22, na 18.28, na Gal 3.1\x*Ainda moca ma minmo an kamna m…®n…®Ňč ndopca waracri, mimo mana m…®n…®Ňča wandaca mina lamŇčina. Na ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAn ramoot RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot, ma g…®rg…®r aŇčg…®ca, ma menaca ma mac nda Ňčgepnande. Na aku nemo mboprena ramoot Iesus, an ramootta RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot.‚ÄĚ  
\v 4 \x - \xo 17:4 \xt Up 13.50, na 15.22, na 15.27, na 15.40, na 28.24\x*Ri, an ndeacrina Iudana meikramta…®r ndeida an kamb mbaraca, ndorita iroar Ňčgetrikica mina r…®paca, Polapa Sailas maraŇčgaiat. Na anna Girikna meikramta…®ra w…®t aniaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®pacrenanda, mitoco maniŇčap maraŇčgaiat, na meik paŇčaind ndeid toco minap maraŇčgaiat. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 17:5 \xt Ro 16.21\x*Ri, Iudananta ramta…®r ndeida minap titikca moca iroar Ňčgorik aŇčg…®ca mina an mbik t…®krena taupna ramta…®r ndeid aŇčg…®ca tumbunna t…®kca, mina Ňčgepca an auŇč aniacmo kam keca ipuŇčga mboprina. Ainda moca mina Iason Ňčgacrina ramootna kaca taŇčga, mina Polapa Sailas Ňčgore laru te, mina maniŇčmo an meikramta…®r tambuŇč naaŇčg…® taŇčnande.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt Up 16.20\x*Karica mina maniŇčmo orea wat Ňčgocor tik, mina Ňčgepca Iasonapa, Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar ndeidmo muoca utiŇčga w…®Ňčgatataca taŇčrina. Minmo aŇčg…®ca an auŇč aniacna ramta…®r paŇčaind tambuŇča taŇčga, aca, aindoprina, ‚ÄúGan ramta…®r, mina gan tiacarpaikmo makukar anikca moa larurenanna, mandeaca mina aina auŇč aniac mak…®pri.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 17:7 \xt Lk 23.2, na In 19.12, na 1 Pi 2.13\x*Na Iasona ma minmo ndona kac inik naaŇčg…®a taŇčca eacrina. Na mina gan Sisana t…®pembca moa maŇčgocraireke, ri, mina aind mambopat, kabena gagrirta ramoot paŇčan ianna maeacreke, mana ia Iesus.‚ÄĚ  
\v 8 Karica an tumbun Ňčgoreaca an kamb topatke, an auŇč aniacna ramta…®r paŇčaindapa meikramta…®ra an kambca waraca mina nikembkatca kamb anik makeat.  
\v 9 Ri, an ramta…®r paŇčainda Iasonapa manap taŇčgatna ramta…®rmo mbopca, mina minmo kituknduk mbuŇč Ňčgoikca mina minmo wattacarica mina mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Polapa Sailasa Beria auŇč aniaca aiŇča mona mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 10 Na maica nenepuatke, anna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara Polap Sailasmo mandaca maniŇča Beria auŇč aniac mataŇčgat. Ri, maniŇča taŇčga an ndaruatke, maniŇča Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kac mataŇčgat.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 17:11 \xt Ais 34.16, na Lk 16.29, na In 5.39\x*Ri, an Beria auŇč aniac ndeacrina meikramta…®ra, mina t…®pemb kirarira laiŇč koind, mina an Tesalonika auŇč aniac ndeacrina meikramta…®rmo kunda tamuŇč Ňčgoin. Ainda moca mina an kam laŇča, Pola mboprinanna waracri, mina toŇčtoŇč aniacap, ainda moca mina ra, ra katuca an RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapca tirca eacrina kam laŇča wiwitia waracri, watrina. Na mina anna wati garacna, mana mboprena kambca gidik ki, wanaiŇč?  
\v 12 Ainda moca an ndeacrina Iudana meikramta…®r w…®tta mar…®pacat, na anna Girikna irembta meik ndeid toco mar…®pacri, na ramta…®r toco mar…®pacat. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 17:13 \xt Up 13.50, na 14.19\x*Karica an Tesalonika auŇč aniac ndeacrina IudanaŇčgepca waracri, Pola Beria auŇč aniacna meikramta…®rmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwitirina. Ri, mina Beria auŇča taŇčga anna meikramta…®rmo moa iroar paurica, mina Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgeprina.  
\v 14 Karica mina ainda moatna mbatca, anna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara Polmo anduna mbag…®rica ma maŇčarmbai mataŇčgat, na Sailasapa Timoti mbaniŇčmo an Beria auŇča t…®kcamacariat.  
\v 15 Ri, an ramta…®ra Polmo aŇčg…®ca taŇčgatnanna, mina manmo warkica taŇčga Atens auŇč aniacna m…®n mbuŇč mat…®kat. Na mina nda taŇčna moatke, Pola minmo mbopa mawaracat, ‚ÄúNe taŇčca Sailasap Timotimo mbopca, maniŇča auk ndambuŇčmo tawi Ňčgoin nak…®p.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola Atens auŇč aniacmo kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwitia mbopatna 
\p  
\v 16 Karica Pola, ramootniŇčna moca, ma Atens auŇč aniaca ndabia eacri, na ma wattatnanna Atens auŇč inikca m…®rpembraraiŇčta dawara w…®t koind, aintik ma anna moca nikinik iro mananna laŇča mba t…®katke.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 17:17 \xt Up 18.19\x*Ainda moca ma Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca t…®kca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda RaraŇč Aetaniacmo torirenanapa, an Iudana meikramta…®rap kam gargar ndoprena, na ra, ra katuca ma an meikramta…®ra mandaia mbik t…®kca oikrena taupca punirinanmo, minapmo kam gargar ndoprena.  
\v 18 Karica Epikuriaapa Stoikna tumbunna landamŇčiapna ramta…®r ndeida manap kambmo upuria mambopri. Na ramta…®r ndeida aind mambopri, ‚ÄúAn ramoot, ma ndomo ndo ndoprina ramootta ma kaina kam ndopna moek?‚ÄĚ Aintik an kamna m…®n…®Ňčna digdigia gaind, Pola ma minmo Iesusna kammapa mana memenacapa nda ŇčgeŇčgepna kambmo minmo mawiwitiat. Ri, ndeida gaind mambopri, ‚ÄúMa tawanmbaina auŇčembta m…®rpembraraiŇč anikta kam ndopre ki?‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 17:18 \ft Na Girikna kamma mina gaindoprena, \ft \+it ‚ÄúAnastasis.‚ÄĚ\+it* Mana m…®n…®Ňč, ‚ÄúMuk ndiŇča mac nda Ňčgeprena.‚ÄĚ Na landamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida gainda ndamŇčirena, an Giriknanda mina waracrenanna, Pola Iesusna kam ndoprinanna, anna ma, ‚ÄúAnastasis‚ÄĚ na kam ndopri, mina mana mboprina kambta m…®niŇča mba garacri. Na an Giriknanda gaind ndamŇčirena, ma kabena auŇčna m…®r…®praraŇč meacapa ramootna i Ňčgacri. Na m…®r…®praraŇč ramootna ia, ‚ÄúIesus‚ÄĚ na m…®r…®praraŇč meacna ia, ‚ÄúAnastasis.‚ÄĚ\f* 
\v 19 Ainda moca mina mamo aŇčg…®ca taŇčga Areopagusna ninikar waŇčgorta punirena taupca t…®kca. Ri, mamo mina ninik waŇčgorta outta t…®kca, mina manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúAia an u mboprena kam Ňčgamma waracna moca, an kamma u meikramta…®rmo riptirenanna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Ri, mina mamo aindopatna, ‚ÄúUn mboprena kamb ndeida aina waparaca, anna aimo kabena auŇčna kam damna kirar. Ainda moca aia an kambta m…®n…®Ňč ndamŇčina toŇčgorena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 21 Ainda moca an Atens auŇčna meikramta…®rapa kabena auŇčna meikramta…®ra k…®pca an ndeacrenanna, mina ndorimo kabena reikca momoa karica. Mina toŇčgorinanna, mina an kam Ňčgam ndopraŇč te, mina waracraŇčna toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. 
\p  
\v 22 Ri, Pola mina tumbunna outta w…®t…®kca ma minmo aindoprina, ‚ÄúAtensna meikramta…®r ne warac, aku watreke, ne an m…®rpembraraiŇčta t…®pemb kirarira ne matau Ňčgoin matorireke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 Karica ma minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOutcait motemma, aku taŇčga wattatnanna, nena muruŇča mbendeireke g…®mbamba morena taupembca, mina ianna, mina gaindta kam t…®pca tirca eacrina, ‚Äė\sc Gan RaraŇčna Ia Aia LamŇči Ňägocor\sc*.‚Äô Na mandeac aku nemo an ne mbendeica raŇčgairena reaca, an reac ne lamŇči Ňčgocor, aku nenmo mana mimitpaca neaŇčnandet.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 17:24 \xt Mt 11.25, na Up 7.48, na 14.15\x*\x - \xo 17:24 \xt 1 GRP 8.27, na Ais 42.5\x*Ri, ma mimo gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniac, mandaia gan tiacarpaikapa mana inik ndeacrena reik muruŇča moatnanna, na an RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma tamuŇčna auŇčapa gan tiacarpaikna Kacoot, na ma mba ramoot par mbuŇča morena mbembendeina kaikca ma mba eacrenanna.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 17:25 \xt Iop 12.10, na Ňäap 50.12, na Sek 12.1, na Up 7.48\x*Na ma mba reac ianna mba matpirenanna, te, ramootta manmo an ma matpirena reik kotacna m…®nna wanaiŇč, na ma ndo eteacna watapa reik muruŇčmo meikramta…®ra neaŇčrena.  
\v 26 Na ma ramoot kabea moatke, an ramoot mbuŇča gan tiacarpaikna barerta meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca laruatna, ri, mina gan tiacarpaikmo muruŇč ndeacrina. Na ma minmo atu Ňčgoinna mina eteacna ra nagaganŇčg…®apa mina eteacna auŇčembca t…®krina.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 17:27 \xt TW 32.8, na Ňäap 145.18, na Ais 55.6, na Ier 23.23, na Up 14.17, na Ro 1.20\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniac ma toŇčgorinanna, meikramta…®ra man ndambuŇča taŇčca, manmo mataua lamŇčina, te, mina mana Ňčgore watna, na ma aimo kabe, kabemo tawanna wanaiŇč,  
\v 28 \x - \xo 17:28 \xt Kol 1.17, na Ta 1.12, na Ib 1.3\x*‚ÄėNa man mbuŇča aia memetmbac ndeacreke, taŇčrena, na ma ndo aimo gargar neaŇčrena.‚Äô Na nena landamŇčiapna ramta…®r ndeida mambopri, ‚ÄėAi toco mana mombonik.‚Äô  
\v 29 \x - \xo 17:29 \xt Ais 40.18-20, na 44.10-17, na Up 19.26\x*Aintik aia RaraŇč Aetaniacna mombonik eacrena, na aia ainda kai lamŇči teac, auŇč tamuŇčna RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma waut, co, gol, co, silwana kirar, co ramootna parapa iro mbuŇča moa larurina dana kirar toc. 
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 17:30 \xt Up 14.16, na Ro 3.25, na Ta 2.11-12, na 1 Pi 1.14\x*‚ÄúAinda moca Ňčgaua meikramta…®ra RaraŇč Aetaniacmo, lamŇči garac Ňčgocor tik, RaraŇč Aetaniaca mina morina reikta ke, mba tacroa mboprinanna. Na gan m…®n mbuŇča, ma minmo kam gargar neaŇčga aindoprina, meikramta…®r muruŇča auŇčembtanna iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica mana raŇčgai.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 17:31 \xt Ňäap 9.8, na 96.13, na Up 2.24, na 10.42, na Ro 2.16, na 14.10\x*Na RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma ra ianna larapaca maeacreke, na an ra laru te, ma meikramta…®rta t…®pemb kirarirmo ritrinande. Na mana t…®p kirar wandoŇč laŇčna moca, ma gan tiacarpaikna meikramta…®rmo ritri waparaca monande. Na ma an ritri waparacna moca ramoot ianna larapacrina, an ramootta ma menaca, RaraŇč Aetaniaca mamo muk ŇčgetacndiŇča mac nda aŇčg…®a Ňčgepatna. Te, aia r…®pacnande, RaraŇč Aetaniac ma ndo Ňčgoinna mamo an aiŇč neaŇčrina.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 32 Ri, mina an menaca mac nda Ňčgeprina kamma waraca, ndeida Polmo taŇčbugainna kam mambopri, na ndeida aindoprina, ‚ÄúAia toŇčgorinanna, u an kam mac mbopca, aia waracna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 33 Karica ma min t…®kcarica ma mataŇčgat.  
\v 34 Ainda moca ramta…®r ndeida mana raŇčgaica, mina mar…®pacat. Mina ianna Dionisius, ma an Areopagusna tumbunna ninik waŇčgapna ramoot ian, na Damaris Ňčgacrena meac toco mar…®pacat, na meikramta…®r ndeid toco mar…®pacat. 
\c 18  
\s1 Pola RaraŇč Aetaniacna kammo auŇč aniac Korinna t…®kca wiwitiatna 
\p  
\v 1 Karica iŇčmbai mbuŇča Pola Atens auŇč aniac t…®kcarica ma Korin auŇč aniac mataŇčgat.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Ro 16.3, na 1 Ko 16.19, na 2 Ti 4.19\x*Anna t…®kca ma Iudananta ramoot ian mandauprikiat, na an ramootna ia Akuwila, na mana pitrik waŇča Pontus, Ňčgaua manapa mana meac Pirisila maniŇča Itali pitrik waŇč t…®kcarica mon Korin mataŇčgat. Na maniŇča Korin auŇča taŇčgatna m…®n…®Ňča gaind, Romna gagrirta ramoot paŇčan aniaca, ma Iudana meikramta…®rmo Rom t…®kcarica taŇčna moca matimdacat. Aintik Pola an Akuwilaapa mana meac Pirisila oke watna taŇčgatna.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Up 20.34, na 1 Ko 4.12, na 1 Te 2.9, na 2 Te 3.8\x*Na an kamootniŇča, maniŇča Ňčgogona kaikca morenan, na Pol toca ma an aiŇč kirar kabea morena, aintik ma maniŇčap eacri, mina an aiŇča morena.  
\v 4 Ri, memetmbaca RaraŇč Aetaniacna W…®kt…®t…®kna Raia Pola Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mbukca Iudananapa, Girikna meikramta…®rta iroara moi Ňčgepca mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam aŇčg…®na ndoprina, te, mina iroar inkarca moi Ňčgepca minmo Iesusa r…®pacna moca. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 18:5 \xt Up 9.22, na 17.3, na 17.14-15, na 18.28\x*Karica an m…®nna Sailasapa Timoti mbaniŇča, Masedonia ndiŇč nak…®pca Pol ndambuŇča Korin ndaruca manap maeacri, na Pola ma memetmbaca ra, ra katuca ma an kam wembaŇč laŇč niŇčgikmo, Iudanandmo mimitpaca neaŇčga, mina garacna moca, ma aindopri, ‚ÄúIesus ma an ramoot RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot.‚ÄĚ  
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Esi 18.13, na Up 13.45-46, na 13.51, na 20.26, na 1 Pi 4.4\x*Ri, Iudananda mana kamma waracna kariri, mina mamo peperena kam Ňčgorik ndeidap mambopri. Ainda morina mbatca ma ndona or tukia minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgai Ňčgocor te, anna nena makuk, aku wanaiŇč. Aintik aku Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo wiwiti taŇčraŇčnandet, na IudanaŇčgepca wanaiŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 7 Karica Pola an kam ndopca maica, ma Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kac t…®kcarica ma taŇčga ramoot, ianna kac mataŇčgat, na an ramootta Titius Iastus. Na an ramoot ma RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mbendeirenan. Mana kaca ande Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacna roumbmbai maeacreke.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 18:8 \xt 1 Ko 1.14\x*Na an Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacna ramoot paŇčanna ia Kirispus, na manapa mana kac ndeacrina meikramta…®ra mina Kacoot Iesusmo r…®pacrena. Na meikramta…®r w…®t toco an Korin ndeacrinan, mina Pola wiwitirina kam wembaŇč laŇča waraca r…®paca k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®at. 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Up 23.11, na 1 Ko 2.3\x*Ri, mouŇč ian Kacootta manmo manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇč nak…®pca aindopatna, ‚ÄúU rugutta kai mo teac, u wiwitica mbopraŇč, u anna moca kai irik mbirac teac.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 \x - \xo 18:10 \xt Ios 1.9, na Ais 41.10, na Ier 1.8, na 1.18-19, na Mt 28.20, na In 10.16\x*Karica ma Polmo aind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúU rugutta kai mo teac, aku unap taŇčraŇčnande, na meac co ramoot ianna unmo reac Ňčgoreac ianna mba moitndai, aukna meikramta…®r w…®tta gan auŇč aniacna inik maeacreke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Ri, ma an ndeaca taŇčga gui kabeapa t…®pap t…®kca, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇčmo, meikramta…®rmo mariptiri. 
\p  
\v 12 Ainda moca Galio ma Akaiana pitrik waŇčna ramoot paŇčan ndeacrina k…®dr…®kca IudanaŇčgepca ndorimo aŇčg…®a tumbunna t…®kca Polmo ndorita puŇčndamoot mamoat. Na mina manmo utiŇčga ritri waparacna taup naaŇčg…®a mataŇčgat.  
\v 13 Ri, mina ramoot paŇčan Galiomo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúGan ramoot, ma meikramta…®rmo RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®t…®pacna riptimo moca kabena kirara moreke, na ma T…®p Wand…®k motocmo, ma nda mboprena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 \x - \xo 18:14 \xt Up 23.29, na 25.11, na 25.19\x*Ainda moca Pola mina kam ruti mbopna moatnanna, ramoot paŇčan Galio ma anduna Ňčgepca gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúNe Iudananda ne warac, aku gan ramootna kamma ritri waparaca mona toawanaiŇč, ma Romna t…®pna makuk ianna moco, ma reac Ňčgoreac ianna mo te, aku mamo ritri waparaca mo mbe.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt In 18.31, na Up 23.29, na 25.18-19\x*Na an makukca ma nena kambapa irembapa nena t…®pemb wandikap, aintik ne ndori puŇčga ritri waparaca mo. Anna nena Iudananta t…®pemb wandik, aku mba waracitndai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Ri, ma minmo latikca mbopca mandaca mina an ritri waparacna taup t…®kcarica malaruat.  
\v 17 Ainda moca mina nikembkatca, an Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacna ramoot paŇčanna, mana ia Sostenis. Na mina mamo muoca utiŇčga mamo an ritri waparacna taupca t…®kca manmo pi Ňčgoreac Ňčgoin mapiat, na ramoot paŇčan Galio, ma anna moca mba irikca mbiratke. 
\s1 Pola Antiok auŇč aniac mac nda mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 18:18 \xt Ndu 6.18, na Up 21.24, na Ro 16.1\x*Ri, Pola Korinna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarap eaca taŇčga rai w…®t aniac Ňčgoin mamoat. Na an k…®dr…®kca Pola Korin t…®kcarica ma Senkiria auŇča taŇčga laruca an t…®kcarina mori, ma ndona paŇčanna lakoar makatacat. Na an kirara Ňčgaua ma RaraŇč Aetaniacap kam leacatna. Aintik an leacatna kamna rai an maiatke, ma an Senkiria t…®kca ma ndona lakoar makatacat. Karica ma minmo kam laŇč neaŇčga, ma Pirisilaapa Akuwilap mina laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Siria pitrik aniac mataŇčgat.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 18:19 \xt Up 17.17\x*Karica mina taŇčga Epesus auŇč aniac ndaruca Pola Pirisilaapa Akuwila mbaniŇčmo anna t…®kcarica. Ma ndo Ňčgoinna ma Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca taŇčga mbukca minap mambopri.  
\v 20 Na mina manmo ndoriap eaca k…®dr…®k rocotta eac ndopatke, ma makariat.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Ro 1.10, na 1 Ko 4.19, na Ib 6.3, na Ie 4.15\x*Ainda moca ma minmo t…®kcarica taŇčna moca ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniaca ndo toŇčgo te, aku nen ndambuŇča mac nda k…®pnande.‚ÄĚ Karica ma laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca ma Epesus auŇč t…®kcamacariat.  
\v 22 Ri, mina taŇčga Sisaria auŇč aniac ndaruca, ma Ierusalem magacat, ma gaca taŇčga anna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunmo ra laŇč neaŇčgacarica, ma Siria pitrikna auŇč aniac Antiok mataŇčgat. 
\p  
\v 23 Karica ma an Antiok auŇčmo emtem ndeaca, an ŇčgetacndiŇča ma Ňčgepca Galesiana pitrikna auŇčembapa, Pirigiana pitrikna auŇčembta inikca mbukca taŇčri, Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo moi gagarana. 
\s1 Apolosa Epesusna auŇč aniaca t…®kca kam wiwitirina 
\p  
\v 24 Na Iudana ramoot ianna mana ia Apolos, ma k…®pca Epesus ndeacrena, mana aemma manmo Aleksandriana auŇč aniaca t…®kca m…®ratna. Na ma kamma mataua mboprina ramoot ian, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapca tirca eacrena kambca ma mataua lamŇčirena.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 18:25 \xt Up 19.3, na Ro 12.11\x*Ri, mina manmo Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgaina mataua riptia maica, mana iro inikca Iesusa raŇčtaŇčgaina moca gargar Ňčgoin. Na ma meikramta…®rmo Iesusna kammo wandoŇč Ňčgoinna minmo an kamb ndoprina, na ma Ionna neaŇčrena k…®tac puk niŇčgik ndamŇčirina.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 18:26 \xt Up 19.8\x*Ainda moca ma taŇčga Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mbukca, iro gargar mbuŇča ma mba nanambiri, ma mimo mambopri. Na Pirisilaapa Akuwila maniŇča man mboprina kambca waraca, maniŇča manmo ndoniŇčna kac naaŇčg…®a taŇčga, mamo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Taup Ňčgoinna raŇčgaina mariptiat.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 18:27 \xt 1 Ko 3.6, na 2 Ko 3.1\x*Karica anna iŇčmbaia Apolosa Akaia pitrikca taŇčna moatke, an Epesusna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara mana iro inikca moi gagraca taŇčna moca, mina timbiŇč rapar ianna tirca aindopatna, ‚ÄúAkaiana Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r, ne Apolosmo aŇčg…®.‚ÄĚ Ainda moca Apolosa an timbiŇč rapar aŇčg…®ca ma min ndambuŇč mataŇčgat. Na ma minap eac te, ma minmo otacna. Na an RaraŇč Aetaniaca kadmaica mina mana r…®pacrina meikramta…®rmo Apolosa minmo otacna.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 18:28 \xt Up 9.22, na 17.3, na 18.5\x*Ri, ma meikramta…®rta outmo kam gargar mbuŇča wiwitia mambopat, mina an Iudana katta mboprina kammo ma wandoŇč mambopat. Ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Timbigta Kapna kambmo, wiwitica mina lamŇči garacna, Iesusa ma RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot. 
\c 19  
\s1 Pola Epesus auŇč aniaca t…®kca kam wiwitiatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 19:1 \xt 1 Ko 1.12, na 3.6\x*Na an m…®nna Apolosa Korin ndeacri, Pola an Esiana pitrik inikna auŇčembmo okeca mawatri, ma taŇčga Epesus ndaruri, ma anna inikna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r ndeidmo mawatat.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 19:2 \xt Up 2.38, na 8.16\x*Ri, ma minmo madigiat, ‚ÄúAn k…®dr…®kca, ne r…®pacatnanna ne ŇäeroŇč Ratta aŇčg…®rat ki, wanaiŇč?‚ÄĚ Na mina ainda rutica mambopat, ‚ÄúAia an ŇäeroŇč Rat ndoprena reacna kam emtemma mba waracrenanna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 \x - \xo 19:3 \xt Mt 3.11\x*Ainda moca ma minmo mac madigiat, ‚ÄúNe titocna k…®tac puk aŇčg…®atna?‚ÄĚ Na mina aindoprina, ‚ÄúAia Ion neaŇčrina k…®tac puk an aŇčg…®atna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 19:4 \xt Mt 3.11, na Mk 1.4, na 1.7-8, na Lk 3.4, na 3.16, na In 1.15, na 1.26-30, na Up 18.25, na 19.4\x*Ri, Pola minmo aind mambopat, ‚ÄúŇägaua Ionna meikramta…®rmo k…®tac puk neaŇčri ma aindopatna, ‚ÄėNe iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica k…®tac puk aŇčg…®. Te, aukna iŇčmbai nak…®k…®pna ramootmo r…®pac, an ramoot, anna Iesus.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 Karica an meikramta…®ra an kamma waraca mina Kacoot Iesusna i mbuŇča k…®tac puk maaŇčg…®at.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 19:6 \xt Up 2.4, na 6.6, na 8.17, na 10.44-46\x*Ri, Pola ndona parmo mina paŇčaind tambatta t…®katke, ŇäeroŇč Ratta minmo mbukatke, mina muruŇča Ňčgepca auŇčembta kamb puŇčga mambopri, na mina rambca morena kamb toprena.  
\v 7 Na an ramta…®rta m…®nna parniŇčapa mbut mbuniŇčna m…®n. 
\p  
\v 8 Ri, karwai mbonkacna m…®nna ma Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mbukca minmo tac toc Ňčgoinna t…®kca minmo mimitpacna an kam wembaŇč laŇčmo mawiwitiat. Ri, minmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuocna kam ndopca mina iroar inkar moi Ňčgepna.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 19:9 \xt Up 9.2, na 2 Ko 6.14-18, na 2 Pi 2.2\x*Ainda mori, mina ndeida ndorita iroar inkara moa gagraca an kambmo waracna karirina, aintik mina r…®pac Ňčgocor. Mina Ňčgepca Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgaina taup laŇčmo kamb t…®pemb Ňčgorikmo mambopri, aintik Polapa Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r, mina Iudana mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mba taŇčrenan. Ainda moca Pola taŇčga Tiranasna ririptina kaca taŇčga anna t…®kca meikramta…®rmo ma mimitpacna kam ndoprina. Na ma IudanaŇčgepta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaca mba mac nda taŇčitndai.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 19:10 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Ri, ma ainda moca taŇčga gui mbuniŇčna m…®n, aintik an Esiana pitrik inik ndeacrina Iudanandapa Girikna meikramta…®ra muruŇča Kacootna kamma waracatna. 
\s1 Sikewana nuikca ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreacmo towai mo kecarina towaiatna 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 19:11 \xt Up 14.3\x*Ainda mori, RaraŇč Aetaniaca ndona gargara Polna para t…®kca ma an gargar mbuŇča ainta Ňčgagatracara moa larurina.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 19:12 \xt Up 5.15\x*Ri, meikramta…®ra mana gagabur murirena iŇčit waŇčgorapa mana r…®ktacniŇča leacrena raraŇčgir mananmo aŇčg…®ca roumbbebta meikramta…®rmo an t…®kca mina laiŇčga mori, na ŇčerŇčgaur Ňčgorik toco minmo t…®kcarirena. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 19:13 \xt Mk 9.38\x*Na Iudana ramta…®r ndeida mina tamtamma taŇčga an ŇčerŇčgaur Ňčgorik mbukca eacrina meikramta…®rta ŇčerŇčgaura moa kecarirena, mina Kacoot Iesusna i mbuŇča towaica an ŇčerŇčgaur Ňčgorikmo ootta mandacrena. Ri, mina gaindopatna, ‚ÄúGan Iesus, Pola wiwitirinan aku nemo mana i mbuŇča gagara aindopnande, ne Ňčgepca laruca taŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 Ainda mori, Iudana taup ndamoot paŇčan ian, mana ia Sikewa. Na mana nuikpaikca parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇč, mina ndori ainta kirara mori taŇčrina.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 19:15 \xt Mk 1.24, na 1.34\x*Karica oit ianna an ramta…®ra ainda moca ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreac ianna minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúAku Iesusmo lamŇčirena, na Pol motocmo aku lamŇčirena, na ne mandaibin?‚ÄĚ  
\v 16 Ainda moca an ŇčeroŇč Ňčgoreaca mbukca eacrina ramootta, an ramta…®ra watca min nambatta putrikica minmo tamtamma pia Ňčgocraiatke, mina tikemb Ňčgapoikmo w…®Ňčga otrea minap rapaca mina lourkamdera, racaindtan ndaruca an kac t…®kcarica, k…®pcamacariat.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 19:17 \xt Lk 7.16, na Up 2.43, na 5.5, na 5.11\x*Ri, Epesus ndeacrina Giriknanapa Iudanan, mina anna watta rapaca mina mananambiat. Ri, mina Kacoot Iesusna imo aŇčg…®a Ňčgepca manmo totori bagaraniac maneaŇčgat.  
\v 18 Ainda moatke, meikramta…®r w…®t aniaca mar…®pacat. Ri, mina k…®pca kabena meikramta…®rta lamn…®acmo, ndori morina t…®pemb Ňčgorikmo mbopca malaruat.  
\v 19 Na mina ndeida koikapa ndururca morinanna, mina ndorita ndururca morina timbigta kaip, aŇčg…®a larua meikramta…®r muruŇčna outta t…®kca marotacat. Na an timbigta kaipa, min Ňčgopoikna kitcartukarta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 50 tausena kitukndukna m…®n.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 19:20 \xt Up 6.7, na 12.24\x*Ainda mori, Kacootna kam wembaŇč laŇča meikramta…®rmo moa magagrari, mina r…®t…®paikca moca gagraca mina taŇčga kam wembaŇč laŇčmo kabena auŇčembmo wiwitica tamtamma taŇčri. 
\s1 Epesusnanda Polap kaega moatna 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 19:21 \xt Up 18.21, na 20.22, na 23.11, na Ro 1.13, na 15.24-28, na Gal 2.1\x*Karica an reikta iŇčmbaia ŇäeroŇč Ratta Polmo aoca Ňčgepca ma ndona iroa moca, ma Masedoniana pitrikapa Akaiana pitrikca taŇčgacarica iŇčmbaia ma Ierusalemma taŇčnande. Ainda moatke, ma aindopatna, ‚ÄúAku anna taŇčca, annan mai te, aku Rom motocmo watna taŇčnande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 \x - \xo 19:22 \xt Ro 16.23, na 2 Ti 4.20\x*Ri, ma ndo Ňčgotacrena ramootniŇč, Timotiapa Erastusmo outta mandaca maniŇča Masedoniana pitrik mataŇčgat. Na ma ndo Ňčgoinna, karica ma Esia pitrikna auŇč Epesusmo teker emtem maeacat. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 19:23 \xt 2 Ko 1.8\x*Karica an m…®n mbuŇča meikramta…®r ndeida Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgairena meikramta…®rap maipuŇčgat, na mina minapmo kamb anik puŇčga ipuŇčga mambopri.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 19:24 \xt Up 16.16-19\x*Na ramoot ianna mana ia Demitirius ma silwa mbuŇča mina m…®r…®praraŇč Artemisna dawarta kaik tekirnoikca moca kituknduk aŇčg…®rena, na mana aiŇč kabena ramta…®rmo anna aiŇč neaŇčga mina kitukndukar anikca an mbuŇča moca aŇčg…®rena.  
\v 25 Ri, Demitiriusa an ramta…®rapa kabena ramta…®ra an kirarirta aiŇča morenan aŇčg…®a punica, ma minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúRamta…®r ne lamŇčirena aia an aiŇč mbuŇča kituknduk aŇčg…®rena.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 19:26 \xt Ňäap 115.4, na Ais 44.10-20, na Ier 10.3, na Up 17.29, na 2 Ti 1.15\x*Na an ramoot Pol, ma meikramta…®r w…®t aniacmo aŇčg…®ca mina iroarmo moa uriracri, ne watrinan, na ne waracrina. Ainda moca ma Epesus niŇčgikca mba mori, ma moca taŇčga Esiana pitrikna auŇčembmo kocnai aŇčg…®na mamoek. Na ma gaindoprina, ‚ÄėAn par mbuŇča morina dawara anna m…®rpembraraiŇč, anna RaraŇč Aetaniac gidikca wanaiŇč.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Ri, ma gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúPolna kamma, ma aina kituknduk aŇčg…®rena taupmo mo mboracnande. Na kabena reac toca gaind, mana kamma aina m…®r…®praraŇčna kac, Artemisnanmo moca meikramta…®rta iroarmo ma reac wanaiŇč toc ndarunande. Ňägaua meikramta…®r muruŇča Esiana pitrikapa kabena pitrikca an m…®r…®praraŇčna meaca mbendeirena. Na Polna kamma mandeaca mana i aniaca mo kecarina mamoek.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28 Karica ramta…®ra an kamma waraca mina nikembkatacarica, mina kamb anik keri. Aind mambopri, ‚ÄúArtemis ma Epesusna m…®r…®praraŇč, ma aniac Ňčgoin.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 \x - \xo 19:29 \xt Up 20.4, na 27.2, na Ro 16.23, na 1 Ko 1.14, na Kol 4.10, na Pm 1.24\x*Ri, an auŇč aniacna inik ndeacrina meikramta…®ra muruŇča lamŇčia paurica. Mina kamb keca, mina Ňčgepca Epesusna punirena taupca taŇčga mina Gaiusapa Aristakas mbaniŇčmo mautiŇčgat, an ramootniŇča maniŇča Masedonia pitrikna ramootniŇč, na maniŇča Polap taŇčrena.  
\v 30 Ainda moca Pola an meikramta…®rta r…®k ndaruna mori, anna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra manmo mak…®racat.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 19:31 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Na Esiana ramta…®r paŇčaind ndeida mina Polna aikor, mitoca mamo kam gargar neaŇč taŇčga aindoprina, ‚ÄúU an mina tumbunna kai mbuk teac.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 32 Ri, an meikramta…®ra kamb anik makeri, ndeida reac ianna kamb makeri, na ndeida kabena reacna kamb makeri, ainda mori an punirina tumbunna kocnaia lamŇčia pauricarica. Na mina w…®t aniaca lamŇči Ňčgocor, kaina moca mina k…®pca tumbunna t…®krina.  
\v 33 Karica Iudana meikramta…®ra Aleksander Ňčgacrina ramootmo, aŇčg…®a an meikramta…®rta outta w…®t…®kca, na mina ndeida mamo watca, mamo an reacna makukca morina ramoot ndopca. Ri, Aleksandera mina kam ruti mbopna moca, ma minmo watitina moca ndona par aŇčg…®a maŇčgepat.  
\v 34 Ri, mina wattatnanna ma Iudana ramoot, aintik mina muruŇča kocnai kamb anik keca taŇčga k…®dr…®k rocot keca aindoprina, ‚ÄúArtemis aina Epesusna m…®r…®praraŇč, ma aniac Ňčgoin.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 35 Ainda moatke, timbiŇč rapara tirrena Epesusnanta, ramoot paŇčan teker ianna minmo mbopca mina watitiatna mbatca, ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe Epesusna meikramta…®r ne warac, gan tiacarpaikna meikramta…®r muruŇča lamŇčirenan, gan auŇč aniac Epesusna m…®r…®praraŇč meac Artemisna kacapa mana dana wautta ne wembaca eacrenanna, an wautta ma auŇč tamuŇč ndiŇč Ňčgirikatnan.  
\v 36 Na meac co ramoot ianna anna kam nda mbopna m…®nna wanaiŇč, aintik ne watitica eac. Na ne anna moca reac ianna kai tawi mo teac.  
\v 37 Ri, ne gan ramootniŇč aŇčg…®ca k…®prina, na maniŇča an aina m…®r…®praraŇča mbendeirena kacna reac ianna mba mak…®mri. Na maniŇča aina m…®r…®praraŇč meacmo peperena kam Ňčgoreac ianna mba mbopri.  
\v 38 Aintik Demitiriusapa mana aiŇč kabena ramta…®ra mina ramoot ianmo ipuŇčna mo te, anna laŇč ritri waparac mona k…®dr…®kca maeacreke. Na ritri waparacna ramta…®r paŇčainda maeacreke, mina an kammo ritri moi wandoŇčainande.  
\v 39 Na ne kamb ndeida mac eac te, ne taŇčca tumbunna punirena taupca t…®kca, ra ian larapac te, anmo mbopi wandoŇčai.  
\v 40 Aintik ne warac, ramta…®r paŇčainda an kambca warac te, aia makuk aŇčg…®na m…®n Ňčgoin. Mandeac ra aia morina reaca, ma m…®n…®Ňč kocor, na mina aimo an tumbunna punirena m…®n…®Ňčna digi te, kaina moca aia kamb anik keca, aca mbopri, na aia mina kam ianna mba rutiatke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 41 Karica ma kamb topca maica ma an meikramta…®rmo mbag…®rica mina mataŇčgat. 
\c 20  
\s1 Pola Masedoniana pitrikapa Girisna pitrik mataŇčgat 
\p  
\v 1 Karica an k…®dr…®kar Ňčgorikca maiatna mbatca, Pola kam neaŇčga taŇčga an Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra man ndambuŇča taŇčga ma minmo mimitpacapa, mina moi gagarana kamb topca maica, karica ma minmo ra laŇč ndopca, ma Ňčgepca Masedonia pitrik mataŇčgat.  
\v 2 Ri, ma an Masedonia pitrikna auŇčembta inikca mbukca minmo reik w…®t aniacna kamb topca, minmo moi gagrana moca, moa maica, karica ma taŇčga Girisna pitrik malaruat.  
\v 3 Ma anmo karwai mbonkacna m…®n maeacat. Karica ma laŇčgum mbuŇča Siria taŇčna mori, Iudananda mamo mo menacna kamb leacatke. Ri, ma ndona iroa moca ma Masedonia ndiŇč mac nda mataŇčgat.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 20:4 \xt Up 19.29, na 21.29, na Epe 6.21\x*Na manap taŇčrina ramta…®rpaikca, Sopata, ma Beria auŇč aniacnan, na ma Pirasna nuoc, na Aristakasapa Sekandas maniŇča Tesalonika auŇč aniacna ramootniŇč, na Gaius ma Derbe auŇč aniacnan, na Timoti toco, ma an auŇč aniacnan, na Tikikusapa Toropimus maniŇča Esiana pitrik waŇčna ramootniŇč, na mina muruŇča Polap mataŇčgat.  
\v 5 Karica an ramta…®rpaikca aimo outmbai mataŇčgat, mina aina moca Toroas auŇč aniac ndabinandet.  
\v 6 Ri, Iudananda is Ňčgocorta tapac gagamna ra maiatke, aia laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Pilipai auŇč t…®kcarica Toroas auŇč mataŇčgat, na ma aimo rai parmbai mamoat. Na aia Toroas auŇčmo rai parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇč maeacat. 
\s1 Iutikusa kac ŇčgetacndiŇča irikca menaca Pola manmo mac nda moa Ňčgepatna 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 20:7 \xt Up 2.42, na 2.46, na 1 Ko 16.2, na KIEK 1.10\x*Karica raita Ňčgatna ra lacauna mouŇča aia tapac r…®mb…®tca amna tumbunna t…®kri, Pola ma mimitpacna kambmo aimo mbopca taŇčtaŇčga mouŇč r…®kniŇč mat…®kcat, na auŇč raru te, ma aimo t…®kcarica Toroas auŇč aniaca taŇčnandet.  
\v 8 Na mina an kacmo tamuŇčmbaina diabca t…®kca anna mimitpac maaŇčg…®at, an kacna inikca memetacna taca…®r w…®tta mitpaca maica eacrena.  
\v 9 Na an kacna wat mbukrena taupca, nuoc Ňčgam ianna ma anna mbiraca eacrina, mana ia Iutikus, na an mouŇč r…®kniŇča Pola mbopri, an nuoca ma lamn…®ac numbca, ma Ňčgoanirena, na ma Ňčgoanirenan mbuŇča ma ndarekrekecarica ma an wat mbukrena taup ndiŇča, irikca p…®k…®nna keca mamenacat.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 20:10 \xt 1 GRP 17.21\x*Ri, Pola minap irikca an nuocmo, potac aŇčg…®ca minmo aind mambopat, ‚ÄúNe kai kadmai teac, ma mba menacri.‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 20:10 \ft An kamna m…®n…®Ňč Ňčgoinna gaind, manmo k…®tac meraca mamo potaca ma minmo aindopatna, ma mba menacri.\f* 
\v 11 Karica Pola mac tamuŇčna diab mac gaca tapac aŇčg…®ca r…®mb…®tca ambri, ma minap kamb topca taŇč, taŇčga auŇč raruatke, ma min t…®kcarica mataŇčgat.  
\v 12 Ri, mina an menaca mac nda Ňčgepatna nuocmo aŇčg…®ca mana kac naaŇčg…®a mataŇčgat, na mina toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin. 
\s1 Pola Toroas auŇč t…®kcarica Miletus auŇča taŇčgatna 
\p  
\v 13 Karica aia laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Asos auŇča outmbaica lembaia taŇčga malaruat, na Pola malambiri, na ma aimo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe taŇčca aukmo anna t…®kca aŇčg…®na,‚ÄĚ ma ndo mbatŇčdiŇča taŇčnande.  
\v 14 Aintik ma k…®pca Asos ndaruca aia watca, man aŇčg…®ca, aia laŇčgum naŇčgabukca aia Mitilini auŇč mataŇčgat.  
\v 15 Na Mitilini ŇčgetacndiŇča iŇčmbaina ra, aia Kios muta taŇčga malaruat, anna t…®kca kabena ra, aia Samos mut mac taŇčga malaruat. Na iŇčmbai Ňčgoinna ra, aia Miletus auŇča taŇčga malaruat.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 20:16 \xt Up 18.21, na 24.17, na 1 Ko 16.8\x*Na Pola ndona iroa moca ma Epesusa taŇčna mba toŇčgori, ma an Esiana pitrikmo k…®dr…®k rocot ndeteaca, ma mba toŇčgori. Ma ndomo Ierusalemmo an Iudananta amtiam aniacna ra, mina Pentikos Ňčgacrena rana moca anna tatkirina. Ma ndomo anna watna. 
\s1 Pola Epesusna tumbunna ramta…®r paŇčaindmo watcarica, ma kocnai taŇčna 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt Up 18.21\x*Karica aia Miletus auŇč ndaruca, Pola Epesus auŇč aniacna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunna ramta…®r paŇčaindmo kam neaŇčga taŇčga, mimo ndo ndambuŇč nak…®pna.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 20:18 \xt Up 18.19, na 19.10\x*Ri, mina k…®pca laruri, ma minmo aindopatna, 
\p ‚ÄúNe ndori aukna t…®pemb kirarirca ne lamŇčirena, aku Ňčgaua Esia pitrikmo outmbai nak…®patnanna memetmbaca aku nenap eacrina.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 20:19 \xt Up 20.3\x*Na ne lamŇčirena, memetmbaca Iudana ramta…®ra kamb leaca aukna an aiŇča mo irikca aukmo kakadmai neaŇčna moreke, anna aukmo moca eacrena, na aku mba karirenanna, wanaiŇč, aku ndona ia mba aŇčg…®a Ňčgepri, aku Kacootna aiŇč niŇčgikca morena.  
\v 20 Na ne lamŇčirena aku memetmbaca wiwitireke, nen Ňčgopotacna reac ianna mba utiŇčrenanna, nena tumnambta outapa nena kaik barerta inikca aku nemo riptirena.  
\v 21 Na memetmbaca aku Iudananapa Giriknanmo mimitpac neaŇčca, mimo iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica, RaraŇč Aetaniaca raŇčgai te, aina Kacoot Iesusa r…®pacna.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 20:22 \xt Up 19.21\x*Na mandeaca ŇäeroŇč Ratta aukmo moca aku Ierusalemma taŇčnande, na anna t…®kca aukmo kaina reaca laru te, aku mba lamŇčireke.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 20:23 \xt Up 19.21, na 21.4, na 21.11, na 1 Te 3.3\x*Aku lamŇčirena, tenna auŇčemb anikta inik aku taŇč te, ŇäeroŇč Ratta aukmo mbopca waracrena, makukar anikapa kac Ňčgoreaca mbumbukca aukna lambia maeacreke. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 20:24 \xt Up 21.13, na Ro 8.35, na 2 Ko 4.1, na 4.16, na Gal 1.1, na 2 Ti 4.7\x*‚ÄúNa aku ndona watmo anmo reac aniac ndopca an nake mba lamŇčiri, na aku ndona watmo nda utiŇčcari nake, mba moa gagrari. WanaiŇč. Aku ndona aiŇča moi korwina, na an aiŇča Kacoot Iesusa aukmo neaŇčrina. An aiŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacna kakadmaina kam wembaŇč laŇč wiwitina. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúAintik laiplacar, ne warac, Ňčgaua aku nenap eacri, taŇčri, aku RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuocna kam wiwitirina. Na mandeaca aku lamŇčirena, iŇčmbai ne aukna inpaŇčanna mba mac watitndai.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 20:26 \xt Up 18.6, na 2 Ko 7.2\x*Aintik aku nemo mbopca waracrena nena ianna Ňčgocrai te, anna aukna makukca wanaiŇč.  
\v 27 Anna moca aku mba irikca mbiracri, aku RaraŇč Aetaniacna iroarta reikmo muruŇča nemo mambopri. Aku ianna mba utiŇčri.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 20:28 \xt 1 Ko 12.28, na 1 Ti 4.16, na Ib 9.14, na 1 Pi 1.19, na 5.2-4\x*Aintik ne ndoritake, matau wat, na RaraŇč Aetaniacna Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbun motocmo, minmo wat, an meikramta…®r ma ndona Nuocna racaindpaik mbuŇč Ňčgoikatna. Nemo ŇäeroŇč Ratta larapaca an RaraŇč Aetaniacna sipsiparta ŇčginaŇča mona.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 20:29 \xt Mt 7.15, na In 10.12, na 2 Pi 2.1\x*Na aku lamŇčirena, aku t…®kcarica taŇč te, raŇčna piriŇč kunnara k…®pca nena r…®kca t…®kca sipsiparmo mo Ňčgocrainande.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 20:30 \xt 1 Ti 1.20, na 1 Io 2.19\x*Te, nena ndeid koinda Ňčgepca nemo paparuna kamb top te, Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo ndorica raŇčgaina moca.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 20:31 \xt Mk 13.37, na Up 19.8-10, na 1 Te 2.11\x*Aintik ne memetmbaca ndorimo matau wat, aku nemo morina t…®pemb kirarirmo, ne iroara kai ndarekrekke teac. Nena kabe, kabemo aku guiarpaik mbonkacna, inikna raiapa mouŇčemba, mba Ňčateri, nemo iro laŇč neaŇčrina. Na aku nemo riptiri, aukna lamn…®acniŇča timbi irikrena. 
\p  
\v 32 \x - \xo 20:32 \xt Up 26.18, na Epe 1.18, na Kol 1.12, na Ib 13.9\x*‚ÄúRi, mandeaca aku nemo RaraŇč Aetaniacna para t…®krina, na ne mana kakadmaina irona ndamŇčina, te, an kakadmaia ndo nemo otaca nemo moi gagraca nemo reik laiŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniac neaŇčrenanna, ma ndona larapacatna meikramta…®ra neaŇčrinan, ne toco aŇčg…®nandet. 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 20:33 \xt 1 Sml 12.3, na 1 Ko 9.11-12, na 2 Ko 7.2\x*‚ÄúNa aku ramoot ianna kituknduk, co tik Ňčgapaocna raraŇčitta mba toŇčgoca aŇčg…®renanna, wanaiŇč.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 20:34 \xt Up 18.3, na 1 Ko 4.12, na 1 Te 2.9\x*Ne ndori lamŇčirina, aku ndona par mbuŇča reikca moca ndo Ňčgotac te, aukap taŇčrenanmo otacrena.  
\v 35 \x - \xo 20:35 \xt Mt 10.8, na 2 Ko 11.9, na 11.12, na Epe 4.28, na 1 Te 4.11, na 2 Te 3.8\x*Ri, aiŇčira aku morinanna, aku nemo wandacrena, aia anna nagagraca an aiŇča mo. Te, aia an meikramta…®ra ndorimo otacna toawanaiŇč, aia minmo otacnande. Na an kamma aina Kacoot Iesusa mboprinan ndamŇči, ma gaindoprina, ‚ÄėRamootta reik aŇčg…®rinan ma toŇčtoŇčap, na ramootta ma ndona reik neaŇčrenanna mana toŇčtoŇča aniac Ňčgoin.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 36 \x - \xo 20:36 \xt Up 21.5\x*Karica Pola an kamb topca maica, ma tutupniŇč r…®mb…®tca ma an ramta…®r paŇčaindap mambendeiat.  
\v 37 Ri, iŇčmbaia mina Ňčgepca Polna parmo utiŇčga, manmo piapopotri, nanae bagaraniac mamoat.  
\v 38 \x - \xo 20:38 \xt Up 20.25\x*Ri, mina Polna moca kakadmai aniac Ňčgoin mamoat, na ma minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAku nena indepaŇčaindmo mba mac watitndai.‚ÄĚ Karica mina manmo laŇčgum naaŇčg…®ra taŇčga maŇčgabukat. 
\c 21  
\s1 Pola laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Ierusalemma taŇčna moca 
\p  
\v 1 Karica aia an ramta…®r paŇčaindmo t…®kcarica aia laŇčgum naŇčgabukca, aia Kos mutmo wandoŇč Ňčgoin mataŇčgat. Na iŇčmbaina ra, aia Rodes muta taŇčga malaruat, anna t…®kca aia mac taŇčga Patara auŇč magat.  
\v 2 Na Patara ŇčgetacndiŇča aia kabena laŇčgum ianna watca, na an laŇčgumma ma Ponisia pitrikca taŇčna mori tik, aia man naŇčgabukca aia mataŇčgat.  
\v 3 Na aia taŇčga Saiprus mutmo, aina par aeŇčmbaia wattacarica, aia taŇčga Siria pitrikca ndaruca, aia Tair auŇč aniaca matundocat. Na an laŇčgumma aia taŇčrinanna, ma an auŇčna reikap tik, mina an aŇčg…® gari aia anna moca an malambiat.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 21:4 \xt Up 20.23, na 21.12\x*Ri, aia rana Ňčgat kabena m…®nna rai, aia anna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r ndeidap maeacri. Anna t…®kca, anna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®ra ŇäeroŇč Ratta, minmo iroar laiŇč neaŇčga mina Polmo Ierusalemma taŇč narica k…®raca mbopca, mawaracat.  
\v 5 Karica laŇčgumma mac taŇčna moatke, aia taŇčna mori, minapa mina meikmombonikap, mina aimo auŇč aniacmo raekca warkica mataŇčri, na aia maŇčara t…®kca aia minap tutpemb r…®mb…®tca mambendeiat.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 21:6 \xt Up 20.36\x*Ri, aia laŇčgum naŇčgabukna mori, aia minmo kam laŇč neaŇčga, mitoco aimo kam laŇč neaŇčga, mina ndorita auŇč mac nda mataŇčgat. 
\s1 Sisaria auŇč aniaca t…®kca ramma morena ramoot Agabusa Polmo kam ian mambopat 
\p  
\v 7 Karica aia Tair auŇč aniacmo t…®kcarica aia lembaia taŇčga Tolemes auŇč aniaca taŇčga malaruat. Anna t…®kca, aia anna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacarmo ra laŇč neaŇčga, minapmo ra kabe maeacat.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 21:8 \xt Up 6.5, na 8.5, na 8.26, na 8.40, na Epe 4.11, na 2 Ti 4.5\x*Ri, iŇčmbaina ra, aia Tolemes auŇč aniac t…®kcarica aia taŇčga Sisaria auŇč aniac malaruat. Karica aia taŇčga RaraŇč Aetaniacna kam wembaŇč laŇča wiwitirina ramoot Pilipna kac maeacat. Na Pilip, mina mamo Ierusalemma t…®kca parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇčap larapacatna ramoot ian, na ma up aŇčg…®rena ramta…®rmo opotacna aiŇča morena ramoot ian.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 21:9 \xt Iol 2.28, na Up 2.17\x*Na ma mombour paur niŇčgikap, na mina laŇčgo Ňčgocor, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna kammo rambca moa mboprena meik. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 21:10 \xt Up 11.28\x*Ri, rai ndepikca aia an ndeaca, ramma morena ramoot ianna, mana ia Agabus, ma Iudia pitrik t…®kcarica ma Sisaria auŇč aniac mairikat.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 21:11 \xt In 21.18, na Up 20.23, na 21.33\x*Karica ma ai ndambuŇč nak…®pca, Polna weaond aŇčg…®ca ma ndona parniŇčapa orniŇč maleacat, ri, ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúŇäeroŇč Ratta gaindoprina, ‚ÄėGan t…®pna kirar mbuŇča, Iudananda Ierusalem ndeacrenan, mina gan weaondna aetmo ainda leacnande, mina manmo Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta para t…®knande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 21:12 \xt Mt 16.22\x*Ri, aiapa an ndeacrinanna muruŇča an kamma waraca, aia Polmo Ierusalemma taŇč narica, aia aemaŇčmaŇčap manmo k…®raca mambopri.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 21:13 \xt Up 20.24\x*Ainda mori, ma aimo nda rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúKaina moca ne aea aukna iroa moa Ňčgocraiapek? Aku kac Ňčgoreaca taŇčna moca kocroca eacrena, na mina aukmo mo menacna mbop te, an toco aku Ierusalemma menaca aina Kacoot Iesusna i aŇčg…® Ňčgepna kocroca mina lambirena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 14 Ri, aia ainda waracrina, Pol, ma anna tataŇčna iro aniacap tik, aia manmo k…®raca mbopna towanaiŇč. Karica aia gaindopatna, ‚ÄúReaca Kacootta laruna toŇčgorinanna, watcarica ma laru.‚ÄĚ 
\ms1 Pola Iudiana kac Ňčgoreac ndeacri, ramta…®r paŇčainda mana kamma ritri waparaca moatna 
\mr (21.15‚ÄĒ26.32) 
\s1 Pola Ierusalemma taŇčga laruatna 
\p  
\v 15 Karica aia rai ndeida an ndeaca taŇčga, iŇčmbai aia Ňčgepca reik kocroca aia Ierusalem mataŇčgat.  
\v 16 Ri, Sisariananda Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®r ndeida, mitoca Ňčgepca aiap mataŇčgat. Na mina aimo Saiprusna ramoot ianna kac naaŇčg…®a mataŇčgat. An ramootna ia M…®nason, ma Ňčgau Ňčgoinna Iesusna iŇča raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta ramoot ian. Ri, aia mana kac maeacat.  
\v 17 Karica aia Ierusalemma taŇčga laruatke, anna Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara aimo toŇčtoŇčap tik, mina aimo aoca aŇčg…®ca mataŇčgat. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 21:18 \xt Up 15.2, na 15.13, na Gal 1.19, na 2.9\x*Na iŇčmbaina ra, Pola aiap, Iemisa watna mataŇčgat. An k…®dr…®k toco mina Iesusa r…®pacrena meikramta…®rta ramta…®r paŇčaindap k…®pca mapuniat.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 21:19 \xt Up 15.4, na 15.12, na Ro 15.18-19\x*Ri, Pola an ramta…®r paŇčaindmo ra laŇč neaŇčga, ma minmo ndo moatna reikca RaraŇč Aetaniaca mana para t…®kca, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta r…®kca t…®kca moatnanmo, ma minmo an reikmo, muruŇča mataua maniniat. 
\s1 Ramta…®r paŇčainda Polmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca taŇčna mambopat 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 21:20 \xt Up 15.1, na 15.5, na 22.3, na Ro 10.2, na Gal 1.14\x*Ainda moca an ramta…®r paŇčainda Polna kamma waraca, mina RaraŇč Aetaniacna i aŇčg…®a Ňčgepca aindoprina, ‚ÄúKaka u lamŇčirena Iudana meikramta…®r w…®t aniac Ňčgoinna Iesusmo mar…®pacri. Na an meikramta…®ra muruŇča mina T…®p Wand…®kca raŇčgaina iro gargar aniacap.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 21:21 \xt Up 16.3, na Gal 2.3\x*Ri, anna ramta…®r ndeida mina gainda waraca, aindoprena, ‚ÄėU Pol, u minmo gainda riptirena, ‚ÄúAn Iudananda mina Iudana meikramta…®ra wanaiŇčnanta r…®k ndeacrenanna, mina Mosesna T…®p Wand…®kca kai raŇčgai teac. Na mina ndorita nuikpitikta tikiŇčita kai katac teac, co mina atuna kirarira kai raŇčgai teac.‚ÄĚ‚Äô  
\v 22 Na aia lamŇčirena, mina un k…®prina kamma waracrina, na aia unmo tida moit?  
\v 23 \x - \xo 21:23 \xt Ndu 6.13-21\x*Aintik aia kam leacrina, na iro ianna unmo anna raŇčgaina, na ramta…®r paur mina RaraŇč Aetaniacap kamma babuca eacrena.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 21:24 \xt Up 18.18\x*Na u an ramta…®rmo aŇčg…®ca, ne muruŇča RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®acmo rat ndaruna t…®p kirara raŇčgai. Na u mina g…®mbamba mona reikta kitukndukmo u minmo otac te, an ramta…®ra ndorita paŇčaindta lakoarmo utnande. Na u an t…®pna kirara mo te, mina lamŇčinande, an kamma mina unmo mboprenanna, anna paparuna kam, na mina lamŇčinande, u toco T…®p Wand…®kca raŇčgairena.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 21:25 \xt Up 15.29\x*Na aia atuna timbiŇč rapar ianna tirca Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo Iesusa r…®pacrenanmo aindoprina, ‚ÄėNe mina r…®Ňčga menaca ndorita m…®rpembraraiŇčta dawarta outta t…®krena Ňčgoaebca kai am teac, na orapa…®r paurna Ňčgoaebmo mina mana logotmo kaorikca ma menaceknanna kai am teac, na Ňčgoaebca racaindapnanmo kai am teac. Te, ne an kabena meikap tataŇčna meacramootna kaŇčtertaapna t…®p kirara morena meikramta…®rta t…®pemb kirarira kai mo teac.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 \x - \xo 21:26 \xt Ndu 6.13, na Up 24.18, na 1 Ko 9.20\x*Ainda moca Pola an ramta…®r paur aŇčg…®ca, iŇčmbaina ra, ma ndona tikmo mo wandoŇčaica rat ndaruna, na an ramta…®rtan motoco ma ainda moatna. Ri, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca taup ndamta…®rmo mbop waracna, mina kaina ramo ndorimo wandoŇčaica g…®mbamba mona. 
\s1 IudanaŇčgepca Polmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca mamo mautiŇčgat 
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 21:27 \xt 2 Ti 1.15\x*Karica raita Ňčgatna ra mai ndambuŇča taŇčna mori, Iudananda Esiana pitrik ndiŇč nak…®prinan, mina Polmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca mamo anna t…®Ňča t…®kca watca, mina anna meikramta…®rta iroara moi Ňčgepca mina Polmo nikembkatca, manap ipuŇčga, manmo utiŇčna.  
\v 28-29 \x - \xo 21:28-29 \xt Esi 44.7, na Up 6.13, na 20.4, na 24.5-6, na 2 Ti 4.20\x*Ainda moca mina Ňčgaua wattatnanna, Epesus auŇčna Toropimusa ma Polap Ierusalem auŇč aniac ndeacri. Na mina gaind ndamŇčirina, ma Toropimusmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inik naaŇčg…®a mambukat. Ri, mina kam keca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúIsraelna ramta…®r, ne aimo otac, gan ramootta ma auŇčembta ramta…®rmo gan RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacapa aina barnanapa T…®p Wand…®kmo ipuŇčga riptirena.‚ÄĚ Na mina minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNa an niŇčgikca wanaiŇč, ma an Iudana ramta…®r wanaiŇčap aŇčg…®ca, gan RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukrinan, na an RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacmo mandeaca moca mana lamn…®aca ma rat Ňčgocor malaruri.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 30 Ri, Ierusalemna meikramta…®ra muruŇča an kamma waraca, Ňčgep Ňčgoreac naŇčgepca mina k…®pca tumbunna t…®kca Polmo utiŇčga mamo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca aŇčg…®a laruri, mina mana tiŇčmo tawi Ňčgoinna maleacat. 
\s1 Romna lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra Polmo mautiŇčgat 
\p  
\v 31 Na an k…®dr…®kca mina Polmo pi menacna mori, Romna lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna an kammo gaind mawaracat, ‚ÄúIerusalemna meikramta…®ra kaega moca tamtamma ruŇčrena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 Karica ma anduna Ňčgepca ndona paŇčaind tekirapa ruŇčrena ramta…®rap, aŇčg…®ca mina an Ňčgootta irikca an Ňčgoke watna. Ri, an IudanaŇčgepta ramta…®ra, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanapa mana ruŇčrena ramta…®r mbatca, mina Polmo mba mac piatke.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 21:33 \xt Up 20.23\x*Ainda moca an ramoot paŇčanna k…®pca Polmo utiŇčga, mana ramta…®rmo mbopca mina Polmo lawirta Ňčgat…®k mbuniŇč mbuŇč maleacat. Ri, ma minmo gaind madigiri, ‚ÄúMa mandai, na ma kaina reaca mo Ňčgocrairina?‚ÄĚ  
\v 34 Ri, an ndeacrina meikramta…®rta tumbun aniaca kamb anik keca ndeida kabena kam ndopri, ndeid toca kabena kam mac mambopri. Na mina ainda moatke, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna an kamna m…®n…®Ňča mba waraca garacatke, ri, ma ndona ruŇčrena ramta…®rmo mbopca mina Polmo ndorita eacrena kac naaŇčg…® taŇčna mambopat.  
\v 35 Karica Pola minap taŇčga an kacna tar ndambuŇča t…®katke, an ruŇčrena ramta…®ra wattatnanna, an meikramta…®ra mina mamo kocnai mo menacna mori tik, mina manmo pa…®rpaik mbuŇč naaŇčg…®ca kaca mbukna mamoat.  
\v 36 \x - \xo 21:36 \xt Lk 23.18, na In 19.15, na Up 22.22\x*Ri, an raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta m…®m…®atta mina iŇča raŇčgairenanna, kamb anik keca aindopatna, ‚ÄúMamo, mo menac.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola IudanaŇčgepmo ndona r…®pacrina nininia moatna 
\p  
\v 37 Karica mina mamo kac naaŇčg…® mbukna mori, Pola an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanmo Girikna kam mbuŇča mamo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAku umo kam ianna mbopna m…®n ki?‚ÄĚ Ri, an ramoot paŇčanna mamo rutica aindopatna, ‚ÄúU Girikna kamma lamŇčire ki?  
\v 38 \x - \xo 21:38 \xt Up 5.36-37\x*Na aku umo gaind ndamŇčiatna, umo an Isipna ramootta Ňčgaua ma runduŇč aniaca mo Ňčgepca 4,000na m…®nna ramta…®rpaik aŇčg…®ca bugrim mbuŇča ruŇčrenanmo, ma reik kocorta taupca minap aŇčg…®ca taŇčgatna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 39 Ri, Pola mana kammo rutica aindopatna, ‚ÄúWanaiŇč. Aku Iudana ramoot, na aukna auŇča Tarasus, ma Silisiana pitrik inik ndeacrena. Na aukna auŇča ma iap. LaŇč u aukmo wattacarica aku an meikramta…®rap mbopna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 40 Karica an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna mamo laŇč ndopatna mbatca, ma Ňčgepca tara w…®t…®kca ndona par mbuŇč naaŇčg…®ra Ňčgagoa, mina anna watca mina watiti te, ma mbopekna kamma mina anna waracna, ainda moca mina watitiri, ma minmo Iburuna kam mbuŇč mambopat. 
\c 22  
\m  
\v 1 Ri, ma mimo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAeterapa laiplacar ne warac, mandeaca aku nemo wandoŇč ndopna mamoek, aku reac Ňčgoreac ianna mba mori.‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 Karica mina waracrinanna, Pola mimo Iburuna kam mbuŇč ndopatke, mina watiticaria mawaracri. Na ma gaind mac mbopatna, 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 22:3 \xt Up 5.34-39, na 9.11, na 21.39, na 26.5, na Ro 10.2, na 2 Ko 11.22, na Gal 1.14, na Pil 3.5\x*‚ÄúAku Iudana ramoot, na aukna aemma aukmo Tarasus auŇča t…®kca m…®ratna, an auŇča Silisiana pitriknan. Na aku gan auŇč Ierusalemma t…®kca ramoot acnaiatna. Na Gamaliela ma aukna riripti, ma aukmo matau Ňčgoinna aina nicarta t…®pemb wandikmo aukmo riptiatna. Na aku an t…®pemb wandikta kirara raŇčgaina moca aiŇč aniaca morina. Na anmo moi gagra te, RaraŇč Aetaniaca toŇčgonande, na an t…®pna kirara ne morena.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 22:4 \xt Up 22.19, na 26.9-11, na Pil 3.6, na 1 Ti 1.13\x*\x - \xo 22:4 \xt Up 8.3\x*Ri, aku an Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo, moa menacrena. Na ramta…®r ndeidapa meikpitik ndeida, aku muoca lawirta Ňčgat…®k mbuŇč leaca, minmo kac Ňčgoreac naaŇčg…®a t…®krena.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 22:5 \xt Up 9.2\x*Na taup ndamoot paŇčan aniacapa mana ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®r paŇčainda mina an reaca aku morinanna, mina lamŇčirena mina nemo mbopna m…®n. Mina morina timbiŇč rapara aukmo neaŇčga aku anap aŇčg…®ca, aina Iudana ramta…®r paŇčainda Damaskus ndeacrinanmo neaŇč te, aku anna Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgairena meikramta…®rmo muoca leaca, Ierusalemma nda aŇčg…® k…®p te, mina minmo anna g…®rg…®r neaŇčna.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola ma ndo Iesusa r…®pacatna ninini mamoat 
\r (Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇč 9.3-19 na 26.12-18) 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 22:6 \xt Up 9.3, na 26.12-13\x*Karica Pola gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúRana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®ca, ramo r…®k Ňčgoinna t…®kri, aku Damaskus auŇč ndaruna mori. TamuŇčna auŇčna memetacna tac ianna aukmo anduna metaca korereca maaŇčg…®at.  
\v 7 Ri, aku pitrik Ňčgirikca keca, aku ramoot ianna kamma gaind mawaracat, ‚ÄėSol, Sol, u kaina moca aukmo moa Ňčgocrairena?‚Äô  
\v 8 Ri, aku rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄėKacoot, u mandai?‚Äô Na ma aukmo aindopatna, ‚ÄėAku Nasaretna Iesus, u aukmo moa Ňčgocrairenan.‚Äô  
\v 9 Na an aukap eacrina ramta…®ra mina an memetaca, mitoco mawatat, na aukap mboprina kamma mina mba waraca garacri. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúAinda moca, aku gaindopatna, ‚ÄėKacoot, aku mandeaca kaia moit?‚Äô Na Kacootta aukmo aindopatna, ‚ÄėU Ňčgepca Damaskus auŇča mbuk. Na ramoot ianna an ndeacrenanna, aku unmo baburina aiŇčna kambmo, ma unmo mbopnande.‚Äô  
\v 11 Ainda moatke, aku watna towanaiŇč, an tacna memetaca aukmo moca aukna lamn…®acniŇča mapurocat, aintik aukap taŇčrina ramta…®ra aukna par ŇčgutiŇčga auŇč naaŇčg…®ca mambukat. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 22:12 \xt Up 9.17, na 10.22, na 1 Ti 3.7\x*‚ÄúNa Damaskus ndeacrina ramoot wandoŇč laŇč ianna T…®p Wand…®kca mataua raŇčgairinan, mana ia Ananaias, na ma an ndeacrena. Na IudanaŇčgepca an ndeacrenanna mina mamo gaindoprena, ‚ÄėMa ramoot laŇč Ňčgoin.‚Äô  
\v 13 Ainda moca ma k…®pca aukna k…®t…®mma w…®t…®kca gaindopatna, ‚ÄėKaka Sol u mac wat,‚Äô aindopatke, aku anduna mamo raia mawatat.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 22:14 \xt Up 9.15, na 1 Ko 9.1, na 11.23, na Gal 1.12\x*Karica ma aukmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAina nicar Ňčgamrirta RaraŇč Aetaniac, ma unmo atuna babuca larapaca umo mana toŇčtoŇčna aiŇč ndamŇčina. Te, mana aiŇča morena ramoot wandoŇča u watnandet, na u mana kambca, mana up ndiŇč ndarueknanna u waracnandet.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 22:15 \xt Up 23.11, na 26.16\x*Na u mana up aŇčg…®ca mana kam wiwiti mbop te, meikramta…®ra muruŇča an reikca u watrenan, na waracrinanna mina lamŇčinande.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 22:16 \xt Up 2.21, na 9.11, na 9.18, na Ro 10.13, na Ib 10.22\x*Ainda moca u kaina moca lambica eacrena? U Ňčgepca mana i mbuŇča k…®tac puk aŇčg…® te, ma una t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukara mo kecarinande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\s1 RaraŇč Aetaniaca Polmo mandaca ma Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo kam wiwitiatna 
\p  
\v 17 Karica ma minmo gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúIŇčmbaia aku Ierusalem mac nda taŇčga laruca, RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca mbukca mbendeica eacri, aku manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram ian mawatat.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 22:18 \xt Up 9.29-30\x*Ri, aku Kacoot Iesusmo watca ma aukmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU tawi Ňčgoinna Ňčgepca Ierusalem t…®kcarica u taŇč, u gan ndeaca aukna kammo ganna wiwiti mbop te, ganna meikramta…®ra an kammo mba aŇčg…®itndai.‚Äô  
\v 19 \x - \xo 22:19 \xt Up 8.3, na 22.4, na 26.9-11\x*Karica aku Kacootmo rutica aindoprina, ‚ÄėMina ndori lamŇčirena Ňčgaua aku Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaikca mbukca an una r…®pacrena meikramta…®rmo muoca leaca, kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca minmo pirena.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 22:20 \xt Up 7.58, na 8.1\x*Na una kamma wiwitirena ramoot Stipenmo, aku w…®t…®kca eacri mina manmo moa menacatna, na ramta…®rta tik Ňčgapaocna reikca aku utiŇčga eacri, na mina manmo moa menacatke, aku toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin.‚Äô  
\v 21 \x - \xo 22:21 \xt Up 9.15, na 13.2, na 13.46, na Gal 1.15-16, na 1 Ti 2.7\x*Ri, Kacootta aukmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėU Ňčgepca taŇč, aku umo mon tawan Ňčgoinna Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnand tambuŇča mbag…®rica taŇčnandet.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rmo aindopatna, aku Romna ramoot 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 22:22 \xt Up 21.36\x*Ainda moca mina waraca k…®pca, an Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanta kamma waraca, mina nikembkatca mina Ňčgepca kam keca gaindoprina, ‚ÄúMamo mo menac, aindta ramootta ma gan ndeacna m…®nna wanaiŇč.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 Ri, mina kamb anikmo tamtam nakeca, ndorita tikemb Ňčgapoikmo riaŇčga tamtam nakecariri, na timgun motoco mina aŇčg…®ca tamuŇč makeri. An Polna mbopatna an kambca, mina mba toŇčgori.  
\v 24 Aintik lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna mbopca, lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra Polmo ndorita kac naaŇčg…®ca mataŇčgat. Ma minmo mbopca mina Polmo pi te, mana morena reik tamŇčina, mina kaina moca kamb anik keca manmo nikembkatrina.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 22:25 \xt Up 16.37\x*Karica mina manmo ramta…®ra pirena ikca leaca mamo pina mona kocrori, ma an ramoot paŇčanmo madigiat, ‚ÄúNe gan t…®p kirara morinanna, anna Romna auŇčna ramootmo ainta t…®p kirara morinanna anna laŇč ki, wanaiŇč? Ne aukmo wanaiŇča pina moca aukna kamma ritri waparaca mo Ňčgocor, anna laŇč ki?‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 26 Ri, an ramoot paŇčanna, an kamma waraca ma taŇčca ndona ramoot paŇčan aniacmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU kaia mona moek? An ramootta ma Romna ramoot ian.‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Karica an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniaca taŇčga Polmo watca madigiat, ‚ÄúU aukmo mbop, u Romna ramoot ki?‚ÄĚ Ri, ma rutica aindopatna, ‚ÄúOre, aku annan.‚ÄĚ  
\v 28 Ri, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniaca aindopatna, ‚ÄúAku kituknduk aniac mbuŇč Ňčgoikca aku Romna ramoot ndarurina.‚ÄĚ Na Pola manmo rutica gaindoprina, ‚ÄúAku wanaiŇč, aukna aemmapa aetta maniŇča Romna meacapa ramoot, aintik auk toco Romna ramoot ian.‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 \x - \xo 22:29 \xt Up 16.38\x*Ainda moatke, an mana pina moatna ramta…®ra tawi Ňčgoinna manmo kacrepca w…®Ňčga aŇčg…®ca taŇčga mamaiat. Pola ndomo Romna ramoot ndopatke, an ramoot paŇčan toca rugut mamoat, ma aind ndamŇčirina, ma ndo ramta…®rmo mbopca mina Polmo lawirta Ňčgat…®k mbuŇča maleacat. 
\s1 Pola Iudananta ninik waŇčgorta outta t…®kca kamb ndopatna 
\p  
\v 30 Ri, iŇčmbaina ra, an lapocna ramoot paŇčan aniaca ma an reikca Pola morinanna wati garacna moca, ma kaia moca an Iudana meikramta…®ra manmo ipuŇčgatna. Aintik ma mina taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindapa, ninik waŇčgormo mbopca mina k…®pca puniri, ma Polmo wattacarica ma taŇčga mina out maw…®t…®kat. 
\c 23  
\m  
\v 1 \x - \xo 23:1 \xt Up 24.16, na 1 Ko 4.4, na 2 Ko 1.12, na 2 Ti 1.3\x*Karica Pola an Iudana ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®r paŇčaindmo, wandoŇč Ňčgoinna watta gagraca minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúLaiplacar memetmbaca aku RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®ac Ňčgoutta taŇčrenan, aku mba katta taŇčrenanna. Aukna nikinik iroa wandoŇč laŇč niŇčgik ndeaca, k…®pca mandeacna m…®n.‚ÄĚ  
\v 2 \x - \xo 23:2 \xt 1 GRP 22.24, na Ier 20.2, na In 18.22-23\x*Na ma aindopatke, taup ndamoot paŇčan aniac Ananaiasa, Polna k…®t…®mma w…®t…®kca eacrena ramta…®rmo mbopca, mina ianna Polna kapg…®nmo maapat.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt TN 19.35, na TW 25.1-2, na Mt 23.27-28, na In 7.51\x*Ainda moatke, Pola manmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúRaraŇč Aetaniaca una kapg…®n motocmo apnande. U an wuoca boboroca eacrenanna, mina pai gogok mbuŇča paica eacrena kirar! Na an meikramta…®ra an reik Ňčgorikca mana kaŇčgauk ndeacrenanna mba watitndai. U ndomo T…®p Wand…®kca raŇčgairena ramoot ndopca u anna mbiraca aukmo ritri waparaca morinanna, anna wanaiŇč Ňčgoin, u ndona an T…®p Wand…®kca mba raŇčgairenanna, na u mimo mbopca mina aukmo pirina.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 4 Ri, Polna k…®t…®mma w…®t…®kca eacrenanna, an kamma waraca mina mamo gaind madigiat, ‚ÄúU RaraŇč Aetaniacna taup ndamoot paŇčan aniacmo u pepereapekna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 \x - \xo 23:5 \xt NA 22.28\x*Karica ma minmo rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúLaiplacar, aku ainda lamŇči Ňčgocor, gan ramootta ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna taup ndamoot paŇčan aniac. Na RaraŇč Aetaniacna timbigta kapca aindoprina, ‚ÄėNe ndorita ramta…®r paŇčanmo kam Ňčgoreaca kai mbop teac.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 23:6 \xt Up 4.2, na 24.15, na 24.21, na 26.5, na Pil 3.5\x*Ri, ma wattatnanna, an tumbunna inik ndeacrenanna, anna Parisina tumbunnanapa Sadisinanda tumbun ndeacrena, aintik ma kam aniaca keca, kam gargar mbuŇča ninik waŇčgormo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAukna laiplacar! Aku Parisina ramoot ian, na auk toco Parisina nuoc ian. Na aku r…®pacrenanna menacrina meikramta…®ra mac nda Ňčgepnande, na an reacna moca aku ganna w…®t…®kca eacrena.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 7 Karica ma aindopatke, Parisinandapa Sadisinanda mina maipuŇčgat. Aintik mina tumbunniŇč matitacat.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 23:8 \xt Mt 22.23, na Mk 12.18, na Lk 20.27\x*Na Sadisinanda mina gaindoprena, meikramta…®ra menacrinanna mba mac Ňčgepitndai, na mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčerŇčgaurapa ŇčerŇčgaur kocor. Na Parisinanda mina an reik mbonkaca r…®paca aindoprena, mina eacrenan.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 23:9 \xt Up 5.39, na 22.7, na 22.17-18, na 25.25\x*Ainda mori, mina kam aniaca keca mambopri. Na t…®pemb wandik tamŇčirena ramta…®r ndeida Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAia man morina reac ianna mba watri, Ňčarikca ŇčeroŇč ian, co, mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇč ianna manmo kamb neaŇčga ma mbop te, anna laŇč.‚ÄĚ Na an ramta…®ra mina Parisina tumbunnan.  
\v 10 Karica an iptipuŇča maica uriraca runduŇč ndaruna moatke, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniaca mananambiat, moca Iudana ramta…®ra Polmo t…®pniŇča w…®Ňči titac nari. Ainda moca ma ndona ruŇčrena ramta…®rmo, mandaca mbopca mina irikca mamo aŇčg…®a iukaica mamo mina ndorita eacrina kac inikca t…®katna. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 23:11 \xt Up 18.9, na 19.21, na 25.11, na 27.23-24, na 28.16-23\x*Ri, an mouŇča Kacootta k…®pca mana k…®t…®mma w…®t…®kca manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU kai nanambi teac, u w…®t…®k gagraca eac. Na u Ierusalemmo aukna kamma gagraca wiwitirina, na an kirar toco u Rom motocmo u ainda wiwitinande.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Iudananda Polmo mo menacna kam leacrina 
\p  
\v 12 Karica kabena ŇčaŇčarmuŇča Iudana ramta…®ra Polmo mo menacna kamb maleacat. Na mina RaraŇč Aetaniacmo kam gargar leaca aindopatna, ‚ÄúGidik Ňčgoin, mina Polmo mo menacnande. Na mina mamo mo menac, Ňčgocor ndeacrena m…®nna mina amna reac co pukca mba amitndai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 13 Na an kam leacrina ramta…®rta ndunduca 40na m…®nmo tamuŇčmbai.  
\v 14 Karica an ramta…®ra taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindapa ramta…®r paŇčaindmo taŇčga watca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAia kam gargar leaca aindoprina, ‚ÄėAia amna reac emtemma mba amitndai, taŇči aia Polmo mo menacnandet.‚Äô  
\v 15 \x - \xo 23:15 \xt Up 25.3\x*Aintik nenapa ninik waŇčgora kammo neaŇč taŇčca, mamo paruca aindop, ‚ÄėAia Polna kamna m…®n…®Ňč mac waracna moca.‚Äô Te, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniacmo mbopca, ma Polmo aŇčg…®ca nen ndambuŇč Ňčgirik. Na aia lambi eaca mina mamo aŇčg…®ca k…®p te, aia mamo mo menacna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 16 Ainda moatke, Polna mbina nuoca ma an kamma waracri, ma taŇčga lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rta kaca mbukca Polmo watca manmo mina mboprina kambmo, ma mamo an mambopat.  
\v 17 Karica Pola lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan teker ianmo aca k…®pca mamo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúGan nuoc Ňčgammo lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniac ndambuŇč naaŇčg…®ca taŇč, ma manap mbopna kammap.‚ÄĚ  
\v 18 Ri, an ramoot paŇčan tekera mamo aŇčg…®ca ndona ramoot paŇčan aniac ndambuŇč naaŇčg…®ca mataŇčgat. Na ma mamo gaindoprina, ‚ÄúKac Ňčgoreac ndeacrena ramoot Pol, ma aukmo aca taŇčga aukmo gan nuocmo un ndambuŇč naaŇčg…® k…®pna ndopca. Na ma unap mbopna kammap.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 19 Aintik an ramoot paŇčan aniaca mana par ŇčgutiŇčga mamo aŇčg…®ca roumbmbaia taŇčga mamo madigiat, ‚ÄúU aukmo kaina kam ndopna morena?‚ÄĚ  
\v 20 Ri, an nuoca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúIudana ramta…®ra kam leaca umo, Pol aŇčg…®ca ninik waŇčgor tambuŇč Ňčgirikna. Te, mina umo paruca aindopnande, mina Polna morina reikta m…®n…®Ňčna Ňčgorena.  
\v 21 Na u mina kamma kai warac teac, mina ndeida kam gargar leaca mina Polmo mo menacna, na mina amna reac, co, pukca mba amitndait, taŇči mina Polmo mo menacnande. Na mandeaca mina iŇčgoroca, taup malambireke, ma k…®p te, mina mamo mo menacnandet. Na mina ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 40na m…®nmo tamuŇčmbai, na mandeaca mina una kam laŇčna ndabia eacrena.‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 Karica an ramoot paŇčanna an nuocmo mandaca mataŇčri, na ma mamo kam gargar mbuŇča gaindopatna, ‚ÄúRamoot ianmo, u aukmo mboprina kambca, kai mbop teac Ňčgoin?‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Polmo mina mandaca ma Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliks ndambuŇča taŇčgatna 
\p  
\v 23 Ri, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniaca ndona ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan tekerniŇčmo, aca k…®pca maniŇčmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúOŇčgo lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rta tumbunna 200na m…®n aŇčg…® kocro, na 70na m…®nna os mbuŇča taŇčrenan, na 200na m…®nna lapoc niŇčgik mbuŇča ruŇčrenanmo aŇčg…®ca kocroca, mouŇča ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a parmbaiapa mbutremb paurna m…®nna t…®k te, ne Sisaria taŇčnande.  
\v 24 Na ne Polna ossar motoco aŇčg…®ca kocro, na ne mamo matau Ňčgoinna bubuoci taŇčca Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliksna para t…®k.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Ri, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan aniaca timbiŇč raparmo gaind matirat, 
\b  
\mi  
\v 26 ‚ÄúRa laŇč, aku Kolodius Lisiasa umo gan timbiŇč rapar tirca umo Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliksmo neaŇčga mak…®pek.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 23:27 \xt Up 21.30-33, na 22.25-27, na 24.7\x*IudanaŇčgepca gan ramootmo utiŇčga mamo mo menacna mori, na aku waraca, aukapa lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra aia taŇčga mina r…®kca t…®kca mamo aŇčg…®rina. Na aku waracrinanna, ma RomnaŇčgepta ramoot ian.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 23:28 \xt Up 22.30\x*Ri, aku an mina manap ipuŇčga mboprina m…®n…®Ňčna moca, aku mamo aŇčg…®ca mina ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®r tambuŇč naaŇčg…® taŇčga,  
\v 29 \x - \xo 23:29 \xt Up 18.14-15, na 25.19, na 26.31\x*aku minmo madigiat, ri, mina aukmo gaindoprina, ma mina Iudana t…®pemb wandikca mba raŇčgairi, aintik mina mamo ipuŇčrina. Na aia watri, ma reac ianna mba mori, aintik mina mamo utiŇčga kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kna towanaiŇč, co mamo mo menacna towanaiŇč.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 23:30 \xt Up 23.20, na 24.5-8\x*Ainda moca aku mandeac waracrinanna, mina kam leaca gan ramootmo mo menacna mori tik, aku tawi Ňčgoinna mamo un ndambuŇča mandaca ma k…®prina. Ri, aku manap ipuŇčrina ramta…®rmo mbopca mina un ndambuŇč nak…®pi watca, an reac wandoŇčaina. Te, u an reacna moca ritri waparaca moca u garacnande.‚ÄĚ 
\b  
\p  
\v 31 Karica an ruŇčrena ramta…®ra mina ramoot paŇčanna kamma waraca mina Polmo aŇčg…®ca an mouŇča Antipatiris auŇč mataŇčgat.  
\v 32 Ri, iŇčmbaina ra, an ossar puŇčga taŇčrina ramta…®ra Polap Sisaria auŇč aniaca taŇčri, na or mbuŇča taŇčrina lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra mina Ierusalem mac nda mataŇčgat.  
\v 33 Karica an ossar puŇčga taŇčrina lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra taŇčga Sisaria auŇč aniac ndaruca mina Polmo aŇčg…®ca taŇčga Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliksna out maw…®t…®kat, na mina manmo an timbiŇč rapar maneaŇčgat.  
\v 34 Ri, an Iudiana ramoot paŇčanna timbiŇč rapara watca, ma Polmo gaind madigiat, ‚ÄúU tenmbai waŇčna pitrikna ramoot?‚ÄĚ Na ma rutica aindoprina, ‚ÄúAku Silisianan.‚ÄĚ  
\v 35 Ainda moca an ramoot paŇčanna mamo gaindoprina, ‚ÄúAn unap ipuŇčrena ramta…®ra k…®p te, aku una makukna kamma waracnande.‚ÄĚ Ri, ma minmo mbopca mina Polmo gagrirta ramoot paŇčan aniac Erot moatna kac naaŇčg…®a taŇčca an mat…®kat. 
\c 24  
\s1 Peliksa Polna kambca ritri waparac mamoat 
\p  
\v 1 Karica rai parmbaia maiatke, taup ndamoot paŇčan aniac Ananaiasa Sisaria auŇč aniac mairikat, na Iudana ramta…®r paŇčaind aniac ndeidapa Romna t…®pemb wandik tamŇčirena ramoot ianap, mana ia Tetulas mitoca manap mairikat. Mina Polmo an Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliksna outta t…®kca kam ndop te, mamo anna t…®kca ritri waparaca mona.  
\v 2 Ri, an ramoot paŇčanna Polmo aca k…®patke, Tetulasa Ňčgepca mamo kamb, kamma t…®kca ipuŇčga gaind mambopri, ‚ÄúRamoot paŇčan Peliks, una iro laŇč mbuŇča, aia mbibirac laŇč ndeacri, runduik kocor, na u Ňčgaua aina pitrik waŇča makukapnanmo u moca wandoŇčairina.  
\v 3 Na kainta reikca, ten ndiŇč ndaru te, aia an reikca watca, memetmbaca aina iroara toŇčtoŇč Ňčgoin, na aia umo kam laŇč Ňčgoin neaŇčrena. 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄúAinda moca aku toŇčgorinan, aia una aiŇča mona k…®dr…®kca rocotta mba utiŇčitndai, u aina kam motemmo warac.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 24:5 \xt Up 6.13, na 16.20, na 17.6, na 21.28, na 1 Pi 2.12, na 2.15\x*Aia gan ramootmo watrenanna, ma aina mbibiracapa aimo makukar anikca morenan. Ma Iudanandmo mina r…®kca t…®kca runduikapa, makukara gan tiacarpaikca morena ramoot. Na ma gan mina acrena tumbun Nasaretna ramoot paŇčan.  
\v 6-8 \x - \xo 24:6-8 \xt Up 21.28-30\x*Ri, Pola ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacmo ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®acmo moca ma rat Ňčgocor, na t…®pemb Ňčgorik toco ma morenan, aintik aia mamo mautiŇčri.\f + \fr 24:6-8 \ft LandamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida gaind ndamŇčirena, kabena kam t…®p toco maeacreke. Na Tetulasa gaindoprena, \fq ‚ÄúAia manmo aina ritri waparaca mo ndopna mori. Na lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan Lisiasapa mana lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra k…®pca aimo ndada ndiaŇčca manmo aina para t…®kca aŇčg…®atna. Ri, Lisiasa aindopatna, ‚ÄėMandaia Polmo ritri waparaca t…®kna mo te, ma un Peliks ndambuŇč ndaruca u mana ritri waparaca monandet.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\f* Aintik u ndo mamo matau digi te, u mana morina reaca u aŇčg…®nande, ma kaia moca aia mamo ritri waparaca mona naaŇčg…®ca k…®prina.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 9 Ri, IudanaŇčgepca Tetulasmo, otaca muruŇča kekelamun keca gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAn kambca anna gidik Ňčgoin.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola ndona makukna mbaborpaikca mona moca kambca Peliksmo mambopat 
\p  
\v 10 Karica Iudiana ramoot paŇčan aniaca Polmo kam ndopna moca ndona par mbuŇča naŇčgagoatna, mbatca Pola Ňčgepca gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúAku lamŇčirena u ritri waparaca, gan pitrik waŇčmo guiar w…®t Ňčgoinna bubuocrina, na aku ndona makukna mbaborpaikmo una outta t…®kna toŇčtoŇčap.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 24:11 \xt Up 21.17, na 21.26, na 24.17\x*Na u mimo digi te, mina unmo mbopnande, aku mbendeina moca Ierusalemmo, raia parniŇčapa mbut mbuniŇča taŇčgatke.  
\v 12 Na gan aukap ipuŇčrena ramta…®ra mina aukmo watrina, aku meacramoot ianap RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca mba ipuŇčri, na Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kacmo meikramta…®r aŇčg…® punirena, co gan auŇč aniacna inikca mimo aŇčg…®ca punirena, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.  
\v 13 Ainda moca mina aukap ritri waparaca morena kamma, ma gagaimb kocor, an kambca mina una outta t…®kca mboprenanna, anna gidikca wanaiŇč. 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 24:14 \xt Up 24.5, na 26.22, na 28.23, na 2 Ti 1.3\x*‚ÄúNa kam gidikca gaind, ‚ÄėAku aina nicar Ňčgamrirta mbendeirena RaraŇč Aetaniacna t…®pca raŇčgairena, na Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgairenan toco aku anna raŇčgairena.‚Äô Anmo mina aindoprina, ‚ÄėAnna paparuna taup.‚Äô Na aku an T…®p Wand…®kna timbigta kapca tirca eacrenanapa, rambca morina ramta…®rta timbigta kapca tirca eacrena kambca auk toco anna r…®pacrena.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 24:15 \xt Dan 12.2, na In 5.28-29, na Up 23.6, na 26.6-7, na 28.20\x*Aintik aku RaraŇč Aetaniacmo r…®paca lambica eacrena ma an menacrina meikramta…®r wandoikapa, Ňčgorikmo mac mo Ňčgepnande. An ramta…®ra r…®pacrena kirara aku ainda r…®pacrina.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 24:16 \xt Up 23.1\x*Ainda moca aku memetmbaca ndona nikinikna iromo moi gagarca ramoot wandoŇč ndeacna, te, RaraŇč Aetaniacapa meikramta…®rta lamn…®ac Ňčgoutmo t…®p Ňčgoreaca kai mo teac.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 24:17 \xt Up 11.29-30, na 20.16, na Ro 15.25-26, na 2 Ko 8.4, na Gal 2.10\x*\x - \xo 24:17 \xt Up 21.17-28\x*Ri, ma mac gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAku Ierusalemmo t…®kcarica taŇčga kabena pitrik waŇčmo guiar ndepik ndeaca. Na iŇčmbai aku mac nda taŇčca ndona pitrik waŇčnan tambuŇč ndaru te, aku an reik Ňčgocorta meikramta…®rapa, meikramta…®rmo reik matpia eacrenanmo, opotacna kitukndukap aŇčg…®ca taŇčca neaŇč te, aku g…®mbamba mona.  
\v 18 Na mina aukmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca wattatnanna, aku ndona tikmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna lamn…®acmo wandoŇč ratta morina. Na anna inikca meikramta…®rta tumbunna eac Ňčgocor, na kamb anik kocor.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 24:19 \xt Up 23.30, na 25.16, na 2 Ti 1.15\x*Ri, Iudana ramta…®r ndeida Esiana pitrik ndeacrenanna, mina ndori k…®pca aukmo utiŇčrina, na an ramta…®ra aukmo kammap te, mina ndori gan nak…®pca una outta t…®kca aukmo ritri waparaca mo.  
\v 20 Na wanaiŇč te, gan ramta…®rmo digi, mina aukna morina makuk ianna wat te, unmo mbop. Mina ninik waŇčgorta ramta…®ra Ierusalemma t…®kca, aku minmo kambca mboprina,  
\v 21 \x - \xo 24:21 \xt Up 23.6, na 28.20\x*na aku mina out naŇčgepca w…®t…®kca mboprina kamma gaind, ‚ÄėAku r…®pacrinanna, menacrina meikramta…®ra mac nda Ňčgepnande.‚Äô Aintik mandeaca mina aukmo nen ndambuŇč, naaŇčg…® k…®pca, ritri waparaca mona.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 22 \x - \xo 24:22 \xt Up 23.26\x*Na Peliksa an Kacoot Iesusna Taupa raŇčgairena meikramta…®rta r…®t…®paikapa t…®pemb kirarirmo, ma mataua lamŇčirena. Karica ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúLapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan Lisiasa irik te, aku nena kamma wandoŇčainande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 23 \x - \xo 24:23 \xt Up 27.3, na 28.16, na 28.30\x*Karica ma lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan tekermo aindopatna, ‚ÄúU manmo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®kca, mamo aiŇčira gagrara kai neaŇč teac, na mana kamkabemo wattacarica mina mana toŇčtoŇčna reikmo mamo otac.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Peliksa Polmo gui mbuniŇča kac Ňčgoreaca t…®katna 
\p  
\v 24 Karica rai ndeida maiatna mbatca Iudiana ramoot paŇčan Peliksapa mana meac Darusila mak…®pat. Na Darusila ma Iudananta meac, maniŇča k…®pca mbiraca Polmo aca ma k…®pca maniŇčmo Karais Iesusa r…®pacna kamb ndopri, maniŇča mawaracri.  
\v 25 Ainda moca Pola maniŇčmo, t…®p kirar wandoŇč laŇčapa, meacramoota ndona iroapa tikmo matau watna kam ndoprina, na RaraŇč Aetaniacna k…®k…®pna ra, ma aimo ritri waparaca mona kam ndopatke, ramoot paŇčan Peliksa mananambiat. Ri, ma Polmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúLaŇč, u pac taŇč, oit ianna ra ecte, aku unmo mac acnande.‚ÄĚ  
\v 26 Karica an k…®dr…®k mbuŇča Peliks ma iro ianap, na mana iroa ma Polmo ndomo kitukndukeniŇč neaŇčna r…®t…®pacap. Ainda moca an k…®dr…®kar w…®tta, ma manmo memetmbaca aca k…®pca manap mboprena. 
\p  
\v 27 \x - \xo 24:27 \xt Up 25.9, na 25.14\x*Ainda moca taŇčga gui mbuniŇč maiatna mbatca, Posias Pestasa, Peliksna aiŇč aŇčg…®ca ramoot paŇčan ndaruatna mbatca, Peliksa Iudana meikramta…®rmo mamo toŇčgona moca ma Polmo wattacarica ma kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrina. 
\c 25  
\s1 Pola aindoprina, Sisa ndo mana makukna kamma waracnandet 
\p  
\v 1 Karica Pestasa k…®pca Iudiana pitrik ndaruca rai mbonkac maiatna mbatca, ma Sisaria ŇčgedacndiŇča Ierusalem magat.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 25:2 \xt Up 24.1, na 25.15\x*Ri, taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindapa Iudana outmbaica taŇčrina ramta…®r paŇčainda man ndambuŇč mak…®pat. Ri, Pestasna outta t…®kca, mina Polmo kamb puŇčga ipuŇčga mbopri, na mina mamo aemaŇčmaŇčap gaindoprina,  
\v 3 \x - \xo 25:3 \xt Up 23.12, na 23.15\x*‚ÄúU aimo otaca Polmo mandaca ma Ierusalem nak…®p.‚ÄĚ Mina aindoprinanna an k…®dr…®kca, mina ramta…®r ndeidmo mbopca, mina taŇčga taup ŇčgiŇčgoroca lambi te, Polmo anna t…®kca mo menacna.  
\v 4 Ri, Pestasa mina kam rutica, gaindoprina, ‚ÄúPola ma Sisariana kac Ňčgoreac maeacreke. Na rocotta wanaiŇč, aku anna taŇčnande.  
\v 5 Aintik nena ramta…®r paŇčainda aukap Sisaria auŇč Ňčgirik, te, an ramootta ma t…®p ianna mo Ňčgocrai te, mina anna t…®kca mana kammo ritri waparaca mona.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 6 Karica Pestasa minap rai mbutremb mbonkac, co, parniŇčna m…®n toca ma minap eaca, iŇčmbaia ma Sisaria auŇč mairikat. Na kabena ra, ma ritri waparacna mbibiracna taupca mbiraca, mimo Pol aŇčg…®ca mina outta t…®kna anna kam ndoprinan.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 25:7 \xt Up 24.5-6, na 24.13\x*Ainda moca, mina mamo aŇčg…®a k…®patke, an Iudananda Ierusalem ndiŇč nak…®prinanna mamo w…®t…®kca paria aŇčg…®ca kekelamun mairikat. Mina mamo kamb gagrar puŇčga ipuŇčga mambopri, na mina mboprina kambca ramoot paŇčan Pestasmo m…®niŇč kocor.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 25:8 \xt Up 24.12, na 28.17\x*Ri, mina Polmo kekelamun keca maiatke, ma mina kammo wandoŇča gainda rutica mambopat, ‚ÄúAku Iudananta t…®p wand…®k ianna mo Ňčgocrai Ňčgocor, na RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna reac ianna mba mo Ňčgocrairi, na gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Sisamo reac ianna mba mori, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 25:9 \xt Up 24.27, na 25.20\x*Karica ramoot paŇčan Pestasa Iudana ramta…®rmo moi iroar inkar wewettana moca, ma Polmo madigiat, ‚ÄúU Ierusalemma taŇčca aku una kammo anna t…®kca aku unanmo ritri waparac mona toŇčgori ki? Na anna laŇč ecte, aku una makukca anna t…®kca waracna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 10 Ri, ma gaindopatna, ‚ÄúGan taupca mandeac aku w…®t…®kca eacrenanna, anna Sisana ritri waparacna mbibiracna taup, na an taup niŇčgikca aku ndona ritri waparacna kamma anna t…®kca monande. Na u ndo Ňčgoinna mataua lamŇčirina, aku Iudananta reac ianna mba moa Ňčgocrairi.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 25:11 \xt Up 23.11, na 23.29, na 25.25, na 26.31-32, na 28.19\x*Na Ňčgaua aku reac aniac ianna moi Ňčgocrai te, aku anna menacna m…®n. Na an kamma mina aukmo anna ritri waparaca morenanna, anna gidikca wanaiŇč ecte, ramoot ianna aukmo mina para t…®kna towanaiŇč. Anna moca aku toŇčgorinanna, gag…®rirta ramoot paŇčan aniac Sisa ndo aukna makukca waracna.‚ÄĚ  
\v 12 Karica Pestasa, ndona landamŇči Ňčgotacrina ramta…®rap mbopca maica, na Polmo gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúU toŇčgorinanna Sisa ma una makukna kamma waracna. LaŇč! U man ndambuŇča taŇčnande.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pestasa gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripamo Polna kam ndopatna 
\p  
\v 13 Ainda moca rai ndeida taŇčga mairi, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripaapa mana mbi Benaisi, maniŇča Pestasmo oke watna moca Sisaria auŇč aniac mataŇčgat. Na maniŇča mamo kam laŇč neaŇčna, na t…®p kirar laŇča wandacna moca.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 25:14 \xt Up 24.27\x*Karica maniŇča an ndeaca rai w…®t mamoat, ri, Pestasa gagrirta ramoot paŇčanmo, Polna kam maniniat, na ma gaindoprina, ‚ÄúŇägaua Peliksa ramoot ianmo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®krinanna, ma an maeacreke.  
\v 15 Na aku Ierusalemma taŇčga eacri, Iudana outmbaica taŇčrina taup ndamta…®r paŇčaindapa mina ramta…®r paŇčainda, manmo kekelamun keca maipuŇčgat. Na mina toŇčgorinanna, aku gaindopna, ‚ÄėMa makukap, te, manmo lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rta para t…®kca mina manmo mo Ňčgocraina.‚Äô  
\v 16 Ri, aku mina kam rutica minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAia Romnanda, aia ramootmo makukca wanaiŇča neaŇčna, t…®pemb kirarir kocor. Na ramootta makukapnanna, ma ndoap kekelamun kerina ramta…®rap mina ritri waparacna ramta…®r tambuŇča taŇčca, ma anna w…®t…®kca minap mbop te. Ritri waparacna ramta…®ra mamo ruti mbopna k…®dr…®k neaŇč te, ma minap moatna reikta kammo nda ruti mbopnande.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúAinda moca mina aukap Sisaria nak…®pri, aku min nake mba lambiri. IŇčmbaina ra Ňčgoinna aku taŇčga ritri waparacna taupca mbukca mbiracri, minmo an ramoot aŇčg…®ca k…®pna kam mambopat.  
\v 18 Ri, manmo kekelamun kerena ramta…®r toca Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca manap maipuŇčgat. Na aku gaind ndamŇčica, ‚ÄėMina mamo reac Ňčgoreac ianna morina kam ndopit ki?‚Äô Na wanaiŇč!  
\v 19 \x - \xo 25:19 \xt Up 18.15, na 23.29\x*Mina Ňčgepca mamo ndorita Iudananta r…®t…®pacna t…®pna moca manap maipuŇčgat, an menacatna ramoot ian, mana ia Iesus. Na Pola aindoprena, an ramootta ma mba menacri.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 25:20 \xt Up 25.9\x*Na aku an kamna m…®n…®Ňčna Ňčgore laruna mori, aukna iroa lamŇčia paurica, aku lamŇči garacna toawanaiŇč. Karica aku mamo madigiat, ‚ÄėU Ierusalemma taŇčna toŇčtoŇčap ki, te, aku una kammo anna t…®kca waracna ki?‚Äô  
\v 21 Ainda digiatke, ma aindopatna, ma kac Ňčgoreac ndeaci taŇčga iŇčmbaia Sisa ndo mana makukna ritri waparaca monande. Na aku mamo gaindoprina, ‚ÄėU kac Ňčgoreac ndeaca taŇčca aku taup ianna wat te, unmo Sisa ndambuŇča mbag…®rica taŇčnande.‚Äô‚ÄĚ  
\v 22 Karica an gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa an kambca waraca maica, ma Ňčgepca Pestasmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAuk toco, an ramootna kambmo ndo Ňčgoin mbuŇča waracna toŇčtoŇčap.‚ÄĚ Ri, Pestasa manmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúŇäorap te, u waracnande.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 25:23 \xt Mt 10.18, na Mk 13.9\x*Ri, iŇčmbaina ra, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripaapa Benaisi, maniŇča lamboi laiŇč aoca k…®pca mina tumbunna punirena kac mambukat. Na lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®r paŇčaind anikapa an auŇčna ramta…®r paŇčaind toco k…®prina, ri, Pestasa mbopca mina Polmo aŇčg…®ca mak…®pat.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 25:24 \xt Up 25.2-3, na 25.7, na 22.22\x*Karica Pestasa Ňčgepca gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúGagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripaapa, ne muruŇča mandaibinna mandeaca aiap gan ndeacrenan, ne gan ramootmo wat, Iudana meikramta…®r muruŇčapa Ierusalemnandapa gannan toco, mina gan ramootmo kekelamun irikca, mamo ipuŇčrena. Mina aukmo gaindopca gagrarina, ‚ÄėU manmo mo menac, na ma kai eac teac.‚Äô  
\v 25 Ainda moca aku ndo watrinanna, ma makuk ianna mba mori, na ma anna menacna toawanaiŇč. Na ma toŇčgorinanna, Sisa ndo mana makukca waracna, aintik aku kam leaca mamo Romma mbag…®rica ma taŇčnande.  
\v 26 Na aku aina gagrirta ramoot paŇčan aniacmo kaina kam tirca neaŇč taŇčnanna, aku mba lamŇčireke, te, ma lamŇčinandet, kaina moca mina gan ramootmo ritri waparaca morina. Aintik gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa, aku unapa ganna muruŇč ndeacrena ramta…®rmo gan ramootmo aŇčg…®ca nen ndambuŇč naaŇčg…®ca k…®p te, aia mana kammo matau waracna, na aku tir ndoprina kammo lamŇčica, timbiŇč rapara t…®kna.  
\v 27 Ainda moca aku kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrena ramoot ianmo mandac taŇč te, na kaina reaca ma moca mina mamo ritri waparaca morina, an kamma wandoŇča neaŇč Ňčgocor ndacari te, aku aind ndamŇčinande anna t…®p kirar laŇča wanaiŇč.‚ÄĚ 
\c 26  
\s1 Gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa ma Polna kamma waracatna 
\p  
\v 1 Karica gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa Ňčgepca Polmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúLaŇč u ndona ritri waparacna kamb top.‚ÄĚ Aindopatna mbatca, Pola Ňčgepca ndona parniŇč aŇčg…®a Ňčgepca Ňčgagoca minmo ndoa waracna moca.  
\v 2 Ri, ma aindopatna, ‚ÄúLaŇč gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa, aku aind ndamŇčirina anna laŇč Ňčgoin, aku gan kammo mandeaca una outta t…®ki mbop waracnandet. Aku an Iudana ramta…®ra aukap ipuŇčga mboprina kamb rutina moca.‚ÄĚ  
\v 3 Karica ma gaind mac mboprina, ‚ÄúU aina Iudana t…®pemb kirarira u matau Ňčgoin ndamŇčirena, titocna reikca aia ipuŇčga mboprena. Aintik aku toŇčgorenanna, u laŇčanna mbiraca auk mbopekna kambca waracna.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 4 Ri, Pola gaindopatna, ‚ÄúIudana meikramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇča aukmo lamŇčirena, titocna kirara aku eacrinan, an Ňčgaua aku mooŇčnuoc tekera ndona pitrik waŇč ndeaca taŇčga, iŇčmbaia aku Ierusalem nak…®pca an ndeacrina.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 26:5 \xt Up 22.3, na 23.6, na 24.15, na 24.21, na Pil 3.5\x*Na mina atuna aukmo lamŇčirina. Ainda moca mina toŇčgo te, an kambca umo ndori mbopna laŇč, na mina lamŇčirena aku ramoot Ňčgam ndeacrina m…®nna aku Parisina tumbunna ramoot ian. Na aku T…®p Wand…®k toco raŇčgairena, na Parisinanda mina t…®pemb kirarira raŇčgaina owai Ňčgoin, ainda moca aina Iudana kabena tumbunnanda, mina Parisina t…®pemb kirarir gagrarta kirarirta toawanaiŇč.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 26:6 \xt TW 18.5, na Ňäap 132.11, na Ais 7.14, na Dan 9.24, na Up 23.6, na 28.20\x*Aintik mandeaca aku ganna w…®t…®kca mina aukmo ritri waparaca morinanna, mana m…®n…®Ňča gaind, aku RaraŇč Aetaniaca r…®paca lambirena ma atua aina nicar Ňčgamrirmo, babu mbopatna reaca ma mo larunande.  
\v 7 Na aina barna tumnamb parniŇčapa mbut mbuniŇča mina RaraŇč Aetaniacmo muruŇča mouŇčapa ra manmo mbendeirena. Na mina r…®t…®paik anik koindap tik, mina an reac niŇčgikna ndabirena. Ainda moca gagrirta ramoot paŇčan, auk toco r…®paca an reacna ndabirena. Na anna m…®n…®Ňčna moca Iudananda aukmo ipuŇčga kekelamun irikrena.  
\v 8 Na kaina moca ne ramta…®r ndeida RaraŇč Aetaniacmo menacrina meikramta…®rmo mac aŇčg…® ŇčgeŇčgepca r…®pac Ňčgocor.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 9 \x - \xo 26:9 \xt 1 Ti 1.13\x*\x - \xo 26:9 \xt Up 8.3, na 22.4-5\x*Karica ma gaind mac mboprina, ‚ÄúŇägaua aku ndo Ňčgoinna gaind ndamŇčirena aku reac w…®t aniaca mo te, aku Nasaretna Iesusna imo mo Ňčgocraica p…®k…®nna t…®knande.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 26:10 \xt Up 9.14, na 9.21, na Gal 1.13\x*Ri, aku an reikmo Ierusalemma t…®kca moatnanna, anna taup ndamta…®r paŇčainda aukmo kam laŇčapa gargar neaŇčga aku an RaraŇč Aetaniacna meikramta…®rmo muoca kac Ňčgoreaca t…®krina, na mina moi menacna kam leac te, auk toco mina mo menacna kam laŇč ndopnande.  
\v 11 Na memetmbaca aku Iudananta mimitpac aŇčg…®rena kaikca mbukca minmo piri, mimo Iesusmo iŇč neaŇčna towaia gagara mbopri, minmo mbopca mamo peperena kam Ňčgoreac ndopna. Na aku nikkatca Ňčgepca mimo mon kabena auŇčembca taŇčga eacrinanmo, raŇčgaica taŇčca ore aŇčg…®ca minmo moa Ňčgocrairena.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola Iesusmo r…®pacatna ninini mamoat 
\r (Up AŇčg…®rena Ramta…®rta AiŇč 9.3-19 na 22.6-16) 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 26:12 \xt Up 9.3, na 22.6\x*Karica ma gaind mac mambopat, ‚ÄúAnna taup ndamta…®r paŇčainda aukmo kam wandoŇč laŇčapa gargar neaŇčga aukmo Damaskusa taŇčna mbag…®riatke, aku mataŇčgat.  
\v 13 Na gagrirta ramoot paŇčan aku umo aindopnande, aia taŇčga taupca t…®kca ra taŇčga r…®kniŇčna m…®nna t…®katke, aku wattatnanna memetac aniac ianna an tamuŇčna auŇč ŇčgedacndiŇča metacatna memetaca rana memetacmo kundacarica. Na mana memetaca aukapa, aukap taŇčrina ramta…®r tambatta, metaca korereca maaŇčg…®at.  
\v 14 Na ainda metacatke, aia muruŇča pitrik Ňčgirikca mameracat, ri, aku waracatnanna, kam ianna aukmo Iburuna kam mbuŇča aukmo gaindoprina, ‚ÄėSol, Sol! U kaina moca aukmo moa Ňčgocrairena? Na u aukap runduŇča anna owai Ňčgoin, na anna umo mba otacitndai.‚Äô\f + \fr 26:14 \ft Na gan kamma ma Timbigta Kapca maeacreke, na gaindoprina, \fq ‚ÄúUna or mbuŇča u reac w…®rw…®r ianmo ke te, u anna g…®rg…®ra aŇčg…®nande.‚ÄĚ\f* 
\v 15 Karica aku an kammo gaind mac nda rutiatna, ‚ÄėKacoot u mandai?‚Äô Ri, ma aukmo rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄėAku Iesus u aukmo moa Ňčgocrairena.‚Äô  
\v 16 \x - \xo 26:16 \xt Up 22.15\x*Ainda moca ma aukmo aindopatna, ‚ÄėU Ňčgepca w…®t…®k. Na mandeaca aku unmo k…®prinanna, u aukna aiŇčna ramootapa kam wiwiti mona ramoot, na aku umo larapacrina. Te, u meikramta…®rmo an u ndo watrina reikapa, an reikmo aku unmo wandaceknan, u mimo mbopnande.‚Äô  
\v 17 \x - \xo 26:17 \xt Up 22.21\x*Na ma aindopatna, ‚ÄėAku unmo Iudana meikramta…®rapa, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanda mba wattacarica, mina unmo mba mo Ňčgocraiitndai, wanaiŇč. Na anna m…®n…®Ňčna moca aku umo mandaca u min ndambuŇča taŇčnande,  
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Ais 35.5, na 42.7, na 42.16, na In 8.12, na Up 20.32, na 2 Ko 6.14, na Epe 2.2, na Kol 1.13\x*te, u mina lamnikca moi p…®arca, mina ndorita t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukarapa neaup t…®kcarica mina nikinik iroara moi wandoŇčaica mina tacna memetac ndaruna. Na mina Ramoot Mb…®kna gargar t…®kcarica RaraŇč Aetaniac ndambuŇč nak…®pna. Na mina t…®pemb Ňčgorikta makukarmo aku mo kecarinande, te, mina an aukmo out Ňčgoinna r…®pacrina meikramta…®ra, aku ndo larapacrina tumbunna inikca mbukna.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola RaraŇč Aetaniacna aiŇča morina kammo Ag…®ripamo mboprina 
\p  
\v 19 Na Pola gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúGagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa, aku an tamuŇčna auŇč ndiŇč nak…®prina reacmo manmb…®anmemraŇčna tamram mbuŇča watca, na aku an kammo raŇčgairena.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 26:20 \xt Mt 3.8, na Up 9.20, na 9.28-29, na 11.26, na 13.14\x*Ainda moca aku Ňčgepca meikramta…®rmo mbopca mina ndorita iroar inkar Ňčgetrikica, RaraŇč Aetaniacna kaŇčgauk ndeacna mo te, minmo kirarir laiŇčga mona. Te, anna ndo wandacna mina maŇčgetrikiri, na aku an kamma Damaskusnandmo outta mbopatna, na iŇčmbaia Ierusalemapa Iudiananapa Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnandmo mboprina.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 26:21 \xt Up 21.30-31\x*Aintik mina aukmo anna m…®n…®Ňčna moca aukmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna Kacna wuocna inikca t…®kca utiŇčga, aukmo mo menacna morina.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 26:22 \xt Lk 24.27, na 24.44, na In 5.46, na Ro 3.21\x*Ainda mori, RaraŇč Aetaniaca aukmo otaca k…®p, k…®pca mandeaca aku ganna w…®t…®kca meikramta…®r tekirapa anikmo, muruŇča aku ndo watrina reikta kamma mboprina. Na aku kam dam ianna mba mbopri, wanaiŇč, aku an atua Mosesapa rambca morina ramta…®ra mbopatna reikta kammo laruna ndopatna.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 26:23 \xt Ais 42.6, na 49.6, na Lk 24.26, na 24.44-47, na 1 Ko 15.20, na Kol 1.18\x*Na mina aindopatna, aimo RaraŇč Aetaniaca babuca mbag…®rica k…®pca aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na ramoot. Na ma g…®rg…®r aniac aŇčg…®ca ma menacnandet, na an menacrina meikramta…®rmo ma outmbai mac Ňčgepnande. Na ma Iudanandapa, Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčnanmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna memetacna tacna kam ndopnande.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Pola Ag…®ripamo r…®pacna kam ndopatna 
\p  
\v 24 Karica Pola an reikta kamb topri mbuŇča, Pestasa Ňčgepca kam bagaraniac mbuŇča gaind mambopat, ‚ÄúPol, u maica maŇčaŇčaoek! Na u kocnaia landamŇčina riptia aŇčg…®ca anna ndo moca u maŇčaŇčaori.‚ÄĚ  
\v 25 Karica Pola rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúRamoot aniac Pestas, aku ŇčaŇčao Ňčgocor, wanaiŇč Ňčgoin. Aku gidik ndoprenan, aku iroap tik, aku mambopreke.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 26:26 \xt In 18.20\x*Na gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa an reikca aku mboprinanna u lamŇčirena, na aku umo wandoŇč Ňčgoinna mbopnande, na aku mba nanambitndai. Na aku lamŇčirena ma an reikta kambca ma waracatnan, na wattatna an reikmo roumb ianna mba t…®kca moatke.‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Karica ma gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripamo madigiat, ‚ÄúU gan rambca morina ramta…®rmo r…®pacre ki, wanaiŇč? Aku lamŇčirena u r…®pacrinan.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28 Ri, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa mamo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU aukmo gaindta k…®dr…®k tekemmotem mbuŇča moi Ňčgetriki naki? Te, aku Karaisna ramoot toc ndaruna toki?‚ÄĚ  
\v 29 Ainda moatke, Pola mamo rutica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúU lamŇčirena k…®dr…®k rocot, co k…®dr…®k mat…®p, unapa gan aku mboprena kambca waracrena meikramta…®ra, aku RaraŇč Aetaniacmo mbendei te, ne auk toc ndarunandet. Na mina gan auk toc ndeacna moca, aku an lawirta Ňčgat…®kmo minap eteaca toŇčgo Ňčgocor.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 30 Aintik gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripaapa ramoot paŇčan Pestasapa, mina ramta…®r paŇčaindapa Benaisiap, an inik ndeacrenanna mina Ňčgepca maw…®t…®kat.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 26:31 \xt Up 23.9, na 23.29, na 25.25\x*Karica mina an kac t…®kcarica mina taŇčri mbuŇča, ndorimo ian, ianna aindoprena, ‚ÄúGan ramootta makukar kocor, na ma kaina m…®n…®Ňčna moca ma menacna, co, mamo kac Ňčgoreaca t…®krina.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 \x - \xo 26:32 \xt Up 25.11\x*Ri, gagrirta ramoot paŇčan Ag…®ripa ramoot paŇčan Pestasmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúMa Sisamo ndona kamb mac ritri waparacna ndopri tik, wanaiŇč co, u mamo watcarica ma taŇčna m…®n, na ma makukar kocor.‚ÄĚ 
\c 27  
\ms1 Pola Romma taŇčna, taŇčrena 
\mr (27‚ÄĒ28) 
\s1 Mina Polmo laŇčgumma t…®kca ma Romma taŇčgatna 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 27:1 \xt Up 25.12, na 25.25\x*Ainda moatke, mina kam leaca aimo laŇčgum aŇčg…®ca Italina pitrikca taŇčna mambopat. Na mina Polapa an kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrena ramta…®r ndeidmo, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčan Iuliesna para t…®katna, ma minmo bubuoca taŇčna. Mana kaŇčgauk ndeacrina lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra 100na m…®n, na mina Sisana lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®r.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 27:2 \xt Up 19.29\x*Ri, aia Adaramitiumna laŇčgum ian naŇčgabukca, ma Esiana pitrikna auŇčembta kamd…®para taŇčna mori t…®k, aia mataŇčgat. Na Aristakas Ňčgacrena ramoot, ma Tesalonika auŇčnan, na an auŇča ma Masedoniana pitrik iniknan, ma toca aiap mataŇčri.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 27:3 \xt Up 24.23\x*Na iŇčmbaina ra, aia taŇčga Saidon auŇč matundocri, na Iuliesa Polmo t…®p laŇč mamoat. Ma Polmo wattacarica ma taŇčca ndona aikormo watca, minmo amna reikapa ndona toŇčgorina reikta digica maaŇčg…®at.  
\v 4 Karica aia Saidon t…®kcarica aia mac lembaia taŇčga Saiprus Ňčgacrena mutmo roumbmbai ndiŇč mataŇčri. Na aia wandoŇča taŇčna towanaiŇč, watta aimo tapacreke.  
\v 5 Ainda moca aia lembaia taŇčga, Silisiaapa Pampiliana macait kataca, taŇčga Maira Ňčgacrena auŇč aniaca ma Lisiana pitrik ndeacrina auŇč magat. 
\p  
\v 6 Karica lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna Aleksandriana laŇčgum ianna watca, na an laŇčgumma ma Italia taŇčna more t…®k, ma aimo an naaŇčg…®a maŇčgabukat.  
\v 7 Karica aia t…®t…®knoca lembaia mataŇčri, aia ainda lembaia taŇč, taŇčga raia w…®t Ňčgoin mamoat. Na an k…®dr…®kca watta aimo ndatapiri, na aia k…®dr…®k owai Ňčgoin maaŇčg…®at. Ri, aia Nidus auŇč teker malaruat, na watta aimo moca aia mac taŇčna toawanaiŇč tik, aia nda uriraca Kirit mut mataŇčgat, na ma Salmonena timup ndeacrena, ri, aia mamo monmbai waŇč mataŇčgat.  
\v 8 Ainda moca laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra aiŇč aniaca moca aia Kiritna maŇčar roumb malembairi. Karica iŇčmbaia aia taup ianna laruca, anmo mina gaind Ňčgacrena Kodur LaŇč, na ma Lasea auŇč tekermo rambuŇčaica eacrena. 
\p  
\v 9 Ri, mina an ndeaca rai w…®t mamoat, na Iudananda amna reacmo wariracna ra toco mataŇčgat. Ri, Pola minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúMacaitta kocnaia Ňčgocraimarica,\f + \fr 27:9 \fk Na Iudananda amna reacmo wariracna ra: \ft An Ra Aniaca RaraŇč Aetaniaca Meikramta…®rta T…®pemb Kirarir Ňägorikta Makukarmo Mo Kecarirena. Na an iarna m…®nna anna Gamai aniaca Mediterenianna macait aniaca Ňčgeprenan, na laŇčguipa mba taŇčrenan.\f* 
\v 10 \x - \xo 27:10 \xt Up 27.22\x*na ramta…®r, ne aukna kamma warac, aku lamŇčirena aia mandeaca taŇč te, aia makukar w…®t Ňčgoinna koacnandet. Gan laŇčgumapa mana inik ndeacrena reikca Ňčgocrainande, na ai toco ndorita tikembca kecarinandet.‚ÄĚ  
\v 11 Aindopatke, lapoca ruŇčrena ramoot paŇčanna, Polna kamma mba waracatke, ma an laŇčgumna tiŇčara morina ramootapa laŇčgumna aetna iro maraŇčgaiat.  
\v 12 Na an kamd…®p toco, laŇč Ňčgoinna wanaiŇč, laŇčgumma ma anmo wat aniacapa macaitmo iŇčgorocna toawanaiŇč. Aintik ramta…®r w…®tta kam leaca mina an kamd…®p t…®kcarica taŇčna. Na mina aind malamŇčiat, mina m…®n te, mina Piniksna kamd…®pa taŇčca anna eaca watna mamaina lambina. Na Piniksa ma Kirit mutmo raŇčmbai ndeacrenanna, na ma toca ra itirikmbaina waŇč maeacrenan. 
\s1 Watapa macait aniaca maŇčgepat 
\p  
\v 13 Ainda moca raŇčmbaina mbunimna watta laŇčanna k…®patke, mina anmo aind malamŇčiat, mina laŇča lembai taŇč te, an mina mboprina kamd…®pa mina taŇčca tundocnande. Aintik mina laŇčgumna keca pukca utiŇčga keraca eacrina reacmo w…®Ňčga gaca, mina Kirit mutna maŇčarmo roumb Ňčgoin malembairi.  
\v 14 Na rocotta wanaiŇč, ra gacgacna wat aniaca ma maŇčgepat, na mana ia Gamai, na ma mutmo waŇčembai ndiŇč mak…®pat.  
\v 15 Ainda mori, an laŇčgumma ma taŇčga an wat gargar aniaca mbukca tapi ootna m…®nna wanaiŇč. Aintik aia towai taŇčna m…®nna wanaiŇč, tik aia wattacarica an watta aimo aŇčg…®ca mataŇčri.  
\v 16 Na aia ootta taŇčga mut teker ianna rambuŇčmbai mataŇčri. Na mana ia Kauda. Na an muta, watmo wawarari, aia aiŇč aniac Ňčgoinna moca, an laŇčgumna kor tekermo w…®Ňčga laŇčgumma Ňčgabukca matau Ňčgoin maleacri.  
\v 17 Karica mina laŇčgumna Ňčga…®r anik aŇčg…®ca, laŇčgummo kaŇčgaukca, keca pukca, an Ňčga…®rpaik mbuŇča mina aŇčg…®ca laŇčgummo leaca magagaracat. Na an ramta…®r toco mina mananambiri, moca mina Apirikana wiwirca macait r…®kca eacrenanna ote ga nari. Aintik mina lembairena embmo p…®arra aŇčg…® mairikat, laŇčgummo watrica ma utia mataŇčri.  
\v 18 Karica kabena ra, an wat aniaca aimo paŇčpaiŇč Ňčgoinna rapacatna mbatca, an laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra laŇčgum inikna reikmo aŇčg…®a pukca kecamacariat.  
\v 19 Na iŇčmbaina ra, ma aind kabe mac eacri, aintik laŇčgum inikna ramta…®ra, laŇčgumna inikna aiŇča mona reik ndeid mac aŇčg…®ca kecamacariat.  
\v 20 Ainda moatke, an wat aniaca maeacri, na rai w…®t aniac Ňčgoinna taŇčgatke, aia raapa guiara mba watri, na aia aind malamŇčiri, aia mba eacitndai, aia menacnande. 
\p  
\v 21 Ri, an laŇčgum ndeacrina ramta…®ra amta reik emtemma mba ambri, mina rai w…®tta am Ňčgocor ndeacri. Ainda moca Pola mina outta Ňčgepca w…®t…®kca minmo gaindopatna, ‚ÄúNe aukna kamma waraca ne mut Kirita t…®kcarica lembai Ňčgocor co, ne gan makukara mba aŇčg…®ca gainda mba moca taŇčraŇč mbe.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 27:22 \xt Up 27.10, na 27.31\x*Aintik aku nemo Ňčgep gaca toŇčgona aindoprena! Na nena ianna mba Ňčgocraiitndai, aia taŇčrena laŇčgumma ma ndo Ňčgocrainande.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 27:23 \xt Dan 6.16, na Up 23.11, na Ro 1.9\x*Na Ňčour mouŇča aku mbendeiri, aku raŇčgairena RaraŇč Aetaniacna, mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča auk ndambuŇč mak…®pat.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 27:24 \xt Up 23.11\x*Ri, an mbaiŇčna aiŇča morena ŇčeroŇča aukmo aindopatna, ‚ÄėU kai nanambi teac, u taŇčca Sisana outta w…®t…®knande, na RaraŇč Aetaniaca unap kam leacrina, na an unap lembairena ramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇč mba menacitndai.‚Äô  
\v 25 \x - \xo 27:25 \xt Ro 4.20-21, na 2 Ti 1.12\x*Ainda moca ramta…®r, ne kai nanambi teac, ne gagra, na aku r…®pacrina RaraŇč Aetaniaca aukmo mboprina reikca muruŇčcamiŇča larunandet.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 27:26 \xt Up 28.1\x*Aintik aina taŇčrena laŇčgumma, ma ootta taŇčca mut ianna wiwir nagacnande.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 LaŇčgumma wiwir magacat 
\p  
\v 27 Na aia Mediterenianna macait aniacna inikca utia taŇč, taŇčga mouŇčemba parniŇčapa paurna m…®nna monamoekna mouŇč r…®kca, laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra laŇčgummo mut ianna taŇčca rambuŇčaina mambopat.  
\v 28 Ri, mina ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®na Ňčgat…®kmo macait inikna keca pukca, ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®ca targaur 20na m…®n, karica mina emtem mac taŇčga mandaca mac keatnanna mana ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®a 15na m…®nna targaur malaruat.  
\v 29 Ainda moca an laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra mananambiat, moca mina watur tambat naganarica. Ri, mina laŇčgum ŇčgutiŇčrena reik paurmo aŇčg…®ca laŇčgumna iŇča keca irikca, mina auŇčmo tawi laruna mambendeiat.  
\v 30 Karica an laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra an laŇčgum t…®kcarica k…®pcarina moca, mina an kor tekermo Ňčga…®r p…®arca manmo puk nakeca mairikat. Ri, mina parua ndorimo laŇčgum ŇčgutiŇčrena reac ianna, an laŇčgum paŇčanmo mac kena mamori.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 27:31 \xt Up 27.22\x*Na mina ainda moatke, Pola an lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®rta ramoot paŇčanapa lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®r ndeidmo aindoprina, ‚ÄúNe wattacarica an ramta…®ra laŇčgumma eac Ňčgocor te, ne Ňčgocrainandet.‚ÄĚ  
\v 32 Ainda moatna mbatca, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra an korna Ňčga…®r kataca wattacarica, an kor tekera ma utia mataŇčgat. 
\p  
\v 33 Na auŇča raruna mori, Pola Ňčgepca minmo muruŇčcamiŇča amna reac emtem amna kam mambopri, ma aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe k…®dr…®k rocot Ňčgoinna, nena iroar inkara laŇča irik meraca eac Ňčgocor, na ne kamaind Ňčgoin maeacri, taŇč, taŇčga mandeaca raia parniŇčapa paurna m…®n mat…®kat.  
\v 34 \x - \xo 27:34 \xt 1 GRP 1.52, na Mt 10.30, na Lk 12.7\x*Ainda moca mandeaca aku nemo gagra mambopek. Ne amna reac emtem aŇčg…®ra am, te, ne eacnande. Na nena ianna mba mac Ňčgocraiitndai. Ne muruŇčcamiŇča laŇča monandet.‚ÄĚ  
\v 35 \x - \xo 27:35 \xt Mt 15.36, na In 6.11, na 1 Ti 4.3-5\x*Ri, ma aindopatke, iŇčmbaia ma tapac t…®p ndeid aŇčg…®ca ma RaraŇč Aetaniacmo, mina outta t…®kca mbendeica kam laŇč neaŇčga, karica ma tapac t…®p emtem witkica aŇčg…® maammbat.  
\v 36 Na ma ainda moatna mbatca, an ramta…®ra muruŇčcamiŇča iroar laiŇč aŇčg…®ca mitoco an tapacar t…®pembca aŇčg…®ca maammbat.  
\v 37 Na aia an laŇčgum mbuŇča taŇčrina ramta…®rta ŇčgaŇčganŇčg…®na m…®nna 276na m…®n.  
\v 38 Karica mina ndorita toŇčtoŇčna m…®nna amba maiatke, mina an laŇčgum inik ndeacrina witarta tamur aŇčg…®a macait inik nakecamariri, mina ainda mo te, laŇčgummo moi gobgica Ňčgep Ňčgacna moca. 
\s1 LaŇčgumma maŇčgocraiat 
\p  
\v 39 Karica auŇča raruatke, an laŇčgumna aiŇča morena ramta…®ra an maŇčara watca mina mba lamŇčiri, anna tenna pitrikna maŇčar. Na mina wattatnanna ma kodur laŇč ianap, tik mina laŇčgummo an ndiŇča ootti taŇčca an maŇčarna wiwir nagacna mori.  
\v 40 Ainda moca mina an laŇčgummo keca utiŇčga eacrina Ňčga…®rpaik kataca an reikmo macait inikca t…®kcarica, karica mina an Ňčgat…®kca Ňčgaua mina tiŇčara leacatnanmo p…®arca mina emba moa gaca watta manmo aŇčg…®ri, mina an maŇčarmo ootta mataŇčri.  
\v 41 \x - \xo 27:41 \xt 2 Ko 11.25\x*Ainda moatke, laŇčgumma an maŇčarmo raekmbaina wiwir nagaca mana paŇčanna anna tapaca ma taŇčna m…®nna wanaiŇč. Na mana iŇča mactir anikca manmo pia taŇč, taŇčga ma maw…®r…®pat.  
\v 42 Ri, an lapoca ruŇčrena ramta…®ra kam leaca mina an kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrena ramta…®rmo mo menacna mori, moca mina iri gaca k…®pcari nari.  
\v 43 Ainda mona moatke, ramoot paŇčan Iulies minmo, Pola mo menac narica ma minmo mbopca mina an kac Ňčgoreac ndeacrina ramta…®rmo mba mo menacri, ma minmo aindopatna, ‚ÄúNe mandaibinna irirenan, ne outta pukca iria maŇčar nagac.‚ÄĚ  
\v 44 \x - \xo 27:44 \xt Up 27.22-25\x*Na iri Ňčgocortanmo, mina an laŇčgum w…®r…®patna waŇčgor puŇčga mina an ŇčgutiŇčga an mbuŇča utia maŇčar magari. Na ande anna kirar mbuŇča aia muruŇčcamiŇča maŇčara magat, na ianna mba Ňčgocraiatke. 
\c 28  
\s1 Pola Malta mut nagaca an ndeacatna 
\p  
\v 1 Karica aia muruŇčcamiŇča maŇčara laŇč magari, na aia an mutmo magaracat, mana ia Malta.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 28:2 \xt Ro 1.14, na 1 Ko 14.11, na 2 Ko 11.27, na Kol 3.11\x*Ri, an mutna meikramta…®ra aimo ndiarirta t…®pemb kirarir laiŇč mamoat. Na an k…®dr…®k toco pukca rapacri, na aia magagauat, aintik mina tac aniac keca, aimo muruŇč Ňčgoinna aca aia an taca w…®t…®kca, aina tikembmo moa owaiatna.  
\v 3 Ainda mori mbuŇča Pola la…®r ndeid aŇčg…®a punica, an la…®rmo aŇčg…®a tac nakeca taca w…®ratke, nduop ianna ramta…®ra wica menacrenan, tacna owowai narica ma laruatnanna, mana para wica ikcamariat.  
\v 4 Na an mutna meikramta…®ra watri, nduopa Polna para loraca eacri, mina ndorimo ian, ianna mambopri, ‚ÄúAn ramootta, ramta…®ra moa menacrena ramoot ki? Aintik ma macait inikca mba menacri, na an kirara m…®r…®praraŇča, ramootmo ritri waparaca morenanna, manmo eteaca mba toŇčgori.‚ÄĚ  
\v 5 \x - \xo 28:5 \xt Mk 16.18, na Lk 10.19\x*Ainda moatke, Pola an nduopmo raurica tac inikca keca mbukca w…®rri, na Polmo reac ianna mba laruri.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 28:6 \xt Up 14.11\x*Na an mutna meikramta…®ra ainda watca, mina aind malamŇčiat, mana para urit ki? Co, ma anduna irikca menacnande. Ri, mina lambiri, mawatri, eaca k…®dr…®k rocot mamoat, na Polmo reac ianna mba laruri, aintik mina ndorita iroar Ňčgetrikica gaindopatna, ‚ÄúAnna ma raraŇč ian.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 7 Na an tiacar ndepikca roumb ndeacrenanna, anna ramoot paŇčan iannan, na mana ia Pubilius. Ma aimo aca aŇčg…®ca ndona kaca taŇčga aimo an rai mbonkacna inikca ma ndiarna t…®pca moca aimo mataua raupŇčiatna.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 28:8 \xt Up 19.11, na 1 Ko 12.9, na 12.28, na Ie 5.14-15\x*Ri, an m…®nna Pubiliusna aetta tik owowaiapa lopukna roumbca mori, na Pola taŇčga mamo watca mamo mbendeia mairi, ma ndona parmo an ramoot nambatta t…®kca mana roumbca laŇč mamoat.  
\v 9 Ainda moatke, an mutna auŇč ndeacrena roumbbebta meikramta…®ra k…®pca Pola mina roumbbebmo moa laŇč mamori.  
\v 10 Karica an mutna auŇčna meikramta…®ra Polmo torica, aimo t…®pemb laiŇč koinda morina. Na aia taŇčna mori, mina aimo maotacri. Na kainta reikca aia kamaind, mina aimo neaŇčrina. 
\s1 Pola taŇčga Rom malaruat 
\p  
\v 11 Na aia Malta mutmo karwir mbonkac maeacat. Karica iŇčmbaia aia an mut ndeacrina laŇčgum ian naŇčgabukca mataŇčgat. Na an laŇčgumma an mutmo wat aniaca k…®patna m…®nna ma anna eacri, na ma Aleksandria auŇčna laŇčgum, mana laŇčgum paŇčanna potaca eacrinanna reaca, anna Sus Ňčgacrina m…®r…®praraŇčna nuocniŇčna da paŇčanniŇč.  
\v 12 Ri, aia lembaia taŇčga Sirakus auŇč aniac ndaruca, an ndeaca taŇčga rai mbonkacna m…®n.  
\v 13 Karica aia Sirakus t…®kcarica, aia lembaia taŇčga Regium auŇč malaruat. Na iŇčmbaina ra, warna watta raŇčmbai ndiŇč nak…®patke, aia lembaia taŇčga rai mbonkac maiatke, aia Puteoli auŇča matundocat.  
\v 14 Na ainda moca aia Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacar ndeida watca, mina aimo minap eacna digiri, na aia minapa eaca taŇčga rai parmbaiapa mbut mbuniŇč mamoat. Karica aia min t…®kcarica, aia or mbuŇča Rom auŇč aniac mataŇčgat.  
\v 15 Ri, Rom ndeacrina Iesusa r…®pacrena laiplacara an kamma waraca, mina k…®pca aimo taupca t…®kca mandauprikiat. Na aia minmo Apiusna mbik t…®krena taupca t…®kca mawatat, anmo mina gaind Ňčgacrena Ňäemb Ňägorena Kaik Mbonkac. Ri, Pola mina watca ma RaraŇč Aetaniacmo kam laŇč neaŇčga, mana iro inikca magagrat. 
\s1 Pola Romma t…®kca kam wembaŇč laŇč mawiwitiat 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 28:16 \xt Up 24.23\x*Na aia taŇčga Rom auŇč aniaca laruri, anna ramoot paŇčanna Polmo wattacarica, ma ndona kac ian magaracri, na mana ŇčginaŇča mona lapoca ruŇčrena ramootap, maniŇča ndoniŇč niŇčgikca an ndeacrina. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 28:17 \xt Up 21.33, na 24.12-13, na 25.8\x*Karica rai mbonkac maiatke, ma Iudana ramta…®r paŇčaindmo aca, mina k…®pca puniatna mbatca, ma minmo aindoprina, ‚ÄúMin laiplacar, aku aina Iudana meikramta…®rmo reac Ňčgoreac ianna mo Ňčgocor, na aina nicar Ňčgamrirta t…®p ianna ipuŇčga, mo Ňčgocrai Ňčgocor. Na mina aukmo Ierusalemma t…®kca muoca utiŇčga RomnaŇčgepta par mat…®kat.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 28:18 \xt Up 22.24, na 25.8, na 26.31\x*Ri, RomnaŇčgepca aukmo ritri waparaca mori, mina wattatnanna, aku reac ianna mba moca, anna menacna, aintik mina aukmo wattacarica taŇčna moatke.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 28:19 \xt Up 25.11\x*Na Iudananda ainda mba toŇčgori, mina mac nda ipuŇčgatna mbatca, aku mbopna taupemb kocor. Aintik aku Sisamo aukna makukca ritri waparaca mona mambopat. Na an k…®dr…®kca aku ndona pitrik waŇčnanap ipuŇčna kam kocor.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 28:20 \xt Up 24.15, na 26.6-7, na 26.29, na Epe 3.1-2, na 2 Ti 2.9, na Pm 1.10, 13\x*Ainda moca aku nenmo aca k…®pca, nenmo wat te, nenap mbopna. Na gan lawirta Ňčgat…®kca mandeaca aukap eacrenanna, anna aku r…®paca aimo Israelnanda lambia eacrina reacna moca, ma ndo aukmo utiŇčga eacrena.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 21 Karica mina mana kammo nda rutica aindoprina, ‚ÄúUna moca aia Iudia auŇčnanta timbiŇč rapar ianna mba aŇčg…®ri. Na aina Iudana laiplacar ndeida an ndiŇča k…®prenanna, aimo una kam Ňčgoreac ian, co, un morina reac Ňčgoreac ianna kamma aŇčg…® k…®pca aimo mbop Ňčgocor.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 28:22 \xt Up 24.5, na 24.14, na 1 Pi 2.12, na 4.14\x*Aintik aia una iroara waracna, na aia lamŇčirina meikramta…®ra tamtam ndeacrenanna, mina gan Iesusna r…®t…®paikta meikramta…®rta tumbunmo nda ipuŇčga mambopreke.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 23 Karica Polapa an Iudana meikramta…®rap, mina ndorita tumbunna punina ra ianna larapacatna. Ri, an ra laruatke, an Iudana meikramta…®r w…®t aniac Ňčgoinna k…®pca, mana eacrina taupca punica mambopri. Na an ŇčaŇčarmuŇča t…®kca taŇčga wigwaca, ma w…®t…®kca minmo an T…®p Wand…®kna kambapa, RaraŇč Aetaniacna rambca morina ramta…®ra tirrina timbigta kapna kamb puŇčga, minmo RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuocna kamb topi p…®ar te, minmo moi iroar uriraca mina Iesusmo r…®pacna.  
\v 24 Ainda moca man mboprina kambca, ndeida anna r…®pacri, na ndeida an kambmo mba r…®pacatke.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 28:25 \xt Ais 6.9-10, na Mt 13.14\x*Ri, Pola mimo gan kam t…®p kabe Ňčgoin mambopat, ‚ÄúŇäeroŇč Ratta nena nicar Ňčgamrirmo kam gidikca RaraŇč Aetaniacna ramma morina ramoot Aisaiana upa t…®kca gaindopatna,  
\v 26 \x - \xo 28:26 \xt Ier 5.21, na Esi 12.2, na Ro 11.8\x*\x - \xo 28:26 \xt Ais 6.9-10\x*‚ÄėGan meikramta…®r tambuŇča taŇčca mimo aindop, ‚ÄúNe waracraŇčnandet, na ne mba mac lamŇči rapacitndai. Na ne watraŇčnandet, na ne mba watti garacitndai.‚ÄĚ  
\v 27 Aintik gan meikramta…®rta iroar inkara mamboracri, ainda moca mina ndorita kour puŇčga kamma waracna Ňčateri, na mina ndorita lamnik mapurocri. Moca mina ndorita kour puŇčga kamma warac nari, na moca mina ndorita lamnik puŇčga wat nari, na nikinik iroar puŇčga ndamŇči rapacna, te, mina auk ndambuŇča nda k…®pca aku minmo moi laiŇčga monandet.‚Äô‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 28-29 \x - \xo 28:28-29 \xt Ňäap 67.2, na Lk 3.6, na Up 13.46-47, na 18.6, na 22.21, na Ro 11.11\x*Ainda moca Pola gaind mac mbopatna, ‚ÄúNe gaind ndamŇči, RaraŇč Aetaniaca ma aimo mac nda aŇčg…®na aiŇč laŇčna kamma, ma Iudana meikramta…®r wanaiŇčmo ma neaŇčga taŇčrina. Na mina waracnande!‚ÄĚ\f + \fr 28:28-29 \ft Na landamŇčina ramta…®r ndeida gaind ndamŇčirena, kabena kam t…®p toca gan timbigta kapna inikca eacrenan. Na an kamma gaind. \fq Pola an kamb ndopca maiatke, an Iudana meikramta…®ra Ňčgepca taŇčre mbuŇča, ndorimo kamb puŇčga maipuŇčga mataŇčri.\f* 
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 28:30 \xt Up 28.16\x*Na gui mbuniŇčna inikca ma ndona t…®p t…®pca oikrena kaca an ndeacri, meikramta…®ra man Ňčgokena moca k…®p te, ma minmo aca t…®krena.  
\v 31 \x - \xo 28:31 \xt Up 4.31, na 28.23, na Epe 6.19\x*Ainda mori, ma mba nanambiri, ma RaraŇč Aetaniacna bubuocna kammo ma kam gargar Ňčgoin mbuŇča wiwitirina, na ma minmo Kacoot Iesus Karaisna t…®pembta kirarirmo mariptiat. Na meac, co ramoot ianna manmo mba k…®racri.